g%20a%20surveillance%20mission%20over%20the%20Black%20Sea%20in%20international%20airspace%20when%20it%20came%20into%20contact%20with%20two%20Russian%20SU-27%20fighter%20jets.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%2C%20the%20Russian%20pilots%20received%20an%20apparent%20command%20from%20their%20ground%20station%20controller%2C%20who%20according%20to%20one%20Western%20source%2C%20told%20them%20loosely%3A%20%26quot%3BYou%20have%20the%20target%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20BBC%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20pilots%20thought%20it%20was%20a%20command%20to%20fire%20so%20released%20an%20air-to-air%20missile%2C%20which%20successfully%20launched%20but%20failed%20to%20lock%20on%20to%20its%20target%2C%20the%20BBC%20reported.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20radio%20communications%20picked%20up%20by%20the%20RAF%20surveillance%20plane%2C%20the%20other%20pilot%20of%20the%20Su-27%20swore%20at%20his%20colleague%20and%20asked%20him%20what%20he%20thought%20he%20was%20doing.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20this%20didn't%20stop%20the%20first%20pilot%20from%20releasing%20another%20missile%2C%20though%20this%20one%20either%20malfunctioned%20or%20was%20aborted%2C%20the%20sources%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Ministry%20of%20Defence%20told%20the%20BBC%20that%20the%20incident%20is%20%26quot%3Ba%20stark%20reminder%20of%20the%20potential%20consequences%20of%20%5BVladimir%5D%20Putin's%20barbaric%20invasion%20of%20Ukraine%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20did%20not%20reveal%20the%20exact%20communications%20between%20the%20pilots.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%20of%20the%20incident%2C%20a%20US%20official%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2023%2F04%2F12%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Frussian-jet-british-spy-plane.html%5C%22%3Etold%20The%20New%20York%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20near-miss%20was%20%26quot%3Breally%2C%20really%20scary.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20highlights%20the%20lack%20of%20professionalism%20of%20Russia's%20air%20force%2C%20the%20newspaper%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20incident%2C%20RAF%20flights%20have%20been%20escorted%20by%20Typhoon%20fighter%20jets%20armed%20with%20air-to-air%20missiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20spokesperson%20for%20Russia's%20Ministry%20of%20Defense%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20Insider's%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-covered-up-pilot-attempt-shoot-down-nato-aircraft-bbc-2023-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694683827000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6502c7e91afe8f0019ea2fc3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-covered-up-pilot-attempt-shoot-down-nato-aircraft-bbc-2023-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Russian%20pilot%20fired%20two%20missiles%20at%20an%20unnamed%20British%20Royal%20Air%20Force%20reconnaissance%20plan%20last%20year%20%E2%80%94%20but%20missed%2C%20the%20BBC%20reported.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22sankel%40businessinsider.com%20(Sophia%20Ankel)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-covered-up-pilot-attempt-shoot-down-nato-aircraft-bbc-2023-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Jaahnavi%20Kandula's%20Family%20Mourns%20%26quot%3BLost%20Child%26quot%3B%2C%20Asks%20Cops%20Tough%20Questions%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20family%20of%20Jaahnavi%20Kandula%2C%20the%20young%20woman%20who%20died%20in%20the%20United%20States%20in%20January%20after%20being%20hit%20by%20a%20patrol%20car%2C%20has%20questioned%20the%20delay%20in%20release%20of%20bodycam%20footage%20in%20which%20a%20Seattle%20police%20officer%20is%20heard%20laughing%20about%20the%20horrific%20incident.%20%26quot%3BBut%20she%20is%20dead...%20%26quot%3B%20the%20officer%20is%20heard%20saying%20before%20laughing.%20%26quot%3BNo%2C%20it's%20a%20regular%20person.%20Yeah%2C%20just%20write%