has%20stopped%20eating%20since%20yesterday%2C%20It%20is%20as%20though%20all%20the%20pain%20has%20come%20alive%20once%20again.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fjaahnavi-kandula-accident-india-seeks-probe-into-us-cop-laughing-after-andhra-pradesh-student-death-in-accident-4387989%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIndia%20Seeks%20Probe%20After%20US%20Cops%20Caught%20Joking%20Over%20Andhra%20Student's%20Death%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Ms%20Kandula's%20family%20has%20also%20released%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20truly%20disturbing%20and%20saddening%20to%20hear%20insensible%20comments%20on%20the%20bodycam%20video%20from%20an%20SPD%20officer%20regarding%20Jaahnavi's%20death.%20Jaahnavi%20is%20a%20beloved%20daughter%20and%20beyond%20any%20dollar%20value%20for%20her%20mother%20and%20family.%20We%20firmly%20believe%20that%20every%20human%20life%20is%20invaluable%20and%20should%20not%20be%20belittled%2C%20especially%20during%20a%20tragic%20loss.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMs%20Kandula%20was%20a%2023-year-old%20student%20at%20Northeastern%20University%2C%20from%20where%20she%20was%20due%20to%20graduate%20with%20a%20degree%20in%20information%20systems%20in%20December.%20According%20to%20a%20Seattle%20Times%20report%20from%20that%20day%20-%20January%2023%20-%20she%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Findian-origin-woman-hit-by-police-vehicle-in-us-dies-report-3725908%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehit%20by%20a%20speeding%20police%20car%20while%20trying%20to%20cross%20a%20road%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20Bodycam%20Footage%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20footage%20was%20released%20Monday%20-%20months%20after%20Ms%20Kandula%20was%20killed%20-%20with%20a%20brief%20statement%20that%20said%20it%20had%20been%20flagged%20by%20Seattle%20Police%20Department%20employee%20%26quot%3Bin%20the%20routine%20course%20of%20business%26quot%3B%20who%20expressed%20%26quot%3Bconcern%20about%20the%20nature%20of%20statements%20heard%26quot%3B%20on%20the%20video.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fspdblotter.seattle.gov%2F2023%2F09%2F11%2Fbody-worn-video-from-officer-involved-collision-january-2023%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESPD%20said%20it%20was%20releasing%20the%20video%20%26quot%3Brecognizing%20public%20concern%3C%2Fa%3E...%20in%20the%20interest%20of%20transparency%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20it%20would%20not%20comment%20further%20pending%20the%20completion%20of%20an%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FEy_wASffmek%3Fsi%3DMdID-bjPWIaP_D-3%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMs%20Kandula%20was%20not%20jaywalking%20-%20i.e.%2C%20crossing%20the%20road%20at%20any%20point%20other%20than%20a%20zebra%20crossing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20video%2C%20Officer%20Daniel%20Auderer%2C%20Vice%20President%20of%20the%20Seattle%20Police%20Officers%20Guild%2C%20had%20responded%20to%20the%20scene%20of%20Ms%20Kandula's%20death.%20She%20had%20been%20struck%20by%20a%20police%20car%20driven%20by%20Officer%20Kevin%20Dave.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMr%20Auderer%20had%20been%20tasked%20with%20determining%20if%20Mr%20Dave%20was%20under%20the%20influence%20and%20concluded%20he%20was%20not.%20After%20finishing%20his%20inquiry%20he%20was%20talking%20to%20SPOG%20chief%20Mike%20Solan%20and%20the%20bodycam%20footage%20captured%20the%20audio%20from%20that%20call.%20Only%20Mr%20Auderer's%20side%20of%20the%20conversation%20is%20audible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.seattletimes.com%2Fseattle-news%2Flaw-justice%2Finvestigation-launched-into-tape-of-seattle-police-guild-leaders-downplaying-death-of-woman-struck-by-officer%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMr%20Auderer%20has%20said%20his%20conversation%20was%20%26quot%3Bprivate%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20that%20he%20had%20left%20the%20bodycam%20on%20by%20mistake.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWhat%20Happened%20To%20Jaahnavi%20Kandula%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EA%20SPD%20report%20released%20in%20June%20said%20the%20patrol%20car%20-%20being%20driven%20by%20Officer%20Kevin%20Dave%20-%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.seattletimes.com%2Fseattle-news%2Flaw-justice%2Ffamily-of-pedestrian-struck-killed-by-seattle-cop-seeks-details%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etravelling%20at%2074%20miles%20per%20hour%20(119%20km%20per%20hour)%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20inquiry%20also%20determined%20the%20speed%20of%20the%20vehicle%20was%20the%20main%20reason%20for%20the%20collision%2C%20the%20Seattle%20Times%20said%20in%20another%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20car%20began%20braking%20less%20than%20a%20second%20before%20it%20hit%20Ms%20Kandula%20and%20was%20travelling%20at%20about%2063%20miles%20per%20hour%20(101%20km%20per%20hour)%20at%20the%20time%20of%20impact.%20Ms%20Kandula%20was%20thrown%20138%20feet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20speed%20limit%20on%20the%20street%20where%20she%20was%20hit%20was%2025%20miles%20per%20hour%2C%20or%2040%20km%20per%20hour.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20officers%20were%20responding%20to%20a%20911%20call%20but%2C%20significantly%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.seattletimes.com%2Fseattle-news%2Fseattle-police-officer-was-driving-74-mph-before-he-hit-killed-pedestrian%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMs%20Kandula%20%26quot%3Bhad%20right%20of%20way%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%3B%20the%20law%20states%20police%20can%20exceed%20speed%20limits%20in%20certain%20cases%20but%20not%20if%20that%20will%20endanger%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EUS%20Assures%20Probe%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Fjaahnavi-kandula-accident-us-assures-probe-amid-outrage-over-video-of-cop-joking-on-indians-death-4388333%23pfrom%3Dhome-ndtv_topscroll%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUnited%20States%20government%20has%20promised%20a%20swift%20but%20fair%20investigation%20into%20Ms%20Kandula's%20death%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20comes%20after%20the%20Indian%20consulate%20in%20San%20Francisco%20demanded%20an%20inquiry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3ERecent%20reports%20including%20in%20media%20of%20the%20handling%20of%20Ms%20Jaahnavi%20Kandula's%20death%20in%20a%20road%20accident%20in%20Seattle%20in%20January%20are%20deeply%20troubling.%20We%20have%20taken%20up%20the%20matter%20strongly%20with%20local%20authorities%20in%20Seattle%20%26amp%3B%20Washington%20State%20as%20well%20as%20senior%20officials%20in%20Washington%20DC%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20India%20in%20SF%20(%40CGISFO)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FCGISFO%2Fstatus%2F1701961201884795055%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ESeptember%2013%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Cp%3ESenior%20officials%20of%20President%20Joe%20Biden's%20administration%20have%20reportedly%20assured%20Taranjit%20Singh%20Sandhu%2C%20India's%20Ambassador%20to%20the%20US%2C%20the%20incident%20is%20being%20taken%20very%20seriously.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20report%20by%20the%20British%20Broadcasting%20Corporation%20quotes%20a%20radio%20talk%20show%20host%20as%20claiming%20he%20has%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-66803960%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewritten%20statement%20from%20Mr%20Auderer%3C%2Fa%3E%20explaining%20his%20comments%20were%20mocking%20what%20he%20thought%20would%20be%20city%20attorneys'%20reaction%20to%20the%20incident%2C%20and%20how%20they%20might%20try%20to%20minimise%20liability.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWith%20input%20from%20agencies%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694683800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fup44s5cg_jaahnavi-kandula_625x300_13_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.n