%20significant%20state%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20a%20report%20by%20a%20similar%20commission%20formed%20to%20study%20the%20division%20of%20the%2027%25%20OBC%20reservation%20has%20been%20lying%20in%20cold%20storage%20since%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20the%20report%20has%20had%20no%20takers%2C%20including%20the%20Adityanath%20government%2C%20probably%20because%20the%20panel%E2%80%99s%20recommendations%20threaten%20to%20not%20only%20jeopardise%20the%20saffron%20party%E2%80%99s%20caste%20calculations%20and%20antagonise%20its%20OBC%20allies%2C%20but%20also%20disturb%20its%20idea%20of%20political%20Hindu%20unity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20OBC%20leader%20Om%20Prakash%20Rajbhar%20%E2%80%93%20who%20had%20been%20breathing%20down%20the%20BJP%20government%E2%80%99s%20neck%20demanding%20the%20implementation%20of%20OBC%20sub-quotas%20%E2%80%93%20returning%20to%20the%20NDA%20recently%2C%20the%20loudest%20voice%20in%20favour%20of%20sub-categorisation%20has%20gone%20silent%20for%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20250px)%2085vw%2C%20250px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F14113331%2FJt.-Raghvendra-Kumar-300x289.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22250%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F14113331%2FJt.-Raghvendra-Kumar-300x289.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F14113331%2FJt.-Raghvendra-Kumar-1024x985.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F14113331%2FJt.-Raghvendra-Kumar.jpg%201200w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-672972%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22240%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EJustice%20Raghvendra%20Kumar.%20Photo%3A%20allahabadhighcourt.in%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20May%202018%2C%20less%20than%20a%20year%20before%20the%202019%20general%20elections%2C%20the%20Adityanath%20government%20appointed%20a%20four-member%20social%20justice%20committee%20headed%20by%20retired%20Allahabad%20high%20court%20judge%20Justice%20Raghvendra%20Kumar%20to%20examine%20a%20division%20of%20the%20OBC%20quota%2C%20just%20like%20some%20other%20states%20such%20as%20Bihar%20had%20done.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20need%20was%20felt%20to%20examine%20the%20possibility%20of%20dividing%20the%2027%25%20quota%20due%20to%20the%20public%20perception%20built%20by%20the%20BJP%20that%20castes%20such%20as%20Yadavs%20were%20cornering%20a%20lion%E2%80%99s%20share%20of%20benefits%20and%20jobs%20under%20the%20reservation%20policy%20%E2%80%93%20especially%20due%20to%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%E2%80%99s%20(SP)%20patronage%20whenever%20it%20came%20to%20power%20%E2%80%93%20while%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20backward%20castes%20were%20left%20under-represented%20and%20deprived.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Kumar%20commission%20submitted%20its%20report%20to%20the%20government%20in%20October%202018.%20But%20despite%20assurances%20in%20the%20UP%20assembly%20that%20the%20government%20was%20legally%20examining%20the%20report%2C%20it%20was%20never%20tabled%20in%20the%20House%20or%20implemented.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChanging%20political%20equations%20over%20the%20past%20five%20years%20and%20newer%20demands%20by%20OBC%20parties%20have%20further%20pushed%20the%20subject%20of%20sub-categorisation%20out%20of%20political%20discourse.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2F4-27-reasons-why-the-bjp-is-panicky-about-caste-consciousness%5C%22%3E4.27%20Reasons%20Why%20the%20BJP%20is%20Panicky%20About%20Caste%20Consciousness%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20copy%20of%20the%20report%20accessed%20by%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20shows%20that%20it%20recommends%20the%20sub-categorisation%20of%20the%2027%25%20OBC%20quota%20into%20three%20divisions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20would%20be%20the%20%3Cem%3Epichda%20varg%3C%2Fem%3E%20(backward%20class)%2C%20who%20would%20get%207%25%3B%20%3Cem%3Eati%20pichda%3C%2Fem%3E%20(more%20backward)%2C%20who%20would%20get%2011%25%3B%20and%20the%20%3Cem%3Eatyant%20pichda%3C%2Fem%3E%20(most%20backward)%2C%20who%20would%20get%209%25%20reservation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOut%20of%20the%2079%20OBC%20castes%20in%20UP%2C%20nine%20would%20be%20categorised%20as%20backward%20class%2C%2037%20as%20more%20backward%20and%2033%20as%20most%20backward.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDominant%20and%20politically%20conscious%20Hindu%20groups%20such%20as%20Yadav%2C%20Kurmi%20and%20Jat%20are%20in%20the%20first%20category%2C%20along%20with%20the%20Sonar%2C%20Koeri%2C%20Kalwar%20and%20Chaurasia%20castes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Kumar%20Commission%20found%20that%20these%20castes%20were%20politically%2C%20socially%2C%20economically%20and%20culturally%20%E2%80%9Ccapable%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cstrong%E2%80%9D%2C%20and%20enjoyed%20employment%20in%20government%20jobs%20at%20all%20levels%20(Group%20A%2C%20B%2C%20C%20and%20D)%20way%20above%20their%20share%20in%20the%20population.%20They%20also%20enjoyed%20influential%20political%20representation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20the%20report%20notes%20that%20these%20castes%20compare%20themselves%20to%20Brahmins%20and%20Kshatriyas%20and%20feel%20a%20sense%20of%20pride%20in%20mentioning%20their%20castes.%20Their%20social%20relationships%20and%20behaviour%20with%20the%20other%20backward%20castes%20mimic%20that%20of%20the%20upper%20castes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20more%20backward%20caste%20category%20includes%20the%20Kushwaha-Maurya-Shakya-Saini%20and%20Gaderia-Pal-Baghel%20groups%2C%20and%20the%20Gurjar%2C%20Prajapati%2C%20Kumhar%2C%20Lodh%20Rajput%2C%20Teli%2C%20Sahu%2C%20Vishwakarma%20and%20Lohar%20castes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Kumar%20Commission%20found%20these%20castes%20to%20have%20poor%20representation%20politically%20and%20economically%2C%20and%20as%20being%20less%20progressive%20than%20the%20backward%20class%20category%2C%20although%C2%A0they%20did%20not%20face%20cultural%20exclusion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20backward%20castes%20had%20an%20employment%20rate%20of%20only%2050%25%20in%20comparison%20to%20their%20population%20share.%20Also%2C%20only%20some%20specific%20castes%20in%20this%20category%20were%20getting%20all%20the%20government%20jobs%2C%20leading%20to%20the%20emergence%20of%20a%20new%20middle%20class%2C%20the%20commission%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERiverine%20castes%20such%20as%20Mallah%2C%20Nishad%2C%20Kewat%2C%20Kahar%2C%20Bind%2C%20Dheevar%20and%20Kahar%20are%20part%20of%20the%20third%20category%2C%20the%20most%20backward%20castes.%20This%20group%20includes%20the%20Rajbhar%2C%20Bhar%2C%20Noniya%20Chauhan%2C%20Ghosi%20and%20Arakvanshi%20castes%2C%20and%20also%20some%20Muslim%20castes%20such%20as%20Qureshi%2C%20Gaddi%20and%20Mansuri.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20are%20the%20most%20deprived%20sections%2C%20with%20limited%20political%20drawing-power%20and%20being%20culturally%2C%20socially%20and%20economically%20backward.%20They%20are%20mostly%20either%20employed%20in%20lower%20levels%20of%20government%20services%20(Group%20C%20and%20D)%20or%20have%20zero%20representation%2C%20the%20report%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F2zUfHp48d8s%3Fsi%3DX7cr2yub9SgkNAnq%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20commission%E2%80%99s%20recommendations%20provided%20for%20the%20better%20representation%20for%20deprived%20sections%20among%20the%20OBCs%2C%20it%20turned%20into%20a%20knotty%20affair%20for%20the%20BJP%2C%20as%20the%20report%20not%20only%20suggested%20reduced%20quotas%20for%20dominant%20castes%20such%20as%20Yadavs%2C%20Kurmis%20and%20Jats%2C%20but%20it%20also%20clubbed%20them%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20grouping%20Kurmis%20and%20Jats%20together%20with%20Yadavs%2C%20the%20BJP%20risked%20disturbing%20its%20anti-Yadav%20narrative%20and%20alienating%20the%20other%20two%2C%20whose%20votes%20it%20needs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20most%20loyal%20ally%20in%20UP%20since%202014%2C%20the%20Apna%20Dal%20(Soneylal)%20led%20by%20Anupriya%20Patel%2C%20is%20based%20on%20Kurmi%20support.%20It%20is%20a%20traditionally%20farming%20caste.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Jats%20are%20a%20landed%2C%20agrarian%20community%20in%20western%20UP%2C%20whose%20votes%20the%20BJP%20has%20banked%20on%20ever%20since%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Ften-years-later-shadow-of-the-2013-riots-still-haunts-muzaffarnagar%5C%22%3EMuzaffarnagar%20communal%20riots%20of%202013%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20the%20Yadavs%2C%20a%20traditional%20herding%20caste%2C%20are%20the%20core%20support%20base%20of%20the%20SP.%20The%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20politics%20in%20the%20state%20in%20recent%20years%20has%20relied%20on%20polarising%20the%20non-Yadav%20backward%20castes%20against%20the%20Yadavs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EImplementing%20the%20social%20justice%20report%20in%20its%20current%20form%20would%20blunt%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20narrative%20that%20only%20the%20Yadavs%20enjoyed%20the%20cream%20of%20reservations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20build-up%20to%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%2C%20before%20the%20Balakot%20airstrike%20changed%20equations%2C%20the%20Apna%20Dal%20leader%20Patel%20had%20accused%20the%20Adityanath%20government%20of%20trying%20to%20divide%20OBCs%20and%20creating%20rifts%20between%20them%20if%20it%20planned%20to%20implement%20the%20sub-categorisation%20without%20a%20caste%20census.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20cannot%20snatch%20one%20one%E2%80%99s%20share%20and%20give%20it%20to%20another%2C%E2%80%9D%20Patel%2C%20a%20minister%20in%20the%20Modi%20government%2C%20said%20in%20January%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESamajwadi%20Party%20president%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%2C%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20chief%20opponent%20and%20an%20OBC%20himself%2C%20had%20then%20accused%20the%20BJP%20of%20divide%20and%20rule%20and%20of%20misleading%20the%20OBCs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20interested%20in%20a%20division%20of%20the%20OBC%20quota%2C%20Yadav%2C%20since%20losing%20power%2C%20changed%20tack%20to%20aggressively%20demanding%20a%20caste%20census%20to%20count%20the%20number%20of%20OBCs%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20other%20OBC%20ally%2C%20the%20NISHAD%20Party%20has%20also%20not%20shown%20any%20interest%20in%20the%20sub-categorisation%20of%20quotas.%20Its%20leader%20Sanjay%20Nishad%20has%20for%20long%20demanded%20that%20riverine%20OBC%20castes%20including%20his%20be%20included%20in%20the%20Scheduled%20Castes%20(SC)%20category.%20He%20argues%20that%20Nishad%20and%20allied%20castes%20were%20sub-castes%20of%20the%20Majhwar%20and%20Turaaiha%20castes%2C%20which%20are%20in%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20SC%20list.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fneed-of-the-hour-a-selfie-called-caste-census-india-must-confront-its-truth%5C%22%3ENeed%20of%20the%20Hour%3A%20A%20Selfie%20Called%20Caste%20Census%20%E2%80%93%20India%20Must%20Confront%20its%20Truth%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20draw%20attention%20of%20the%20Union%20government%20%E2%80%93%20which%20has%20the%20power%20to%20add%20castes%20to%20the%20SC%20list%20%E2%80%93%20and%20mobilise%20its%20own%20voters%20on%20the%20issue%2C%20Nishad%20in%20June%20launched%20an%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EArakshan%20Mahasampark%20Abhiyan%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20%5BHindi%20for%20%E2%80%98Campaign%20for%20Great%20Outreach%20on%20Reservation%E2%80%99%5D%20from%20eight%20districts%20in%20UP%E2%80%99s%20Purvanchal%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20December%202021%20rally%20in%20Lucknow%20hosted%20by%20Nishad%2C%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fother-states%2Fonly-pm-modi-has-worked-for-backward-castes-amit-shah%2Farticle37978907.ece%5C%22%3Epromised%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20if%20the%20BJP%20returned%20to%20power%20in%20UP%20in%202022%2C%20it%20would%20%E2%80%9Cfulfil%20all%20agendas%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20Nishad%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20inclusion%20of%20the%20Nishads%20in%20the%20SC%20category%20is%20still%20awaited%2C%20Nishad%20did%20fulfill%20his%20personal%20ambition%20and%20got%20himself%20inducted%20as%20a%20cabinet%20minister%20in%20the%20Adityanath%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20in%20recent%20months%20and%20especially%20after%20returning%20to%20the%20NDA%2C%20even%20Om%20Prakash%20Rajbhar%20has%20started%20to%20raise%20a%20similar%20demand%20that%20the%20Rajbhars%20be%20included%20in%20the%20SC%20category.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20there%20is%20a%20parallel%20movement%20led%20by%20an%20outfit%20called%20Jago%20Rajbhar%20Jago%20Samiti%20(JRJS)%20to%20get%20Rajbhars%20and%20Bhars%20included%20in%20the%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20(ST)%20list.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20July%2C%20hearing%20a%20contempt%20petition%20by%20JRJS%2C%20the%20Allahabad%20high%20court%20directed%20the%20Adityanath%20government%20to%20respond%20within%20two%20months%20to%20a%20letter%20issued%20by%20the%20Centre%20in%20October%202021%20to%20the%20state%20seeking%20its%20proposal%20for%20the%20inclusion%20of%20Rajbhars%20and%20Bhars%20in%20the%20ST%20list.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20informed%20the%20high%20court%20that%20it%20had%20completed%20its%20survey%20in%2072%20out%20of%2075%20districts%20in%20the%20state%20and%20needed%20more%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20high%20court%20had%20in%20March%202022%20directed%20the%20state%20to%20respond%20to%20the%20Centre%E2%80%99s%20letter%2C%20but%20the%20government%20did%20not%20comply%20with%20the%20order.%20The%20JRJS%20then%20filed%20a%20contempt%20petition.%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EArakshan%20nahi%2C%20toh%20vote%20nahi%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20goes%20the%20JRJS%E2%80%99%20slogan%20%5BHindi%20for%20%E2%80%98no%20vote%20if%20no%20reservation%E2%80%99%5D%2C%20which%20has%20got%20louder%20after%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fdespite-using-all-might-bjp-loses-ghosi-assembly-seat-to-india-in-uttar-pradesh%5C%22%3EBJP%20lost%20the%20recent%20assembly%20by-poll%20in%20Ghosi%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20seat%20with%20a%20substantial%20number%20of%20Rajbhar%20voters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F08173312%2FF4tErMfbMAArKnN-1024x600.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F08173312%2FF4tErMfbMAArKnN-1024x600.jpeg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F08173312%2FF4tErMfbMAArKnN-425x250.jpeg%20425w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-672148%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22492%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20Samajwadi%20Party%20won%20the%20Ghosi%20bypoll.%20Party%20chief%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20is%20pictured%20here%20at%20a%20rally%20in%20Ghosi.%20Photo%3A%20X%2F%40yadavakhilesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Allahabad%20high%20court%20has%20on%20three%20occasions%20previously%20stayed%20attempts%20by%20the%20state%20government%20to%20issue%20SC%20certificates%20to%20some%20OBC%20castes%2C%20saying%20that%20only%20the%20Union%20government%20had%20such%20powers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Mulayam%20Singh%20Yadav%20government%20had%20in%202005%20amended%20the%20UP%20Public%20Services%20Act%2C%201994%20to%20make%20way%20for%20the%20inclusion%20of%2017%20most%20backward%20castes%20into%20the%20SC%20list.%20His%20son%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20tried%20a%20similar%20manoeuvre%20when%20he%20was%20in%20power%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Flucknow%2Fup-govt-clears-proposal-to-include-17-backward-sub-castes-in-sc-list-4440909%2F%5C%22%3Epassing%20a%20proposal%20for%20the%20inclusion%20of%20these%2017%20castes%20into%20the%20SC%20list%3C%2Fa%3E%20through%20a%20cabinet%20decision.%20In%202019%2C%20Adityanath%20too%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Flucknow%2Fin-caste-certificate-move-bjp-tries-to-net-fishing-community-for-2022-up-elections-5815845%2F%5C%22%3Edirected%3C%2Fa%3E%20all%20districts%20to%20issue%20SC%20certificates%20to%20these%20OBC%20castes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%2017%20castes%2C%20if%20the%20OBC%20sub-categorisation%20becomes%20a%20reality%2C%20would%20fall%20under%20the%20more%20backward%20and%20most%20backward%20category%2C%20but%20predominantly%20under%20the%20latter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20majority%20of%20these%2017%20castes%20are%20riverine%20communities%20such%20as%20Mallah%2C%20Kashyap%2C%20Nishad%20and%20Kewat.%20The%20Rajbhar-Bhar%20communities%20and%20Prajapati-Kumhar%20communities%2C%20which%20have%20been%20traditionally%20engaged%20in%20pottery%2C%20make%20up%20the%20rest.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBahujan%20Samaj%20Party%20(BSP)%20chief%20Mayawati%20has%20been%20a%20vocal%20critic%20of%20the%20possibility%20of%20the%20inclusion%20of%20these%20OBCs%20into%20the%20SC%20list%20and%20maintained%20that%20such%20a%20move%20should%20only%20take%20place%20after%20increasing%20the%20SC%20quota%20limit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20also%20not%20the%20first%20time%20the%20BJP%20has%20tried%20to%20divide%20the%20OBC%20quota.%20The%20Rajnath%20Singh%20government%20had%20in%202001%20constituted%20a%20social%20justice%20committee%20headed%20by%20parliamentary%20affairs%20minister%20Hukum%20Singh%20to%20examine%20the%20distribution%20of%20quotas%20for%20both%20OBCs%20and%20SCs%2C%20as%20the%20party%20was%20trying%20to%20loosen%20the%20hold%20of%20the%20SP%20and%20BSP%20on%20these%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Hukum%20Singh%20Committee%20report%20recommended%20division%20of%20the%20OBC%20quota%20into%20three%20categories%2C%20isolating%20the%20Yadavs%20to%20a%20mere%205%25%20reservation.%20It%20raised%20the%20OBC%20quota%20from%2027%25%20to%2028%25%2C%20taking%20a%20percentage%20from%20the%20share%20of%20the%20tribals%2C%20whose%20population%20had%20reduced%20in%20the%20state%20after%20the%20formation%20of%20Uttarakhand%20in%202000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20calculated%20the%20population%20of%20OBCs%20in%20UP%20to%20be%2054.05%25%20(79%20castes)%2C%20a%20huge%20jump%20from%20the%2041.13%25%20in%201991%2C%20when%20the%20number%20of%20castes%20designated%20as%20OBCs%20were%20just%2055%2C%20wrote%20political%20analyst%20A.K.%20Verma%20in%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.epw.in%2Fjournal%2F2001%2F48%2Fcommentary%2Fbjps-caste-card.html%5C%22%3Earticle%3C%2Fa%3E%20published%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3EEconomic%20and%20Political%20Weekly%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%202001.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIts%20report%20isolated%20the%20Yadav%20community%20as%20the%20only%20backward%20caste.%20Eight%20castes%2C%20which%20would%20get%20nine%20percent%20reservation%2C%20were%20put%20in%20the%20more%20backward%20category.%20These%20castes%20included%20the%20Jats%2C%20Kurmis%2C%20Gurjars%2C%20Lodhs%20and%20Sonars.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20third%20category%2C%20most%20backward%2C%20was%20the%20largest%20as%20it%20included%2070%20castes%2C%20which%20made%20up%20a%20massive%2061.69%25%20of%20the%20OBC%20population.%20These%20communities%20would%20get%2014%25%20reservation.%20The%20Most%20Backward%20category%20included%20Kumhar%2C%20Koeri%2C%20Pal%2C%20Gaderia%2C%20Lohar%2C%20Nishad%2C%20Teli%2C%20Rajbhar%2C%20Shakya%2C%20Kushwaha%2C%20Noniya%20Chauhan%2C%20Maurya%20and%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20report%2C%20Yadavs%2C%20who%20constituted%2019.40%25%20of%20the%20OBC%20population%2C%20were%20occupying%20a%20disproportionate%20share%20in%20government%20services%20with%2033%25%20of%20the%20jobs.%20Kurmis%20and%20Jats%20too%20were%20reaping%20the%20benefits%20of%20reservation%20beyond%20their%20numbers.%20Kurmis%20(7.46%25%20of%20OBCs)%20had%2012.49%25%20share%20in%20jobs%2C%20while%20Jats%20(3.61%25)%20had%206.85%25%20presence%20in%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA.K.%20Verma%20writes%20that%20the%20UP%20cabinet%20had%20accepted%20the%20report%20in%20September%202001%20and%20the%20state%20Assembly%20even%20approved%20an%20ordinance%20amending%20existing%20reservation%20rules.%20However%2C%20the%20BJP%20government%20could%20not%20implement%20the%20report%20as%20it%20soon%20lost%20power%20in%20UP.%20Besides%2C%20the%20court%20too%20had%20put%20a%20stay%20on%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsupreme-court-bench-reservation%5C%22%3EReservation%20Is%20About%20Adequate%20Representation%2C%20Not%20Poverty%20Eradication%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20Rohini%20Commission%20report%20now%20in%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20domain%2C%20Suheldev%20Bharatiya%20Samaj%20Party%20(SBSP)%20chief%20spokesperson%20Arun%20Rajbhar%20says%20the%20party%2C%20which%20held%20the%20backward%20classes%20welfare%20ministry%20under%20Yogi%201.0%2C%20is%20hopeful%20that%20the%20Modi%20government%20would%20divide%20the%20OBC%20quota%20at%20the%20national%20level%20and%20include%20the%20recommendations%20of%20the%20Raghavendra%20Kumar%20commission%20in%20its%20formula.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAsked%20by%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20on%20why%20the%20party%20had%20gone%20silent%20on%20sub-categorisation%20at%20the%20state%20level%2C%20Arun%20Rajbhar%20said%20the%20SBSP%20would%20include%20a%20demand%20for%20its%20implementation%20in%20its%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20manifesto.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20sub-categorisation%20of%20OBCs%20into%20three%20large%20blocs%20may%20also%20potentially%20disrupt%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20till-now%20successful%20narrative%20of%20isolating%20Jatavs%2C%20Yadavs%20and%20Muslims%2C%20who%20together%20make%20up%2040%25%20of%20the%20state%20population%2C%20while%20using%20Hindutva%20and%20realpolitik%20to%20wean%20away%20sections%20of%20the%20first%20two.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUP%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20Keshav%20Prasad%20Maurya%20has%20best%20described%20it%20thus%3A%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3ESau%20mein%20saat%20hamara%2C%20chalis%20mein%20bhi%20batwara%20hai.%20Aur%20batware%20mein%20bhi%20hamara%20hain%3C%2Fem%3E.%E2%80%9D%20Loosely%20translate%20it%20reads%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%2060%25%20of%20the%20votes.%20The%20remaining%2040%25%20are%20divided%2C%20but%20even%20in%20that%2C%20we%20have%20a%20share.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20last%20time%20the%20BJP%20government%20was%20openly%20confronted%20by%20the%20SBSP%20on%20the%20issue%20of%20sub-categorisation%20was%20in%20August%202021.%20Anil%20Rajbhar%2C%20then%20backward%20classes%20welfare%20minister%2C%20had%20said%20the%20government%20was%20examining%20the%20report%20to%20ensure%20that%20it%20did%20not%20have%20any%20legal%20loopholes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20the%20Kumar%20Commission%20report%20had%20also%20classified%20OBC%20castes%20into%20three%20groups%20on%20just%20the%20political%20representation%20they%20had%20got%20under%20the%20previous%20two%20governments%20headed%20by%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20and%20Mayawati%20respectively.%20Castes%20like%20the%20Yadavs%2C%20Kurmis%2C%20Lodhs%2C%20Moraos%2C%20Jats%2C%20Telis%20and%20Gurjars%20got%20the%20most%20political%20representation.%20Behind%20them%20were%20Binds%2C%20Malis%2C%20Kumhars%2C%20Bhars%2C%20Mallahs%2C%20Noniya%20Chauhans%20and%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECastes%20such%20as%20the%20Sonars%2C%20Lohars%2C%20Arakhvanshis%2C%20Giris%20and%20Baris%20got%20zero%20political%20representation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20draws%20near%2C%20one%20wonders%20if%20the%20BJP%2C%20which%20is%20being%20challenged%20by%20the%20PDA%20(%3Cem%3Epichda%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Dalit%2C%20%3Cem%3Ealpsankhyak%3C%2Fem%3E)%20narrative%20of%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20in%20UP%2C%20would%20take%20the%20risk%20of%20dividing%20the%20OBC%20quota%20while%20opposing%20a%20caste%20census.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20heard%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fother-states%2Fbjp-plans-obc-mahakumbh-in-up-with-eye-on-2024-general-election%2Farticle67303887.ece%5C%22%3Ethe%20BJP%20plans%20to%20hold%20an%20%E2%80%98OBC%20%3Cem%3EMahakumbh%E2%80%99%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0of%20leaders%20of%20the%20backward%20castes%20in%20November%20in%20Prayagraj%20to%20reach%20out%20to%20the%20crucial%20voting%20bloc.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHow%20the%20BJP%20deals%20with%20the%20complicated%20and%20inter-linked%20questions%20of%20sub-categorisation%2C%20caste%20census%20and%20inclusion%20of%20certain%20OBC%20castes%20in%20the%20SC%20and%20ST%20lists%2C%20only%20time%20will%20tell.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694683509000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F02%2F01203851%2FYogi-Adityanath-PTI-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fjustice-kumar-commission-findings-remain-in-cold-storage-in-uttar-pradesh%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20commission%20similar%20to%20the%20one%20led%20by%20Justice%20Rohini%20submitted%20its%20findings%20on%20OBC%20sub-categorisation%20in%20UP%2C%20but%20its%20findings%20have%20remained%20in%20cold%20storage%20owing%20to%20risks%20it%20poses%20to%20the%20BJP%20with%20respect%20to%20its%20political%20narratives%20in%20the%20state.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fjustice-kumar-commission-findings-remain-in-cold-storage-in-uttar-pradesh%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Elon%20Musk%20had%20just%20%244%2C000%20when%20he%20moved%20to%20Canada%20and%20shared%20a%20room%20with%205%20other%20people%3A%20book%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222140%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Black%20and%20white%20illustration%20of%20Elon%20Musk%20wearing%20a%20suit%20next%20to%20the%20X%20logo%20%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F650186a9992da60019eb422a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221422%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EElon%20Musk%20was%2017%20when%20he%20left%20South%20Africa.%3Cp%3EGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EElon%20Musk%20left%20South%20Africa%20in%201989%20with%20%244%2C000%20from%20his%20parents%2C%20per%20Walter%20Isaacson's%20biography.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMusk%20initially%20stayed%20in%20a%20youth%20hostel%2C%20sharing%20a%20room%20with%205%20other%20people%2C%20per%20the%20book.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20biography%20debunks%20suggestions%20that%20he%20left%20his%20homeland%C2%A0%20with%C2%A0%26quot%3Bpockets%20filled%20with%20emeralds%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EElon%20Musk%20had%20just%20%244%2C000%20to%20his%20name%20when%20he%20left%20South%20Africa%20at%20the%20age%20of%2017%20and%20moved%20to%20Canada%20to%20study%2C%20according%20to%20Walter%20Isaacson's%20biography.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20father%2C%20Errol%20Musk%2C%20%26quot%3Bgave%20him%20%242%2C000%20in%20traveler's%20checks%26quot%3B%20and%20his%20mother%2C%20Maye%20Musk%2C%20handed%20him%20%242%2C000.%C2%A0His%20mother%20was%20born%20in%20Canada%2C%20which%20meant%20he%20was%20able%20to%20obtain%20a%20Canadian%20passport.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIsaacson%20writes%20in%20the%20biography%2C%20released%20this%20week%2C%20that%20when%20Musk%20arrived%2C%20he%20shared%20a%20room%20with%20five%20other%20people%20at%20a%20youth%20hostel.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202018%2C%20Musk%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Felonmusk%2Fstatus%2F1005593651219582977%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Etweeted%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20he%20%26quot%3Barrived%20in%20North%20America%20at%2017%20w%20%242000%2C%20a%20backpack%20%26amp%3B%20a%20suitcase%20full%20of%20books.%26quot%3B%20He%20also%20claimed%20he'd%20paid%20his%20own%20way%20through%20college%20and%20dropped%20out%20of%20Stanford%20University%20with%20%26quot%3B%24110k%20in%20college%20debt.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20revelation%20follows%20speculation%20recounted%20in%20the%20book%20that%20he%20departed%20with%20%26quot%3Bpockets%20filled%20with%20emeralds%26quot%3B%20from%20a%20mine%20that%20his%20father%20supposedly%20owned.%20However%2C%20the%20biography%20also%20confirmed%20that%20Errol%20Musk%20did%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-father-errol-never-owned-emerald-mine-telling-truth-2023-9%3Fr%3DUS%26IR%3DT%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Enot%20actually%20own%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20mine.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIsaacson%20said%20Errol%20Musk%20had%20swapped%20a%20light%20plane%20he%20owned%20for%20some%20emeralds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EErrol%20Musk%20told%20Insider%20in%20an%20email%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20exchanged%20the%20Cessna%20421%20Golden%20Eagle%20for%20a%20share%20in%20the%20mine%20in%201985.%20As%20initial%20payment%20I%20received%20108%20quality%20cut%20emeralds.%20Thereafter%20I%20received%20rough%20emeralds.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20%26quot%3Bthe%20mine%20was%20registered%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20that%20%26quot%3Bno%20government%20office%20had%20paper%2C%20let%20alone%20a%20pencil%26quot%3B%20during%20the%201980s%20in%20Zambia.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EErrol%20Musk%20also%20claimed%20that%20the%20emerald%20business%20collapsed%20in%201990%20when%20Russia%20bought%20lab-grown%20artificial%20emeralds%2C%20which%20sent%20prices%20dropping%20by%2090%25.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20emerald%20business%20helped%20us%20through%20a%20very%20difficult%20time%20in%20South%20Africa%2C%20when%20the%20white%20government%20collapsed%20and%20black%20government%20took%20over%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BAll%20development%20collapsed%20with%20the%20white%20government.%20As%20a%20property%20developer%20that%20affected%20me%20a%20lot.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EElon%20Musk%20didn't%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv