ond%20has%20been%20traveling%20full%20time%20since%202012%20and%20sharing%20his%20adventures%20on%20social%20media.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAs%20a%20content%20creator%2C%20he%20earns%20between%20%241%2C000%20and%20%2410%2C000%20for%20posts%20working%20with%20brands%20like%20Google.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHis%20goal%20is%20to%20visit%20every%20country%20in%20the%20world%3B%20so%20far%2C%20he's%20been%20to%20159.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Tom%20Grond%2C%20a%20full-time%20traveler%20and%20content%20creator%20from%20Simpelveld%2C%20Netherlands.%20Insider%20has%20verified%20his%20income%20with%20documentation.%20The%20following%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20travel%20full%20time%2C%20and%20I've%20visited%20159%20countries%2C%20including%20Vatican%20City%2C%20Kosovo%2C%20and%20Taiwan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20four%20reasons%20I%20travel%20to%20a%20new%20country%3A%20I%20want%20to%20see%20it%2C%20I've%20been%20invited%20by%20a%20brand%2C%20I%20want%20to%20create%20content%20there%2C%20and%20I%20have%20a%20goal%20to%20visit%20every%20country%20in%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20went%20to%2062%20countries%20in%202022%2C%2025%20of%20them%20for%20the%20first%20time.%20I%20document%20my%20travels%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.traveltomtom.net%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eon%20my%20blog%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Ftraveltomtom%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Emy%20social%20media%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Through%20ad%20revenue%20and%20brand%20deals%2C%20I%20earn%20between%20%2415%2C000%20to%20%2420%2C000%20a%20month.%20Here's%20how%20I%20do%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EMy%20first%20overseas%20trip%20was%20to%20Aruba%20for%20vacation%20in%202006%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20went%20to%20Aruba%20in%202006%20and%20met%20a%20lot%20of%20different%20people%20from%20the%20Americas%2C%20and%20I%20discovered%20I%20was%20keen%20to%20learn%20about%20other%20cultures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20returning%20home%20to%20the%20Netherlands%2C%20I%20worked%20as%20a%20process%20analyst%20for%20the%20government's%20welfare%20department%20and%20saved%20up%20to%20backpack%20around%2023%20countries%20for%20all%20of%202008.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20my%20big%20backpacking%20trip%2C%20I%20went%20back%20home%20and%20returned%20to%20my%20job%2C%20which%20I%20liked.%20But%20traveling%20was%20my%20love.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20worked%20again%20until%20I%20saved%20up%20enough%20to%20quit%20my%20job%20in%202012%20with%20plans%20to%20travel%20by%20myself%20for%20four%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EInstagram%20started%20to%20take%20off%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%20which%20changed%20everything%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20worked%20temporary%20jobs%20in%20the%20places%20I%20visited%20to%20help%20support%20myself.%20When%20I%20was%20working%20as%20a%20dive%20guide%20in%20Ko%20Tao%2C%20Thailand%2C%20I%20started%20posting%20pictures%20of%20my%20work%20on%20Instagram%2C%20which%20had%20started%20getting%20popular.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20posts%20gained%20traction%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-get-best-instagram-engagement-captions-hashtags-posting-time-2021-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Elargely%20through%20hashtags%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Some%20of%20my%20posts%20also%20got%20reposted%20on%20bigger%20travel%20accounts%2C%20which%20helped%20me%20reach%20new%20followers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20following%20grew%2C%20and%20hotels%20around%20the%20world%20started%20to%20invite%20me%20to%20stay.%20At%20first%2C%20one%20in%20Bangkok%20asked%20me%20to%20come%20and%20take%20photos%2C%20and%20I%20didn't%20realize%20they%20were%20offering%20me%20free%20accommodation.%20I%20kept%20telling%20them%20I%20couldn't%20afford%20to%20stay%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20there%2C%20it%20snowballed%2C%20and%20I%20kept%20getting%20more%20and%20more%20invites.%20In%202017%2C%20I%20stayed%20in%20three%20luxury%20hotels%20in%20the%20Maldives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20changed%20my%20travels%20to%20accommodate%20the%20demand%20instead%20of%20going%20to%20places%20I%20wanted%20to%20see.%20After%20a%20while%2C%20I%20felt%20like%20I%20was%20a%20slave%20to%20this%20new%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20realized%20I%20needed%20to%20step%20up%20my%20game%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20World%20Tourism%20Forum%20in%20Istanbul%20in%20January%202017%2C%20there%20were%20people%20onstage%20who%20talked%20about%20making%20%2410%2C000%20a%20month%20%E2%80%94%20they%20knew%20who%20I%20was%20and%20had%20fewer%20followers%20than%20me.%20I%20knew%20I%20needed%20to%20start%20making%20money%2C%20as%20I%20was%20still%20paying%20for%20my%20own%20flights%20most%20of%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20started%20blogging%20in%20summer%202016%20and%20realized%20I%20could%20make%20good%20money%20through%20ad%20revenue.%20A%20year%20later%2C%20I%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fwhat-is-seo-search-engine-optimization%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Estarted%20getting%20ranked%20on%20Google%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20realized%20it%20was%20the%20future%20for%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20don't%20work%20for%20exposure%20anymore%20%E2%80%94%20clients%20have%20to%20pay%20for%20my%20time%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20I%20really%20like%20a%20destination%20and%20I'm%20interested%2C%20I'm%20happy%20to%20negotiate%20a%20deal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20a%20photo%20post%20on%20Instagram%2C%20I%20charge%20a%20minimum%20of%20%241%2C500.%20A%20reel%20starts%20at%20%242%2C000%2C%20and%20three%20Instagram%20stories%20(my%20minimum)%20is%20%241%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHalf%20of%20my%20income%20comes%20from%20influencer%20partnerships.%20I%20worked%20with%20Google%20on%20a%20Maps%20campaign%20and%20was%20paid%20%2410%2C000%20for%20one%