cted%20my%20visa%20applications%20when%20I%20first%20tried%20to%20go%20because%20I%20went%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Findia-pakistan-kashmir-nuclear-weapons-climate-cooling-2019-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ethe%20Indian-controlled%20side%20of%20Kashmir%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20had%20a%20stamp%20from%20there%20on%20my%20passport.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20I%20love%20about%20being%20a%20creator%20and%20influencer%20is%20changing%20perceptions%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20important%20to%20remember%20that%20going%20to%20a%20country%20doesn't%20mean%20you%20support%20a%20regime.%20When%20I%20go%20to%20the%20United%20States%2C%20no%20one%20asks%20me%20if%20I%20support%20Joe%20Biden%2C%20so%20when%20I%20go%20to%20Iran%2C%20don't%20think%20that%20means%20I%20support%20its%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20lot%20of%20people%20were%20really%20blown%20away%20by%20my%20recent%20trip%20to%20Algeria.%20Many%20thought%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-most-conservative-countries-in-the-world-2017-1%2325-sri-lanka-sri-lanka-came-108th-in-the-environmental-performance-index-out-of-180-countries-surveyed-and-performed-badly-on-personal-rights-tolerance-and-access-to-information-in-the-social-progress-index-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAlgerian%20women%20needed%20to%20be%20super%20conservative%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20that's%20not%20always%20true.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20man%20takes%20a%20selfie%20in%20Algeria%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6501c68b992da60019eb6ea5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221701%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGrond%20in%20Algeria.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Tom%20Grond%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20followers%20also%20thought%20my%20photos%20from%20the%20mountains%20in%20Pakistan%20looked%20like%20Switzerland.%20It%20was%20cool%20to%20be%20able%20to%20showcase%20the%20beauty%20and%20the%20people%20of%20a%20country%20that%20many%20aren't%20familiar%20with.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222316%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22man%20takes%20a%20selfie%20in%20front%20of%20a%20place%20of%20religious%20worship%20in%20Pakistan%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6501c6161afe8f0019e98420%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223088%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGrond%20in%20Pakistan.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Tom%20Grond.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3EI%20love%20traveling%2C%20but%20I%20don't%20like%20to%20live%20as%20a%20tourist%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%204%2C000%20days%20of%20traveling%2C%20I%20don't%20need%20to%20see%20every%20attraction.%20It's%20exhausting%20%E2%80%94%20I%20just%20want%20to%20hang%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20learned%20to%20live%20in%20the%20moment%20and%20not%20miss%20things%20about%20the%20Netherlands%2C%20other%20than%20my%20friends%20and%20family%20sometimes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20the%20future%2C%20slower%20travel%20is%20something%20that%20I'm%20looking%20forward%20to.%20One%20day%20I'll%20settle%20down%2C%20but%20not%20in%20the%20next%20year%20at%20least.%20I%20get%20offered%20so%20many%20great%20opportunities.%20How%20can%20I%20say%20no%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-travel-full-time-make-money-social-media-2023-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694683261000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6501c7cd992da60019eb6fda%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-travel-full-time-make-money-social-media-2023-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Tom%20Grond%20started%20traveling%20full%20time%20in%202012%20and%20hasn't%20stopped.%20He's%20visited%20159%20countries%20and%20earns%20up%20to%20%2410%2C000%20a%20post%20working%20with%20brands%20like%20Google.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Elle%20Hardy)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-travel-full-time-make-money-social-media-2023-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Buyer%20beware%3A%20All%20those%20hidden%20fees%20you%20pay%20online%20are%20getting%20even%20more%20hidden%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20group%20of%20ninjas%20stealthily%20add%20extra%20zeros%20to%20a%20price%20tag%2C%20unbeknownst%20to%20a%20mesmerized%20shopper%20who%20thinks%20she's%20getting%20a%20good%20deal%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65021434992da60019ebcc9b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECompanies%20have%20for%20years%20added%20hidden%20fees%20onto%20every%20online%20purchase%20we%20make%20%E2%80%94%20but%20now%20these%20nefarious%20fees%20are%20getting%20even%20harder%20for%20customers%20to%20see.%3Cp%3ENicole%20Zaridze%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20I%20wanted%20to%20do%20was%20attend%20a%20concert.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20ready%20to%20pay%20my%20hard-earned%20money%20to%20see%20one%20of%20my%20favorite%20bands%20perform%20at%20New%20York%20City's%20Madison%20Square%20Garden.%20Ticket%20buying%20is%20simple%20enough%20in%20theory%20%E2%80%94%20but%20as%20I%20went%20in%20pursuit%20of%20the%20tickets%20a%20few%20months%20ago%2C%20I%20was%20prepared%20for%20a%20fee%20shock.%20For%20years%2C%20the%20initial%20price%20of%20tickets%20has%20been%20a%20tease%20%E2%80%94%20after%20totals%20are%20adding%20up%20during%20checkout%2C%20the%20final%20price%20is%20often%20an%20unpleasant%20surprise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20making%20my%20way%20to%20the%20front%20of%20the%20dreaded%20virtual%20ticket%20queue%2C%20I%20scored%20three%20tickets.%20But%20when%20I%20got%20to%20the%20checkout%2C%20something%20shocking%20happened%3A%20There%20were%20no%20pricey%20add-ons%20%E2%80%94%20no%20service%20fee%2C%20no%20processing%20fee%2C%20no%20convenience%20fee.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHad%20something%20gone%20wrong%3F%20Had%20I%20gotten%20away%20with%20purchasing%20tickets%20at%20face%20value%3F%20As%20my%20initial%20fervor%20subsided%2C%20I%20had%20a%20second%20realization%3A%20Those%20tickets%20weren't%20cheap!%20Even%20compared%20with%20previous%20events%20at%20MSG%20%E2%80%94%20including%20a%20concert%20by%20this%20same%20band%20%E2%80%94%20the%20tickets%20felt%20much%20more%20expensive.%20But%20the%20total%20cost%20was%20the%20same%20as%20previous%20tickets%20I'd%20gotten.%20Instead%20of%20being%20tacked%20on%20at%20checkout%2C%20the%20fees%20I%20had%20been%20dreading%20were%20baked%20into%20the%20up-front%20price.%20The%20company%20still%20got%20their%20fees%2C%20but%20my%20user%20experience%20was%20different.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEvery%20time%20we%20log%20on%20to%20shop%2C%20buy%20a%20new%20cable%20plan%2C%20or%20book%20that%20long-awaited%20vacation%2C%20companies%20have%20been%20playing%20psychological%20tricks%20to%20lure%20us%20into%20paying%20more%20than%20anticipated.%20And%20these%20hidden%20fees%20have%20spread%20from%20big-ticket%20splurges%20to%20nearly%20every%20type%20of%20online%20transaction%2C%20Neale%20Mahoney%2C%20a%20professor%20of%20economics%20at%20Stanford%20University%20who%20just%20spent%20a%20year%20on%20the%20White%20House's%20National%20Economic%20Council%2C%20told%20me.%20Now%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bthere%20are%20so%20many%20opportunities%20for%20people%20to%20add%20fees%26quot%3B%20directly%20into%20your%20shopping%20cart.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20combination%20of%20spreading%20of%20worse%20practices%20and%20the%20internet%2C%20which%20has%20turbocharged%20all%20of%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20rise%20of%20tacked-on%20fees%20has%20continued%20unabated%20for%20years%2C%20growing%20consumer%20backlash%20and%20President%20Joe%20Biden's%20recent%20initiative%20to%20eliminate%20hidden%20junk%20fees%20have%20pushed%20more%20companies%20to%20shift%20to%20transparent%2C%20all-in%20pricing.%20But%20this%20seemingly%20generous%20act%20is%20anything%20but.%20Companies%20are%20just%20baking%20all%20those%20fees%20into%20the%20total%20price%20%E2%80%94%20making%20the%20hidden%20fees%20even%20more%20hidden.%20That%20%2420%20booking%20fee%20and%20the%20%247%20handling%20fee%20are%20still%20there%2C%20just%20shrouded%20in%20an%20extra%20layer%20of%20mystery.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20shift%20may%20seem%20insidious%2C%20but%20experts%20told%20me%20there's%20hope%20for%20a%20better%2C%20free-fee%20future%3A%20If%20every%20company%20adopts%20up-front%20pricing%2C%20consumers%20can%20begin%20to%20understand%20the%20true%20cost%20of%20things%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0and%20make%20more%20informed%20decisions%20that%20force%20companies%20to%20compete%20on%20price.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20good%20evidence%20that%20when%20you%20require%20firms%20to%20price%20in%20an%20all-in%2C%20up-front%20manner%2C%20that%20it%20makes%20markets%20more%20competitive.%20It's%20easier%20for%20consumers%20to%20comparison%20shop%2C%26quot%3B%20Mahoney%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat%20means%20that%20market%20forces%20are%20stronger%2C%20and%20that%20pushes%20down%20the%20total%20price%20that%20consumers%20are%20paying.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225546%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20woman%20with%20a%20sign%20asks%20for%20a%20ticket%20before%20the%20concert%20of%20Bob%20Dylan%2C%20at%20the%20Alfonso%20XIII%20Botanical%20Garden%20of%20the%20Complutense%20University%20of%20Madrid%2C%20on%20June%207%2C%202023%2C%20in%20Madrid%2C%20Spain.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6501c63f1afe8f0019e98462%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224160%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EShowing%20up%20in-person%20and%20asking%20for%20tickets%20is%20one%20way%20to%20avoid%20fees.%3Cp%3EMarcos%20Villaoslada%2FEuropa%20Press%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3EHow%20the%20internet%20became%20fee%20city%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%2020%20years%2C%20the%20internet%20has%20revolutionized%20how%20we%20buy%20things.%20Flights%2C%20concert%20tickets%2C%20pizzas%2C%20and%20even%20toilet%20paper%20are%20just%20a%20click%20away.%20The%20ease%20of%20use%20made%20the%20early%20web%20a%20buyers'%20mecca%3A%20You%20could%20see%20how%20much%20it%20would%20cost%20to%20fly%20on%20one%20airline%20versus%20another%20or%20compare%20the%20price%20of%20PC%20equipment%20on%20different%20sites.%20Sara%20Fisher%20Ellison%2C%20a%20senior%20lecturer%20at%20MIT%20who%20since%202004%20has%20been%20researching%20pricing%20on%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdeliverypdf.ssrn.com%2Fdelivery.php%3FID%3D375091000096115106064124066074066124060087060080003065108005066109065100104072080073057037122017121015000007068070001088099107033086048020108115004017091094005010046040105017024065076095111015087122099073117093073025116024072011071121005002093124%26EXT%3Dpdf%26INDEX%3DTRUE%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20internet%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20told%20me%20that%20for%20a%20while%2C%20this%20transparency%20was%20good%20for%20price-conscious%20consumers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20have%20been%20times%20when%20the%20consumers%20did%20have%20an%20upper%20hand%20and%20were%20able%20to%20perform%20these%20price%20searches%20and%20comparisons%20in%20a%20pretty%20effective%20and%20efficient%20way%20online%2C%26quot%3B%20Ellison%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20that%20golden%20era%20of%20price%20search%20was%20short-lived%20as%20companies%20got%20more%20sophisticated.%20As%20sellers%20got%20used%20to%20the%20internet%2C%20they%20started%20to%20employ%20%26quot%3Bobfuscation%2C%26quot%3B%20as%20Ellison%20called%20it%20%E2%80%94%20methods%20of%20pricing%20jiujitsu%20that%20hid%20the%20true%20cost%20to%20eke%20out%20more%20profits.%20Instead%20of%20your%20airline%20ticket%20including%20baggage%2C%20food%20and%20beverages%2C%20and%20a%20%26quot%3Breasonable%20procedure%20to%20board%20the%20plane%2C%26quot%3B%20Ellison%20said%2C%20all%20those%20have%20become%20unbundled.%20The%20price%20customers%20now%20use%20to%20compare%20across%20airlines%20is%20simply%20a%20base%20price%20%E2%80%94%20but%20the%20variable%20cost%20of%20add-ons%2C%20such%20as%20priority%20boarding%20and%20checked%20luggage%2C%20make%20it%20nearly%20impossible%20to%20tell%20which%20airline%20will%20actually%20end%20up%20costing%20you%20more.%20Obfuscation%20has%20cost%20consumers%20the%20upper%20hand%3A%20Companies%20can%20reel%20in%20customers%20with%20an%20artificially%20deflated%20price%20before%20jacking%20the%20cost%20up%20via%20fees%20%E2%80%94%20consumers%20spent%20over%20%245.2%20billion%20on%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bts.gov%2Fnewsroom%2Fbaggage-fees-airline-2021%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebaggage%20fees%20in%202018%20alone%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20also%20lowers%20the%20overhead%20for%20many%20sellers%3A%20Instead%20of%20having%20to%20hire%20an%20army%20of%20Harold%20Hill-like%20master%20salespeople%20to%20upsell%20you%2C%20firms%20could%20just%20hide%20those%20premium%20costs%20on%20the%20checkout%20page.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20suspected%20that%20firms%20would%20be%20really%20taking%20advantage%20of%20the%20fact%20that%20obfuscation%20was%20much%20easier%20and%20cheaper%20for%20them%20to%20implement%2C%26quot%3B%20Ellison%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20that%20seems%20to%20have%20very%20much%20been%20the%20case.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EYour%20brain%20vs.%20your%20wallet%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20may%20be%20thinking%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20a%20savvy%20consumer.%20I%20always%20make%20sure%20I'm%20getting%20the%20best%20deal%20possible.%26quot%3B%20Unfortunately%2C%20research%20has%20found%20that%20the%20obfuscation%20strategy%20can%20make%20it%20hard%20to%20even%20realize%20when%20you've%20been%20suckered.%20Vicki%20Morwitz%2C%20a%20professor%20at%20Columbia%20Business%20School%20who%20studies%20the%20psychology%20of%20how%20consumers%20interpret%20prices%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbusiness.columbia.edu%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles-efs%2Fpubfiles%2F26100%2FSantana%2520Dallas%2520Morwitz%2520Marketing%2520Science%2520forthcoming.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eidentified%20two%20types%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20pricing%20tricks.%20One%20type%2C%20called%20partition%20pricing%2C%20is%20when%20a%20product's%20price%20is%20divided%20into%20two%20or%20more%20parts%3B%20she%20gave%20me%20the%20example%20of%20a%20cruise%2C%20where%20the%20cruise%20ticket%20is%20a%20base%20price%20and%20the%20mandatory%20port%20charge%20is%20labeled%20as%20a%20surcharge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20we%2C%20as%20consumers%2C%20see%20partition%20prices%2C%20our%20brain%20tends%20to%20focus%20on%20the%20base%20price%2C%26quot%3B%20Morwitz%20told%20me.%20That%20bigger%2C%20more-salient%20number%20typically%20represents%20to%20us%20the%20cost%20of%20the%20item%20we%20want%20to%20buy.%20%26quot%3BWe%20tend%20not%20to%20pay%20sufficient%20attention%20to%20those%20surcharges%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%20That%20means%20we%20underestimate%20what%20a%20partition-price%20item%20costs%20%E2%80%94%20so%20we're%20more%20likely%20to%20make%20that%20purchase.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%3E%3Cq%3EEven%20when%20we%20know%20there%20are%20those%20surcharges%2C%20we%20don't%20pay%20attention%20to%20them%20because%20we%20kind%20of%20think%20of%20them%20as%20the%20cost%20of%20doing%20business.%3C%2Fq%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20is%20called%20drip%20pricing.%20That's%20when%20charges%20that%20will%20get%20added%20to%20your%20total%20aren't%20apparent%20up%20front%20but%20are%20dripped%20throughout%20the%20process%20of%20purchasing.%20Think%20of%20the%20convenience%20fees%20that%20rack%20up%20as%20you%20buy%20a%20concert%20ticket%2C%20for%20instance.%20On%20the%20first%20page%2C%20you%20see%20the%20ticket%20price.%20On%20the%20next%20one%2C%20once%20you%20select%20your%20ticket%2C%20you%20see%20the%20booking%20fee.%20Finally%2C%20when%20it's%20time%20to%20whip%20out%20your%20credit%20card%2C%20you%20see%20a%20facility%20or%20venue%20fee.%20Drip%20pricing%20relies%20on%20a%20timed%20aspect%3A%20You%20invest%20a%20certain%20amount%20of%20time%20in%20each%20step%20of%20the%20purchase%2C%20with%20fees%20slowly%20revealed%20throughout%20that%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20may%20realize%20at%20the%20end%3A%20'This%20ticket's%20a%20lot%20more%20expensive%20than%20I%20thought%20%E2%80%94%20and%20maybe%20there's%20another%20option%20where%20I%20could%20get%20the%20ticket%20cheaper.'%20But%20consumers%20tend%20not%20to%20do%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Morwitz%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey%20tend%20to%20follow%20through%20on%20the%20purchase%20even%20when%20it's%20more%20expensive%20than%20they%20thought%20it%20was.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20drip%20pricing%2C%20consumers'%20brains%20trick%20them%20again%3A%20Morwitz's%20research%20has%20found%20that%20when%20you%20make%20it%20to%20the%20final%20checkout%20process%20and%20realize%20that%20your%20tickets%20are%20more%20expensive%20than%20you%20saw%20initially%2C%20you've%20already%20mentally%20committed%20to%20the%20experience.%20It%20can%20be%20hard%20to%20pull%20the%20plug%20so%20late%20in%20the%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMaybe%20because%20of%20'FOMO%2C'%20they%20can%20already%20visualize%20themselves%20at%20a%20concert%2C%26quot%3B%20Mahoney%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey%20already%20can%20visualize%20themselves%20eating%20their%20dinner.%20They%20won't%20go%20searching%20for%20a%20cheaper%20option.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20exacerbated%20by%20websites%20presenting%20big%2C%20flashing%20countdown%20clocks%20or%20telling%20you%20that%20there's%20just%20a%20few%20tickets%20left%20at%20that%20price.%20We%20assume%20the%20time%20we've%20invested%20in%20purchasing%20the%20tickets%20is%20a%20sunk%20cost%20and%20click%20buy%20%E2%80%94%20spending%20more%20than%20we%20intended%20and%20overestimating%20the%20cost%20of%20restarting%20our%20search.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EHow%20to%20combat%20it%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20has%20been%20more%20drip%20and%20partition%20pricing%20over%20time%2C%20Morwitz%20said%2C%20largely%20thanks%20to%20internet%20shopping.%20The%20fee-laden%20model%20has%20become%20a%20part%20of%20online%20life%20and%20embedded%20itself%20into%20the%20psyche%20of%20many%20shoppers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20when%20we%20know%20there%20are%20those%20surcharges%2C%20we%20don't%20pay%20attention%20to%20them%20because%20we%20kind%20of%20think%20of%20them%20as%20the%20cost%20of%20doing%20business%2C%26quot%3B%20Morwitz%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20like%2C%20'Oh%2C%20well%20all%20the%20competitors%20must%20have%20them.%20They%20must%20be%20all%20more%20or%20less%20the%20same.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20consumers%20might%20say%20they%20want%20clearer%2C%20fee-free%20pricing%20%E2%80%94%2051%25%20of%20consumers%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.documentcloud.org%2Fdocuments%2F23875007-yougov-airline-poll%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esurveyed%20by%20YouGov%20in%20July%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20it%20was%20important%20that%20they%20do%20not%20pay%20more%20than%20the%20price%20initially%20shown%20for%20concerts%20%E2%80%94%20they've%20rejected%20it%C2%A0in%20practice.%20Just%20look%20at%20the%20ticket-resale%20platform%20StubHub.%20The%20company%20moved%20to%20an%20%26quot%3Ball-in%20pricing%26quot%3B%20model%20in%202014%2C%20meaning%20consumers%20would%20see%20how%20much%20their%20ticket%20cost%20up%20front.%20But%20instead%20of%20consumers%20flocking%20to%20single-cost%20tickets%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Farticles%2Fstubhub-gets-out-of-all-in-pricing-1441065436%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethey%20started%20to%20ditch%20the%20platform%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Research%20on%20StubHub's%20pricing%20experiments%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nber.org%2Fsystem%2Ffiles%2Fworking_papers%2Fw25186%2Fw25186.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elater%20found%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20concealing%20those%20fees%20through%20drip%20or%20partition%20pricing%20increased%20revenue%20by%2020%25%20and%20that%20%26quot%3Bexperienced%20users%26quot%3B%20of%20StubHub%20still%20spent%20more%20when%20the%20fee%20was%20hidden.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUnfortunately%2C%20the%20broader%20industry%20did%20not%20adopt%20all-in%20pricing%2C%20leaving%20buyers%20confused%20and%20StubHub%20at%20a%20significant%20competitive%20disadvantage%2C%26quot%3B%20Laura%20Dooley%2C%20StubHub's%20head%20of%20global%20government%20relations%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whitehouse.gov%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2FStubhub-Laura-Dooley-remarks.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etestified%20at%20a%20White%20House%20panel%20in%20March%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BStubHub's%20all-in%20pricing%20confused%20buyers%20who%20assumed%20our%20prices%20were%20exclusive%20of%20fees%20and%20therefore%20more%20expensive%20relative%20to%20our%20competitors.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20even%20if%20people%20rewire%20their%20brains%20and%20become%20staunch%20anti-fee%20activists%2C%20the%20movement%20will%20need%20government%20action%20to%20support%20the%20fight.%20Without%20an%20industry%20overhaul%2C%20the%20companies%20that%20choose%20to%20do%20all-in%20pricing%20will%20go%20the%20way%20of%20StubHub%3A%20Our%20fee-addled%20brains%20will%20think%20they're%20more%20expensive%20and%20tell%20us%20to%20go%20purchase%20elsewhere.%20The%20practice%20needs%20to%20be%20widespread%20for%20us%20to%20actually%20be%20able%20to%20compare%20prices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%3E%3Cq%3EI%20have%20never%20seen%20a%20good%20justification%20of%20what%20I'd%20call%20mandatory%20hidden%20fees.%3C%2Fq%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Europe%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20all-in%20pricing%20is%20an%20obligation.%20That%20means%20that%20prices%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feuropa.eu%2Fyoureurope%2Fcitizens%2Fconsumers%2Fshopping%2Fpricing-payments%2Findex_en.htm%23shortcut-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethings%20such%20as%20airline%20and%20train%20tickets%20have%20to%20include%20all%20costs%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20including%20fees%20and%20taxes%20%E2%80%94%20when%20you%20start%20trying%20to%20book%3B%20that's%20explicitly%20meant%20for%20consumers%20to%20be%20able%20to%20compare%20prices.%20The%20Canadian%20government%20is%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cbc.ca%2Fnews%2Fbusiness%2Fjunk-fees-us-canada-crackdown-1.6836993%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ealso%20looking%20to%20pare%20down%20hidden%20fees%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20White%20House%20has%20begun%20to%20take%20on%20this%20fight%20in%20the%20US%2C%20launching%20several%20initiatives%20to%20help%20eliminate%20junk%20fees%20and%20raise%20awareness%20of%20hidden%20costs.%20The%20White%20House's%20hope%20is%20that%20a%20push%20to%20get%20firms%20including%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fticketmaster-live-nation-seatgeek-remove-hidden-ticket-fees-checkout-2023-6%5C%22%3ETicketmaster%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbiden-new-plan-to-save-renters-from-bogus-apartment-fees-2023-7%5C%22%3EZillow%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20have%20all-in%20pricing%20will%20not%20only%20aid%20consumer%20transparency%20but%20also%20increase%20competition%20to%20offer%20the%20lowest%20cost%20to%20customers.%20Michael%20Negron%2C%20the%20special%20assistant%20to%20the%20president%20for%20economic%20policy%20at%20the%20National%20Economic%20Council%2C%20told%20me%20that%20while%20the%20White%20House's%20campaign%20against%20fees%20would%20%26quot%3Bstart%20with%20the%20consumers%20%E2%80%94%20you%20raise%20awareness%2C%20you%20use%20the%20bully%20pulpit%2C%20hopefully%20push%20for%20positive%20private-sector%20action%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20eventually%20there%20would%20need%20to%20be%20something%20%26quot%3Bdone%20via%20either%20a%20regulatory%20tool%20or%20a%20new%20law.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ETrue%20costs%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMuch%20like%20how%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-prices-inflation-soaring-corporate-greed-profits-margins-wages-jobs-2023-4%5C%22%3Ecompanies%20hid%20price%20hikes%20behind%20the%20guise%20of%20inflation%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20fees%20are%20hiding%20costs%20consumers%20can't%20fully%20process.%20It's%20what%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.npr.org%2F2023%2F07%2F27%2F1189665392%2Ffees-inflation-white-house-service-hidden%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENPR%20called%3C%2Fa%3E%20%26quot%3Bfee-flation.%26quot%3B%20Some%20fees%20may%20be%20necessary%2C%20but%20others%2C%20as%20Mahoney%20told%20me%2C%20are%20made%20up%20and%20designed%20to%20look%20like%20they're%20government-imposed%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20when%20they're%20not.%20Those%20are%20the%20fees%20that%20could%20be%20trickier%20to%20regulate%20as%20they%20get%20folded%20into%20pricing%20%E2%80%94%20the%20made-up%20fees%20will%20get%20more%20hidden.%20Thankfully%2C%20they're%20also%20the%20kind%20of%20%26quot%3Bunnecessary%2C%20unavoidable%2C%20or%20surprise%20charges%20that%20inflate%20costs%20while%20adding%20little%20to%20no%20value%26quot%3B%20that%20have%20drawn%20the%20attention%20of%20the%20Federal%20Trade%20Commission.%20But%20in%20lieu%20of%20more%20government%20action%2C%20the%20move%20to%20up-front%20prices%20means%20that%20at%20least%20now%20we%20can%20fully%20see%20how%20much%20things%20cost.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225298%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22.%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20delivers%20remarks%20on%20protecting%20consumers%20from%20hidden%20junk%20fees%20as%20(L-R)%20CEO%20of%20SeatGeek%20Jack%20Groetzinger%2C%20Co-CEO%20of%20TickPick%20Brett%20Goldberg%2C%20CEO%20of%20DICE%20Phil%20Hutcheon%2C%20CEO%20of%20xBk%20Tobi%20Parks%2C%20Director%20of%20the%20National%20Economic%20Council%20Lael%20Brainard%2C%20CFO%20of%20Airbnb%20Dave%20Stephenson%2C%20and%20President%20of%20Live%20Nation%20Venues%20Tom%20See%20listen%20during%20an%20event%20at%20the%20South%20Court%20Auditorium%20at%20Eisenhower%20Executive%20Office%20Building%20on%20June%2015%2C%202023%20in%20Washington%2C%20DC.%20P%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6501c5641afe8f0019e98334%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223974%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPresident%20Joe%20Biden%20has%20successfully%20gotten%20some%20companies%20to%20commit%20to%20all-in%20pricing.%3Cp%3EAlex%20Wong%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELooking%20back%20at%20my%20concert%20ticket%2C%20I%20realized%20how%20much%20my%20music%20habits%20were%20costing%20me.%20Experts%20hope%20that%20the%20budgeting%20reckoning%20I%20experienced%20when%20faced%20with%20the%20true%20cost%20of%20my%20decisions%20can%20be%20replicated%20among%20other%20consumers.%20Eventually%2C%20people's%20self-realization%20and%20drive%20to%20comparison%20shop%20could%20end%20up%20pushing%20prices%20down.%20It%20could%20also%20help%20firms%20that%20are%20trying%20not%20to%20trick%20their%20customers%2C%20since%20the%20hidden-fees%20model%20penalizes%20companies%20who%20price%20accurately.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20of%20the%20problems%20with%20the%20use%20of%20partitioning%20in%20pricing%20is%20it%20makes%20it%20very%20difficult%20for%20an%20honest%20business%20who%20wants%20to%20do%20the%20right%20thing%20to%20do%20so%20in%20the%20face%20of%20competitors%20who%20are%20using%20these%20practices%2C%26quot%3B%20Morwitz%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20constant%20battle%20between%20companies%20and%20customers%20has%20led%20to%20some%20creative%20solutions%20to%20the%20fee%20problem.%20In%20April%2C%20the%20artist%20Maggie%20Rogers%20invited%20her%20fans%20to%20come%20buy%20concert%20tickets%20in%20person%20at%20the%20box%20office%2C%20where%20they%20wouldn't%20be%20charged%20extra%20fees%2C%20saying%20that%20%26quot%3Bthere's%20been%20a%20lot%20of%20conversation%20about%20how%20intense%20ticketing%20fees%20are%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20she'd%20been%20thinking%20about%20ways%20to%20provide%20alternatives%20to%20fans.%20Others%20are%20also%20fighting%20back.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20walk%20up%20to%20any%20of%20our%20box%20offices%2C%20you%20could%20buy%20a%20ticket%20to%20any%20of%20our%20venues%20and%20not%20be%20charged%20a%20fee%2C%26quot%3B%20Audrey%20Fix%20Schaefer%2C%20the%20director%20of%20communications%20for%20I.M.P.%2C%20an%20independent%20promoter%20in%20Washington%2C%20DC%2C%20that%20owns%20the%209%3A30%20Club%20and%20the%20vice%20president%20of%20the%20board%20at%20the%20National%20Independent%20Venue%20Association%2C%20told%20me.%20In%20fact%2C%20some%20of%20her%20venues%20have%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gwhatchet.com%2F2019%2F09%2F09%2F930-club-to-bring-mobile-box-office-truck-to-campus%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eroving%20box%20offices%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20drive%20to%20different%20parts%20of%20the%20city%20or%20state%20to%20help%20music%20lovers%20buy%20tickets%20sans%20fees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20these%20one-off%20solutions%20won't%20kill%20the%20scourge%20of%20hidden%20fees%20overnight%20and%20are%20generally%20available%20only%20to%20customers%20with%20the%20time%2C%20ability%2C%20and%20savviness%20to%20circumvent%20an%20extra%20charge.%20But%20in%20the%20end%2C%20fees%20aren't%20a%20force%20of%20nature%2C%20and%20a%20concerted%20effort%20on%20the%20part%20of%20regular%20consumers%20and%20policymakers%20could%20move%20us%20to%20a%20better%2C%20more-transparent%20future.%20After%20all%2C%20Mahoney%20told%20me%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20never%20seen%20a%20good%20justification%20of%20what%20I'd%20call%20mandatory%20hidden%20fees.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20data-mrf-link%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fauthor%2Fjuliana-kaplan%5C%22%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-uri%3D%5C%222f034fc248d03796697470ab601b9810%5C%22%20data-analytics-post-depth%3D%5C%22100%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fauthor%2Fjuliana-kaplan%5C%22%20data-analytics-product-module%3D%5C%22body_link%5C%22%3EJuliana%20Kaplan%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0is%20a%20senior%20labor%20and%20inequality%20reporter%20on%20Insider's%20economy%20team.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fonline-shopping-hidden-junk-fees-getting-worse-sneakier-prices-tickets-2023-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694683261000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F650215ab992da60019ebce9b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fonline-shopping-hidden-junk-fees-getting-worse-sneakier-prices-tickets-2023-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22From%20concert%20and%20plane%20tickets%20to%20hotel%20rooms%20and%20vacation%20rentals%2C%20companies%20are%20making%20their%20hidden%20fees%20even%20harder%20for%20customers%20to%20see.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Juliana%20Kaplan)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fonline-shopping-hidden-junk-fees-getting-worse-sneakier-prices-tickets-2023-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22INDIA%20Wants%20To%20Finish%20Sanatana%2C%20Push%20Country%20Back%20Into%20Slavery%3A%20PM%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20scathing%20attack%20on%20the%20opposition%20INDIA%20alliance%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20has%20said%20that%20it%20wants%20to%20finish%20Sanatana%20Dharma%20and%20push%20the%20country%20back%20into%20slavery%20for%201%2C000%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20statement%2C%20which%20was%20made%20by%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20at%20a%20rally%20in%20poll-bound%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20on%20Thursday%2C%20is%20his%20first%20public%20reaction%20to%20the%20controversy%20over%20DMK%20leader%20Udhayanidhi%20Stalin's%20remarks%20on%20Sanatana%20Dharma.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20held%20a%20meeting%20in%20Mumbai%20recently%2C%20and%20I%20think%20they%20decided%20the%20policy%20and%20strategy%20of%20how%20to%20run%20the%20'ghamandiya'%20alliance%20there.%20They%20have%20also%20decided%20on%20a%20hidden%20agenda.%20The%20strategy%20is%20to%20attack%20the%20culture%20of%20India.%20They%20have%20decided%20to%20attack%20the%20faith%20of%20Indians%20and%20finish%20the%20thoughts%2C%20values%20and%20traditions%20that%20have%20united%20the%20country%20for%20thousands%20of%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20PM%20said%20in%20Hindi.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDrawing%20a%20link%20between%20India's%20heroes%20and%20the%20Sanatana%20culture%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20'ghamandiya'%20alliance%20has%20resolved%20to%20finish%20the%20Sanatana%20culture%20and%20traditions%20that%20inspired%20Devi%20Ahilyabai%20Holkar.%20It%20was%20the%20strength%20of%20Sanatana%20that%20the%20Rani%20of%20Jhansi%2C%20Lakshmibai%2C%20could%20challenge%20the%20British%20and%20say%20that%20she%20would%20not%20give%20up%20her%20Jhansi.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20said%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20considered%20Sanatana%20Dharma%20to%20be%20essential%20to%20his%20life.%20%26quot%3BHe%20was%20inspired%20by%20Lord%20Ram%20all%20his%20life.%20His%20last%20words%20were%20'hey%20Ram'%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%20asserted%20that%20Swami%20Vivekanand%20and%20Lokmanya%20Tilak%20were%20also%20inspired%20by%20Sanatana%20and%20it%20was%20this%20culture%20that%20moved%20freedom%20fighters%20who%20were%20hanged%20by%20the%20British%