%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20cute%20dwelling%20was%20constructed%20in%20late%20July%20over%2044%20hours%2C%20the%20company's%20CTO%20said.%20It%20was%20nicknamed%20%26quot%3BFujitsubo%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20translates%20to%20%26quot%3Bbarnacle.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EFujitsubo%20was%20designed%20to%20accommodate%20a%20couple.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222300%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Two%20people%20on%20the%20walls%20of%20an%20incomplete%20Serendix%2050%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6501e682992da60019eb980a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221150%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3Eserendix%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EInside%2C%20the%20single-story%20527-square-foot%20home%20has%20one%20bedroom%2C%20bathroom%2C%20and%20living%20room%20with%20a%20kitchen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ELike%20most%20homes%20built%20using%20the%20tech%2C%20the%20walls%20were%203D-printed.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222300%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Someone%20standing%20inside%20an%20incomplete%20Serendix%2050%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6501e67d992da60019eb97f9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221725%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3Eserendix%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20wood%20roof%20was%20then%20built%20using%20a%20CNC%20(computer%20numerical%20control)%20cutter.%20Because%20almost%20all%20of%20the%20primary%20components%20of%20the%20home%20were%20built%20using%20automated%20tech%2C%20the%20startup%20was%20able%20to%20save%20both%20time%20and%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ETo%20print%20the%20walls%2C%20Serendix%20turned%20to%20Winsun%20and%20Twente%20Additive%20Manufacturing's%20printers%2C%20Ogata%20said.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222300%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20incomplete%20Serendix%2050%20wall%20inside%20factory%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6501e681992da60019eb9807%3Fformat%3Djpeg%