rs%20and%20I'm%20always%20shocked%20when%20a%20new%20one%20comes%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20US%20government%20intercepts%20some%20counterfeit%20products%2C%20there%20are%20limitations.%20For%20one%20thing%2C%20many%20packages%20shipped%20through%20e-commerce%20sites%20are%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fshein-and-temu-skirt-import-tariffs-us-lawmakers-fast-fashion-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E%20small%2C%20low-value%20orders%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20More%20than%2090%25%20of%20all%20counterfeit%20seizures%20happen%20through%20international%20and%20express%20mail%2C%20according%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cbp.gov%2Ftrade%2Ffakegoodsrealdangers%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EUS%20Customs%20and%20Border%20Protection%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225074%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22close%20up%20of%20a%20woman%20tapping%20the%20screen%20of%20her%20phone%20shopping%20for%20handbags%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64ff7e44a39a1b00190d7914%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223376%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOnline%20shopping%20has%20made%20it%20easier%20for%20counterfeiters%20to%20sell%20fake%20products.%3Cp%3EWang%20Zhao%2FGetty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20factor%20could%20be%20that%20for%20sellers%2C%20the%20return%20outweighs%20the%20cost.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20penalty%20for%20trafficking%20and%20counterfeits%20is%20about%20three%20to%20six%20months%20in%20federal%20prison%2C%26quot%3B%20Shapiro%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20the%20penalty%20is%20very%20low%20and%20the%20money%20is%20very%20good.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ussc.gov%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fpdf%2Ftraining%2Fprimers%2F2023_Primer_Intellectual_Property.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EUS%20Sentencing%20Commission%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20maximum%20sentence%20for%20selling%20counterfeit%20goods%20is%2010%20years%20in%20prison.%20In%202021%2C%20the%20average%20sentence%20for%20copyright%20and%20trademark%20infringement%20was%2010%20months%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ussc.gov%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fpdf%2Fresearch-and-publications%2Fquick-facts%2FCopyright_FY21.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ethe%20agency%20reported%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShapiro%20said%20a%20law-enforcement%20official%20once%20told%20him%20that%20selling%20counterfeit%20Nike%20sneakers%20can%20reap%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.occrp.org%2Fen%2Fdaily%2F6240-ngo-transnational-organized-crime-groups-make-us-2-2-trillion-a-year%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E%20higher%20profit%20margins%20than%20selling%20drugs%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20might%20cost%20you%20%248.50%20per%20pair%20of%20shoes%2C%20and%20if%20you%20could%20sell%20them%20on%20e-commerce%20sites%20for%20%2485%2C%26quot%3B%20Shapiro%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat%20margin%20was%20greater%20than%20the%20margin%20if%20you%20were%20trying%20to%20buy%20heroin%20or%20cocaine%20from%20your%20dealer%20and%20then%20resell%20it%20on%20the%20streets.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20government%20often%20relies%20on%20corporations%20to%20fill%20in%20the%20gaps.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20complaints%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fastcompany.com%2F90412216%2Fa-team-of-1000-major-brands-are-fighting-back-against-counterfeit-design-on-amazon%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Epressure%20from%20retailers%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.modernretail.co%2Ftechnology%2Fa-timeline-of-amazons-efforts-to-curb-counterfeit-selling%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EAmazon%20increased%20its%20efforts%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20combat%20counterfeits%2C%20which%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.technologyreview.com%2F2023%2F06%2F20%2F1075088%2Fchinese-amazon-seller-counterfeit-lawsuit%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Erampant%20on%20the%20marketplace%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202020%2C%20Amazon%20established%20its%20Counterfeit%20Crimes%20Unit%2C%20which%20works%20with%20brands%20to%20identify%20and%20remove%20counterfeit%20products.%20It%20also%20conducts%20investigations%20and%20sends%20criminal%20referrals%20to%20law%20enforcement.%20In%20some%20cases%2C%20Amazon%20files%20civil%20lawsuits.%20The%20company%20recently%20filed%20a%20joint%20lawsuit%20alleging%20a%20crime%20ring%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aboutamazon.com%2Fnews%2Fpolicy-news-views%2Fthe-latest-updates-from-amazons-counterfeit-crimes-unit%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E%20attempted%20to%20sell%20counterfeit%20Therabody%20massage%20devices%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Amazon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20the%20company%20removed%20more%20than%206%20million%20counterfeit%20items%20from%20the%20marketplace%20and%20referred%20over%201%2C300%20individuals%20to%20law%20enforcement%20in%20the%20US%2C%20UK%2C%20Europe%2C%20and%20China%2C%20according%20to%20Amazon's%20annual%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbrandservices.amazon.com%2Fprogressreport%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EBrand%20Protection%20Report%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShapiro%20said%20online%20counterfeits%20will%20continue%20to%20be%20a%20never-ending%20battle%20for%20most%20brands.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20too%20much%20money%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20going%20away.%26quot%3B%20But%20without%20a%20strategy%2C%20brands%20can%20suffer%20reputational%20damage%20from%20bad%20reviews%20when%20people%20buy%20phony%20products%20marketed%20as%20their%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BReviews%20can%20pile%20up%20and%20we%20can%20then%20go%20in%20and%20take%20down%20the%20counterfeits%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20can't%20fix%20your%20reviews%20for%20you.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-sales-of-knockoffs-have-soared-2023-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694682061000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6501db1c1afe8f0019e99b65%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-sales-of-knockoffs-have-soared-2023-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Technology%20has%20escalated%20the%20counterfeit%20market%20and%20made%20it%20difficult%20to%20differentiate%20between%20real%20and%20fake%20products.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jortakales%40insider.com%20(Jennifer%20Ortakales%20Dawkins)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-sales-of-knockoffs-have-soared-2023-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Using%20the%20wrong%20USB-C%20charger%20could%20permanently%20ruin%20your%20new%20iPhone%2015%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224158%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Two%20iPhone%2015%20charging%20ports%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6501d85e1afe8f0019e9984b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223119%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20iPhone%2015%20will%20come%20with%20a%20new%20USB-C%20port.%3Cp%3EJustin%20Sullivan%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EYou%20should%20be%20careful%20about%20how%20you%20charge%20your%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-iphone-15-event-announcements-usb-c-titanium-pro-watches-2023-9%5C%22%3EiPhone%2015.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EUsing%20low-quality%20USB-C%20chargers%20could%20make%20it%20easier%20to%20accidentally%20fry%20your%20phone.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThis%20is%20because%20some%20USB-C%20connectors%20don't%20have%20safeguards%20for%20electricity%20surges.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EBuyers%20of%20the%20iPhone%2015%20should%20beware%3A%20using%20the%20wrong%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feverything-wrong-usb-c-cables-explained-which-cable-2018-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUSB-C%20connectors%3C%2Fa%3E%20could%20fry%20your%20device.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fiphone-15-preorder-price-release-date-new-features-2023-9%5C%22%3EApple%20will%20release%20the%20new%20iPhone%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20September%2022%20and%20for%20the%20first%20time%20it%20will%20feature%20a%20USB-C%20port%20%E2%80%94%20marking%20a%20shift%20from%20Apple's%20Lightning%20connectors.%20This%20is%20the%20first%20time%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-iphone-15-will-require-usb-c-charger-lightning-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enew%20iPhone%20charger%3C%2Fa%3E%20will%20be%20launched%20in%20over%20a%20decade.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20USB-C%20cables%20and%20plugins%20can%20have%20fewer%20protections%20for%20your%20phone%20than%20Apple's%20official%20Lightning%20cables%2C%20so%20you%20should%20be%20wary%20of%20public%20plugins%20and%20cheap%20connectors.%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsupport.apple.com%2Fguide%2Fiphone%2Fimportant-safety-information-iph301fc905%2Fios%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EApple%3C%2Fa%3E%20recommends%20that%20iPhone%20owners%20use%20Apple%20chargers%20or%20other%20brands%20that%20meet%20certain%20safety%20regulations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUsing%20a%20charger%20that%20doesn't%20meet%20standards%20could%20put%20iPhones%20at%20risk%2C%20Jessa%20Jones%2C%20the%20owner%20of%20the%20mobile%20device%20repair%20shop%20iPad%20Rehab%2C%20told%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2023%2F09%2F12%2Ftechnology%2Fpersonaltech%2Fapple-iphone-lightning-usb-c.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20New%20York%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20NYT's%20Brian%20X.%20Chen%20explains%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHigh-quality%20chargers%20are%20essentially%20electronics%20with%20tiny%20circuit%20boards%20inside%20them.%20On%20Apple's%20official%20Lightning%20cable%2C%20there%20are%20two%20chips%3A%20One%20authenticates%20that%20the%20cable%20is%20made%20by%20Apple%2C%20while%20the%20other%20acts%20as%20a%20fuse%20that%20isolates%20damage%20to%20the%20charger.%20In%20the%20event%20of%20a%20power%20fluctuation%2C%20for%20example%2C%20only%20the%20charger%20would%20be%20destroyed%20and%20not%20the%20phone%20itself%2C%20Ms.%20Jones%20said.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-fake-chargers-study-2016-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKnockoff%20chargers%3C%2Fa%3E%20may%20be%20less%20expensive%20but%20you%20could%20end%20up%20paying%20the%20price%20in%20future%20repairs.%20If%20you%20buy%20a%20charger%20that%20isn't%20Apple%20brand%2C%20you%20should%20look%20at%20the%20product's%20description%20and%20reviews.%20You%20can%20also%20use%20tools%20like%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-deals-prime-day-camelcamelcamel-fakespot-2017-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFakespot%3C%2Fa%3E%20when%20shopping%20on%20Amazon%20to%20make%20sure%20you're%20getting%20a%20quality%20product.%20Ideally%2C%20your%20charger%20should%20be%20MFi.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EApple's%20MFi%20%E2%80%94%20or%20Made%20for%20iPhone%20%E2%80%94%20program%20is%20meant%20to%20help%20protect%20users%2C%20whether%20or%20not%20they%20choose%20to%20buy%20Apple%20chargers%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tomsguide.com%2Fnews%2Four-iphone-15-usb-c-fears-might-have-just-been-confirmed-this-is-a-very-bad-idea%5C%22%20target%3D