es.com%2Fphoto%2F103659261.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EJawan%20has%20broken%20the%20record%20of%20'Pathaan'%20with%20its%20first%20week%20collections.%20The%20film%20now%20stands%20at%20Rs%20323%20crore%20nett%20by%20the%20end%20of%20its%20day%207.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bhim%20Army%20Founder%20Chandra%20Shekhar%20Aazad%20Could%20Contest%20LS%20Polls%20as%20INDIA%20Bloc%20Candidate%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F14142607%2FF5wQer1akAAVH0o.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20founder%20of%20Bhim%20Army%20and%20Azad%20Samaj%20Party%20Chandra%20Shekhar%20Aazad%20may%20contest%20his%20maiden%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20in%202024%20as%20an%20Indian%20National%20Developmental%20Inclusive%20Alliance%20(INDIA)%20bloc%20candidate.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20some%20reports%2C%20the%20Jayant%20Singh-led%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%20is%20trying%20to%20convince%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20chief%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20to%20accommodate%20him%20in%20the%20proposed%20Samajwadi%20Party-Congress-RLD%20alliance%20that%20is%20likely%20to%20contest%20together%20in%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fbhim-army-chief-chandra-shekhar-azad-may-contest-lok-sabha-poll-from-ups-nagina%2Farticle67303259.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20talks%20are%20on%20to%20bring%20Aazad%20under%20the%20INDIA%20umbrella.%20Aazad%20himself%20is%20interested%20in%20contesting%20from%20Western%20Uttar%20Pradesh%E2%80%99s%20Nagina%20(a%20reserved%20constituency)%20which%20has%20a%20substantial%20Dalit%20and%20Muslim%20population.%20If%20Aazad%20is%20brought%20into%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%2C%20the%20possibility%20of%20Mayawati-led%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%20to%20join%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20will%20practically%20end%2C%20as%20both%20Aazad%20and%20Mayawati%20have%20emerged%20as%20two%20rival%20ends%20of%20Dalit%20politics%20in%20UP.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUntil%20now%2C%20however%2C%20BSP%20has%20consistently%20maintained%20that%20it%20will%20contest%20alone%20in%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%20In%20such%20circumstances%2C%20Aazad%20could%20emerge%20as%20the%20Dalit%20face%20for%20UP%E2%80%99s%20INDIA%20bloc%20chapter%20which%20will%20heavily%20depend%20on%20its%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EPeechda%2C%20Dalit%2C%20Alpasankhyak%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(PDA%2C%20for%20%E2%80%98backward%2C%20Dalit%20and%20minority%E2%80%99)%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3Epolitical%20strategy%20to%20counter%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Hindutva.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAazad%20belongs%20to%20Saharanpur%20in%20western%20UP%20and%20over%20the%20years%20has%20emerged%20as%20a%20popular%20leader%20among%20Dalits%20and%20Muslims%20because%20of%20his%20consistent%20aggression%20against%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CYes%2C%20of%20course%2C%20I%20will%20be%20fighting%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%20For%20the%20last%20nine%20years%2C%20the%20Bhim%20Army%20has%20led%20people%E2%80%99s%20struggles%2C%20but%20without%20a%20presence%20in%20the%20legislatures%2C%20we%20feel%20that%20we%20reached%20a%20roadblock.%20Vote%20is%20after%20all%20the%20strongest%20weapon%20in%20the%20hand%20of%20the%20common%20man.%20And%20we%20want%20them%20to%20wield%20it%2C%20to%20replace%20the%20current%20political%20class%2C%20who%20show%20their%20faces%20only%20during%20the%20elections%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CNot%20only%20the%20Dalits%2C%20the%20minorities%2C%20tribals%20and%20the%20backward%20classes%20do%20not%20have%20any%20strong%20representation%20today.%20The%20MPs%20and%20MLAs%20belonging%20to%20these%20communities%20are%20silent%2C%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECurrently%2C%20Aazad%E2%80%99s%20party%20holds%20nine%20district%20council%20seats%20and%20has%20a%20significant%20influence%20in%20western%20UP.%20Nagina%20was%20a%20part%20of%20the%20erstwhile%20Bijnor%20seat%20from%20where%20several%20national%20Dalit%20leaders%20like%20Mayawati%2C%20Ram%20Vilas%20Paswan%20and%20Meira%20Kumar%20have%20earlier%20contested.%20It%20is%20currently%20considered%20a%20BSP%20stronghold.%20Contesting%20from%20Nagina%20would%20mean%20Aazad%20directly%20challenging%20BSP%20in%20UP%2C%20the%20impact%20of%20which%20may%20be%20tectonic%20as%20far%20as%20BSP%E2%80%99s%20future%20is%20concerned.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CTo%20stake%20a%20claim%20and%20to%20signal%20the%20beginning%20of%20his%20campaign%20Mr.%20Azad%20will%20be%20holding%20a%20public%20meeting%20here%20(Nagina)%20on%20October%209%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EHindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAzaad%E2%80%99s%20electoral%20performance%20until%20now%20has%20been%20poor.%20He%20contested%20against%20UP%20chief%20minister%20Adityanath%20from%20Gorakhpur%20(Sadar)%20in%20the%202022%20assembly%20elections%20but%20lost%20his%20deposit.%20However%2C%20if%20he%20manages%20to%20join%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%2C%20his%20electoral%20prospects%20may%20receive%20a%20huge%20boost.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAzaad%20has%20been%20showering%20praises%20on%20Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20and%20his%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Yatra%20over%20the%20last%20few%20months%2C%20and%20has%20admitted%20that%20despite%20his%20differences%20with%20the%20Congress%2C%20he%20has%20admired%20Rahul%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20work.%20He%20also%20hailed%20the%20attempts%20by%20opposition%20parties%20to%20come%20together%20under%20one%20platform%20when%20INDIA%20was%20taking%20shape.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20in%20an%20unprecedented%20situation%2C%20the%20inflation%20and%20unemployment%20rate%20are%20at%20an%20all%20time%20high.%20The%20cases%20of%20caste%20atrocities%20are%20completely%20ignored%20by%20the%20current%20dispensation.%20There%20is%20a%20deep%20resentment%20among%20the%20electorate%2C%20in%20such%20a%20scenario%2C%20it%20is%20only%20natural%20for%20all%20parties%20to%20come%20together%2C%E2%80%9D%20Azaad%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EHindu%3C%2Fem%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%2C%20however%2C%20said%20that%20currently%20his%20party%20plans%20to%20contest%20the%20upcoming%20assembly%20elections%20in%20Telangana%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20and%20Rajasthan%20for%20which%20he%20has%20planned%20a%20series%20of%20public%20meetings%20next%20month.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20sizeable%20cadres%20in%20all%20the%20four%20states%2C%E2%80%9D%20Azaad%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20has%20planned%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Epadyatras%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(foot-marches)%20from%20September%2019%20to%2023%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20from%20September%2027%20to%20October%206%20in%20Rajasthan.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694681921000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F14142607%2FF5wQer1akAAVH0o.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fchandra-shekhar-aazad-bhim-army-india-lok-sabha-election%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Azaad%E2%80%99s%20electoral%20performance%20until%20now%20has%20been%20poor.%20He%20contested%20against%20UP%20CM%20Adityanath%20from%20Gorakhpur%20(Sadar)%20in%20the%202022%20assembly%20elections%20but%20lost%20his%20deposit.%20However%2C%20if%20he%20manages%20to%20join%20the%20INDIA%20bloc