lling%20of%20a%20saga%20that%20does%20a%20reasonable%20job%20of%20presenting%20an%20account%20of%20a%20megalopolis'%20turbulent%20past.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EBambai%20Meri%20Jaan%3C%2Fem%3E%20portrays%20on%20one%20man's%20obsession%20with%20power%20and%20money.%20It%20also%20delves%20into%20the%20nitty-gritties%20of%20the%20policing%20of%20a%20city%20in%20the%20grip%20of%20unstoppable%20criminal%20gangs%20at%20war%20with%20each%20other.%20The%20series%2C%20marred%20by%20a%20gratuitous%20surfeit%20of%20foul%20language%2C%20rides%20on%20the%20spectacle%20of%20cops%20and%20criminals%20in%20a%20tight%20embrace%20as%20Bombay%20grapples%20with%20the%20depredations%20of%20a%20rampaging%20underworld.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKay%20Kay%20Menon%20and%20Avinash%20Tiwary%20as%20a%20pair%20of%20father%20and%20son%20who%20do%20not%20see%20eye%20to%20eye%20lead%20the%20charge%20but%20there%20is%20much%20more%20to%20the%20series%20on%20the%20acting%20front%20than%20the%20two%20actors%20who%20turbocharge%20the%20show.%20Several%20of%20the%20supporting%20cast%20members%20-%20notably%20Jitin%20Gulati%2C%20Saurabh%20Sachdeva%2C%20Nivedita%20Bhattacharya%2C%20Nawab%20Shah%2C%20Vivan%20Bhathena%20and%20Kritika%20Kamra%20-%20throw%20everything%20they've%20got%20into%20a%20show%20that%20requires%20all%20the%20heft%20that%20they%20can%20bring%20to%20the%20table.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EProduced%20by%20Excel%20Media%20%26amp%3B%20Entertainment%20and%20created%20by%20Rensil%20D'Silva%20and%20the%20show's%20director%20Shujaat%20Saudagar%2C%20%3Cem%3EBambai%20Meri%20Jaan%3C%2Fem%3E%20rustles%20up%20a%20cocktail%20of%20organized%20crime%2C%20violence%20and%20vengeance%20and%20delivers%20it%20in%20a%20manner%20that%20focuses%20as%20much%20on%20the%20bloody%20gang%20wars%20on%20the%20streets%20and%20dockyards%20of%20Bambai%20as%20it%20does%20on%20the%20emotional%20dynamics%20that%20are%20at%20work%20in%20the%20life%20of%20a%20boy%20determined%20to%20change%20his%20and%20his%20family's%20fortunes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FmkTcLd3b_Us%3Fsi%3DSPEftMuxLe5H95eW%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EBambai%20Meri%20Jaan%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20lit%20and%20lensed%20by%20cinematographer%20John%20Schmidt%2C%20captures%20the%20grit%20and%20grime%20of%20gang%20wars%20that%20leave%20behind%20a%20long%20trail%20of%20bodies%20and%20push%20a%20city%20to%20the%20edge.%20It%20pits%20a%20morally%20upright%2C%20God-fearing%20patriarch%20against%20a%20recalcitrant%20son%20who%20figures%20out%20that%20honesty%20does%20not%20pay%20in%20a%20world%20where%20fear%20is%20the%20key.%20The%20latter%20bamboozles%20his%20way%20into%20a%20life%20of%20crime.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDara%20Ismail%20(Avinash%20Tiwary)%20seeks%20to%20dislodge%20the%20reigning%20underworld%20triumvirate%20of%20Haji%20Maqbool%20(Saurabh%20Sachdeva)%2C%20Azeem%20Pathan%20(Nawab%20Shah)%20and%20Anna%20Rajan%20Mudaliar%20(Dinesh%20Prabhakar)%2C%20who%20have%20carved%20up%20the%20city%20into%20three%20zones%20to%20share%20the%20spoils%20of%20their%20smuggling%20and%20extortion%20rackets%20run%20in%20collusion%20with%20corrupt%20segments%20of%20the%20police%20force.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20special%20task%20force%20christened%20the%20%26quot%3BPathan%20Squad%26quot%3B%20is%20set%20up%20under%20Ismail%20Kadri%20(Kay%20Kay%20Menon)%2C%20a%20cop%20of%20unwavering%20integrity%2C%20and%20charged%20with%20the%20task%20of%20reining%20in%20the%20mafia%20dons.%20The%20squad%20does%20everything%20in%20its%20power%20to%20justify%20its%20existence%20but%20neither%20its%20best%20nor%20the%20power%20at%20its%20disposal%20is%20good%20enough%20to%20accomplish%20the%20mission%20of%20wiping%20out%20the%20underworld.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20story%20of%20Dara%20Kadri%20is%20narrated%20entirely%20from%20the%20standpoint%20of%20his%20father%2C%20Ismail%20Kadri%20(Kay%20Kay%20Menon)%2C%20who%20detests%20his%20rebellious%20son's%20criminal%20activities%20and%20attempts%20to%20distance%20himself%20from%20him%20and%20the%20quagmire%20that%20he%20drags%20the%20family%2C%20which%20includes%20his%20mother%20Sakina%20(Nivedita%20Bhattacharya)%2C%20elder%20brother%20Saadiq%20(Jitin%20Gulati)%20and%20younger%20siblings%20Ajju%20((Lakshya%20Kochhar)%20and%20Habiba%20(Kritika%20Kamra)%2C%20into.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDara's%20father%20is%20a%20tragic%20figure%2C%20a%20sort%20of%20last%20man%20standing%20in%20a%20crumbling%20world.%20He%20is%20honest%20to%20a%20fault%20but%20pays%20the%20price%20for%20a%20single%20indiscretion.%20Ismail%20Kadri's%20fall%20from%20grace%20is%20swift.%20H%20is%20condemned%20to%20a%20life%20of%20great%20financial%20hardship%2C%20which%20forces%20him%20to%20accept%20the%20wily%20Haji's%20inducements%20and%20compels%20Dara%20to%20renege%20against%20his%20father%20and%20take%20on%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20Bombay%20underworld.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EBambai%20Meri%20Jaan%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20a%20crime%20drama%20that%20hinges%20on%20the%20ups%20and%20downs%20of%20filial%20relationships%2C%20which%20sets%20it%20apart%20a%20bit%20from%20other%20similar%20generic%20offerings%20that%20usually%20come%20out%20of%20the%20Mumbai%20industry.%20The%20equations%20between%20Ismail%20and%20Dara%20is%20the%20show's%20focal%20point%20but%20also%20important%20to%20the%20plot%20is%20the%20sibling%20'rivalry'%20that%20arises%20between%20Dara%20and%20Saadiq%20(who%20feels%20he%20has%20always%20received%20the%20rough%20end%20of%20the%20stick)%20and%20the%20bond%20between%20Dara%20and%20his%20feisty%20kid%20sister%20Habiba.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EBambai%20Meri%20Jaan%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20also%20a%20love%20story%20involving%20a%20gangster%20and%20the%20city%20that%20is%20described%20his%20beloved.%20Dara%20is%20obviously%20no%20poet%20and%20he%20has%20no%20words%20of%20his%20own%20to%20express%20his%20passion%20for%20Bombay%2C%20for%20its%20underworld%20at%20any%20rate.%20The%20protagonist%20also%20has%20a%20more%20mundane%20love%20interest%20in%20Pari%20(Amyra%20Dastur)%2C%20daughter%20of%20an%20Irani%20caf%26amp%3B%23233%3B%20owner%20he%20has%20frequently%20rubbed%20up%20the%20wrong%20way.%20Words%20fail%20him%20here%20too%20and%20he%20is%20barely%20able%20to%20profess%20his%20love%20for%20the%20girl%20he%20has%20been%20smitten%20with%20since%20he%20was%20a%20schoolboy.%20Neither%20Bombay%20nor%20Pari%20seems%20destined%20to%20be%20his%20in%20the%20long%20run%20but%20Dara%20isn't%20one%20to%20give%20up%20without%20a%20fight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EBambai%20Meri%20Jaan%3C%2Fem%3E%20begins%20in%201986.%20Dara%20Kadri%2C%20cornered%20by%20the%20law%2C%20is%20all%20set%20to%20fly%20out%20of%20Bombay.%20It%20is%20evident%20that%20this%20prelude%20is%20where%20the%20show%20is%20going%20to%20end.%20The%20story%20jumps%20a%20couple%20of%20decades%20into%20the%20past%20-%20to%201964%2C%20to%20be%20precise%20-%20and%20homes%20in%20on%20the%20Kadri%20couple%20surviving%20on%20a%20policeman's%20meagre%20salary%20and%20preparing%20for%20the%20birth%20of%20their%20fourth%20child.%20The%20financial%20strain%20worsens%20as%20the%20years%20go%20by%20and%20Ismail's%20second%20son%20Dara%20begins%20to%20go%20astray%20with%20intent.%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20an%20avowedly%20fictional%20account%20inspired%20by%20true%20events.%20Most%20of%20the%20key%20characters%2C%20including%20Assistant%20Commissioner%20of%20Police%20Ranbir%20Malik%20(Shiv%20Pandit)%2C%20who%20props%20up%20Dara%20Kadri%20with%20the%20aim%20of%20countering%20the%20clout%20of%20Haji%20and%20Pathan%2C%20have%20been%20drawn%20from%20real%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20tale%20is%20hackneyed%20on%20two%20critical%20levels.%20One%2C%20the%20Dawood%20story%20has%20been%20documented%20on%20the%20big%20screen%20several%20times%20in%20the%20new%20millennium%20as%20well%20as%20given%20the%20documentary%20treatment%20as%20recently%20as%20early%20this%20year%20(in%20Netflix's%20Mumbai%20Mafia%3A%20Police%20vs%20the%20Underworld)%2C%20so%20%26lt%3Bi%3EBambai%20Meri%20Jaan%26lt%3B%2Fi%3E%2C%20despite%20all%20the%20action%20and%20dramatic%20twists%20that%20it%20musters%20up%2C%20struggles%20to%20deliver%20anything%20that%20could%20be%20deemed%20novel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20the%20language%20that%20%3Cem%3EBambai%20Meri%20Jaan%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Eemploys%20-%20the%20screenplay%20is%20credited%20to%20Rensil%20D'Silva%20and%20Sammeer%20Arora%20and%20the%20dialogues%20have%20been%20written%20Abbas%20Dalal%20and%20Hussain%20Dalal%20-%20adds%20no%20real%20value%20to%20the%20exercise.%20It%20is%20coarse%2C%20which%20may%20be%20understandable%20to%20a%20certain%20extent%20given%20the%20setting%2C%20and%20the%20profanities%20are%20way%20too%20over%20the%20top.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EBambai%20Meri%20Jaan%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20sweeping%20and%20sporadically%20gripping%20underworld%20history%20couched%20in%20a%20highly%20dramatic%20shell%20that%20stands%20on%20generalisations%20about%20criminality%2C%20policing%20and%20a%20sprawling%20city%20of%20dreams%20and%20nightmares.%20It%20is%20the%20actors%20who%20save%20the%20day%20for%20%3Cem%3EBambai%20Meri%20Jaan.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694679900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2F45dqc5d_avinash-_625x300_14_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fbambai-meri-jaan-review-the-actors-save-the-day-in-sporadically-gripping-underworld-history-2-5-stars-4388813%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bambai%20Meri%20Jaan%20Review%3A%20Kay%20Kay%20Menon%20and%20Avinash%20Tiwary%20as%20a%20pair%20of%20father%20and%20son%20who%20do%20not%20see%20eye%20to%20eye%20lead%20the%20charge%20but%20there%20is%20much%20more%20to%20the%20series%20on%20the%20acting%20front%20than%20the%20two%20actors%20who%20turbocharge%20the%20show.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22ht