set%20to%20your%20computer.%20For%20the%20best%20results%2C%20invest%20in%20a%20USB%203%20cable%2C%20though%20you%20might%20also%20get%20acceptable%20results%20from%20a%20USB%202%20cable.%20Meta%20sells%20its%20own%2015-foot%20USB%203%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.meta.com%2Fquest%2Faccessories%2Flink-cable%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELink%20Cable%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20%2480%2C%20though%20you%20can%20find%20less%20expensive%20cables%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20If%20you%20haven't%20already%2C%20install%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.meta.com%2Fquest%2Fsetup%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOculus%20desktop%20app%3C%2Fa%3E%20onto%20your%20PC.%20Log%20in%20with%20your%20Meta%20account%20credentials.%20Also%20be%20sure%20you%20have%20installed%20and%20signed%20into%20the%20Steam%20desktop%20app.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Turn%20on%20your%20Quest%202%20and%20connect%20it%20to%20your%20computer%20via%20the%20USB%20cable.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E4.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Start%20the%20Oculus%20desktop%20app%2C%20click%20%3Cstrong%3EDevices%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20in%20the%20navigation%20pane%20on%20the%20left%2C%20and%20click%20%3Cstrong%3EAdd%20Headset%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%20Choose%20%3Cstrong%3EQuest%202%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20and%20follow%20the%20instructions%20to%20set%20up%20the%20headset%20for%20connection%20to%20your%20computer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221008%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Oculus%20desktop%20app%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F61e702aa04ce6e0018d79521%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22746%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAfter%20installing%20the%20Quest%20desktop%20app%2C%20you%20need%20to%20add%20your%20headset.%3Cp%3EDave%20Johnson%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E5.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20When%20the%20headset%20setup%20is%20comp