Shah%20Will%20Decide%20on%20Seat%20Sharing%20with%20JD(S)%2C%20Yediyurappa%20Strikes%20a%20Cautious%20Note%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F04%2F01101931%2Fyediyurappa.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EAfter%20announcing%20that%20the%20Janata%20Dal%20(Secular)%20would%20get%20to%20contest%20four%20out%20of%2028%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20as%20part%20of%20the%20alliance%20with%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20in%20Karnataka%20in%202024%20polls%2C%20former%20chief%20minister%20B.S.%20Yediyurappa%20struck%20a%20cautious%20note%2C%20saying%20that%20the%20matter%20of%20seat-sharing%20is%20left%20to%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20earlier%20statement%20on%20seat%20sharing%20was%20based%20on%20JD(S)%20leader%20H.D.%20Deve%20Gowda%E2%80%99s%20meeting%20with%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah.%20As%20most%20of%20you%20know%20the%20two%20leaders%20have%20met%3B%20I%20am%20also%20aware%20of%20it.%20But%20seat%20sharing%20is%20a%20matter%20left%20to%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20Shah.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20the%20authority%20to%20decide%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fkarnataka%2Fyediyurappa-adopts-a-cautious-approach-on-proposed-alliance-with-jds%2Farticle67304082.ece%5C%22%3Equoted%3C%2Fa%3E%20him%20as%20saying%2C%20after%20he%20attended%20the%20BJP%20parliamentary%20board%20meeting%20in%20Delhi%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20September%2013.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20not%20aware%20of%20further%20developments%20in%20this%20regard.%20We%20will%20come%20to%20know%20about%20it%20after%20further%20discussions.%E2%80%9D%20Yediyurappa%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20being%20pressed%20for%20an%20answer%20on%20the%20seat-sharing%20arrangement%20by%20media%20persons%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20what%20is%20in%20the%20minds%20of%20Modi%20and%20Shah.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20Yediyurappa%20who%20first%20confirmed%20the%20electoral%20alliance%20on%20September%208%2C%20going%20as%20far%20as%20announcing%20that%20JD(S)%20would%20get%20four%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20to%20contest.%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20happy%20that%20Deve%20Gowda%20%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E%20met%20our%20prime%20minister%20and%20they%20have%20already%20finalised%20about%20four%20seats.%20I%20welcome%20them%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%20the%20former%20chief%20minister%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20after%20attending%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20parliamentary%20board%20meeting%2C%20he%20said%20he%20isn%E2%80%99t%20sure%20of%20the%20seat-sharing%20arrangement%20and%20it%20is%20for%20Modi%20and%20Shah%20to%20decide.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYediyurappa%E2%80%99s%20remarks%20that%20JD(S)%20would%20get%20four%20seats%20as%20part%20of%20the%20alliance%20had%20JD(S)%20leader%20Kumaraswamy%20responding%20that%20no%20such%20decision%20had%20yet%20been%20taken%20and%20Yediyurappa%20had%20spoken%20in%20his%20personal%20capacity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWord%20has%20it%20that%20the%20JD(S)%20wants%20to%20contest%20in%20five%20seats%20%E2%80%93%20Mandya%2C%20Hassan%2C%20Tumakuru%2C%20Chickballapur%2C%20and%20Bengaluru%20Rural.%20However%2C%20it%20is%20being%20speculated%20that%20the%20BJP%20wants%20to%20offer%20to%20the%20JD(S)%20four%20seats%20of%20Kolar%2C%20Hassan%2C%20Mandya%2C%20and%20Bengaluru%20Rural.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESources%20in%20the%20BJP%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20Yediyurappa%E2%80%99s%20cautious%20note%20on%20the%20seat-sharing%20arrangement%20is%20an%20indication%20that%20there%20are%20some%20challenges%20going%20forward%20that%20need%20to%20be%20resolved%20before%20finalising%20who%20gets%20to%20contest%20what.%20The%20source%20further%20added%20that%20Yediyurappa%E2%80%99s%20comments%20also%20indicate%20that%20such%20sensitive%20matter%20is%20left%20to%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20high%20command.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694676020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F04%2F01101931%2Fyediyurappa.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmodi-shah-will-decide-on-seat-sharing-with-jds-yediyurappa-strikes-a-cautious-note%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22It%20was%20Yediyurappa%20who%20first%20confirmed%20the%20BJP-JD(S)%20electoral%20alliance%20on%20September%208%2C%20going%20as%20far%20as%20announcing%20that%20the%20latter%20would%20get%20four%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20to%20contest.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmodi-shah-will-decide-on-seat-sharing-with-jds-yediyurappa-strikes-a-cautious-note%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20Anantnag%20Encounter%2C%20India%20Loses%203%20Bravehearts%2C%204%20Children%20Their%20Fathers%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhen%20Major%20Ashish%20Dhonack%20said%20his%20goodbyes%20to%20his%20family%2C%20including%20his%20two-year-old%20daughter%2C%20to%20resume%20his%20duties%20in%20Kashmir%20one%20and%20a%20half%20months%20ago%2C%20he%20promised%20to%20return%20to%20Haryana's%20Panipat%20in%20October%20to%20help%20them%20move%20house.%20Weeks%20later%2C%20his%20body%20was%20being%20retrieved%20from%20the%20higher%20reaches%20of%20Anantnag's%20Kokorenag%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EColonel%20Manpreet%20Singh%2C%2041%2C%20commanding%20officer%20of%20the%2019%20Rashtriya%20Rifles%20(19%20RR)%20and%20a%20recipient%20of%20the%20prestigious%20Sena%20Medal%2C%20spoke%20to%20his%20family%2C%20including%20a%20six-year-old%20son%20and%20a%20two-year-old%20daughter%20in%20Chandigarh%2C%20just%20hours%20before%20dying%20of%20gunshot%20wounds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHimayun%20Bhat%2C%20son%20of%20retired%20Inspector%20General%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%20Police%20Ghulam%20Hassan%20Bhat%2C%20had%20become%20a%20father%20just%20a%20month%20ago.%20He%20was%20the%20third%20officer%20to%20die%20in%20an%20encounter%20with%20terrorists%20last%20night%20at%20Kokorenag.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%20night%2C%20the%20army%20and%20police%20had%20launched%20a%20joint%20operation%20in%20response%20to%20specific%20intelligence%20about%20terrorists%20in%20the%20area.%20The%20troops%2C%20led%20by%20the%20commanding%20officer%20and%20the%20deputy%20superintendent%20of%20police%2C%20came%20under%20heavy%20fire%20from%20the%20terrorists.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThree%20officers%20were%20critically%20injured%20in%20the%20gun%20battle.%20Reinforcements%20were%20sent%20to%20the%20scene%2C%20but%20the%20injured%20could%20not%20be%20immediately%20evacuated%20due%20to%20the%20terrorists'%20well-entrenched%20position%20and%20heavy%20gunfire.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHimayun%20Bhat's%20father%20Ghulam%20Hassan%20Bhat%20laid%20a%20wreath%20on%20his%20son's%20body%20in%20Kashmir's%20Budgam%20yesterday.%20His%20stoic%20demeanour%20did%20not%20betray%20his%20devastation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20just%20five%20years%20of%20service%20with%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20Police%2C%20Himayun%20Bhat%20handled%20extremely%20difficult%20tasks%20including%20his%20tenure%20in%20the%20Special%20Operations%20Group%20that%20deals%20exclusively%20with%20anti-terrorist%20operations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EColonel%20Singh%2C%20commander%20of%20the%20Sikh%20Light%20Infantry%20who%20was%20awarded%20the%20Sena%20Medal%20(Gallantry)%20in%202021%2C%20had%20spoken%20to%20his%20family%20in%20Chandigarh%20on%20the%20day%20he%20died.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20last%20spoke%20to%20him%20at%206%3A45%20am.%20He%20said%20he%20would%20speak%20later.%20He%20was%20a%20good%20man.%20Last%20year%2C%20he%20was%20awarded%20the%20Sena%20Medal%20for%20his%20duty.%20I%20salute%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20Colonel%20Singh's%20brother-in-law%20Virender%20Gill%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20thirty-four-year-old%20Major%20Dhonack's%20home%20in%20Patiala%2C%20three%20sisters%20mourn%20their%20only%20brother.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLast%20spoke%20to%20him%20on%20the%20telephone.%20He%20was%20home%20one%20and%20a%20half%20months%20ago%20and%20was%20supposed%20to%20return%20in%20October%20to%20shift%20houses%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Major%20Dhonack's%20uncle%2C%20whose%20nephew%20was%20conferred%20with%20the%20Sena%20Medal%20in%20August%20this%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETributes%20poured%20in%20for%20the%20three%20soldiers%20from%20across%20the%20country.%3Cbr%3E%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%26quot%3BPaid%20tributes%20to%20JKP's%20DySP%20Humayun%20Bhat%2C%20who%20laid%20down%20his%20life%20in%20an%20anti-terror%20operation%20in%20Anantnag.%20I%20salute%20the%20indomitable%20courage%20and%20supreme%20sacrifice%20of%20Col%20Manpreet%20Singh%20%26amp%3B%20Major%20Ashish%20Dhonack.%20Entire%20nation%20stands%20firmly%20with%20their%20families%20in%20this%20hour%20of%20grief%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20Lieutenant%20Governor's%20office%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20brave%20Army%20personnel%20and%20a%20DSP%20have%20made%20the%20supreme%20sacrifice%20fighting%20terrorists%20in%20an%20encounter%20at%20Anantnag%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%20We%20are%20extremely%20saddened%20by%20their%20loss.%20Our%20deepest%20condolences%20to%20the%20families%20of%20our%20bravehearts%2C%26quot%3B%20Congress%20president%20Malikarjun%20Kharge%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIndia%20stands%20united%20against%20terrorism%2C%20the%20Congress%20chief%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694675880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fsqv5332_kashmir_625x300_14_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fin-anantnag-encounter-india-loses-3-bravehearts-4-children-their-fathers-4388598%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22When%20Major%20Ashish%20Dhonack%20said%20his%20goodbyes%20to%20his%20family%2C%20including%20his%20two-year-old%20daughter%2C%20to%20resume%20his%20duties%20in%20Kash