sday%2C%20adding%20that%20contact%20tracing%20has%20begun.%20Of%20the%20706%20contacts%2C%2077%20are%20in%20the%20high-risk%20category%20and%20153%20health%20workers%20are%20in%20the%20low-risk%20category.%2013%20people%20are%20under%20observation%20in%20a%20hospital%20and%20are%20showing%20mild%20symptoms%2C%20like%20headache.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EThe%20nine-year-old%20boy's%20condition%20is%20critical%20and%20he%20is%20on%20ventilator%20support%20at%20a%20hospital%20in%20Kozhikode%2C%20the%20minister%20said.%20The%20state%20government%20has%20ordered%20monoclonal%20antibody%20from%20the%20Indian%20Council%20of%20Medical%20Research%20to%20treat%20him.%20It%20is%20the%20only%20available%20anti-viral%20treatment%20for%20Nipah%20virus%20infection%2C%20though%20it%20has%20not%20been%20clinically%20proven%20yet%2C%20news%20agency%20PTI%20reported.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EResponding%20to%20a%20question%20in%20the%20state%20assembly%2C%20the%20Kerala%20government%20has%20said%20seven%20village%20panchayats%20in%20Kozhikode%20district%20-%20Atanchery%2C%20Maruthonkara%2C%20Tiruvallur%2C%20Kuttiyadi%2C%20Kayakkodi%2C%20Villyapalli%2C%20and%20Kavilumpara%20-%20have%20been%20declared%20containment%20zones%20to%20limit%20the%20spread%20of%20the%20infection.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EThe%20Kerala%20government%20has%20also%20formed%2019%20core%20committees%20to%20coordinate%20all%20measures%20to%20contain%20the%20spread%20of%20the%20virus.%20Essential%20items%20are%20being%20delivered%20to%20those%20in%20isolation%20by%20volunteer%20teams%20formed%20by%20the%20local%20self-government.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EA%20holiday%20has%20been%20declared%20for%20all%20educational%20institutions%20in%20Kozhikode%2C%20which%20is%20the%20epicentre%20of%20the%20outbreak%2C%20on%20Thursday%20and%20Friday.%20The%20announcement%20was%20made%20by%20Kozhikode%20District%20Collector%20A%20Geetha%20in%20a%20Facebook%20post.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EFormer%20Kerala%20health%20Minister%20and%20senior%20CPM%20MLA%20KK%20Shailaja%2C%20who%20is%20also%20known%20as%20Shailaja%20Teacher%20and%20was%20praised%20for%20containing%20the%20Nipah%20infection%20effectively%20in%202018%2C%20has%20said%20that%20the%20situation%20is%20not%20as%20scary%20as%20it%20was%20that%20year.%20She%20said%20the%20state%20has%20a%20standard%20operating%20procedure%20in%20place%20to%20fight%20the%20infection.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BIn%202018%2C%20it%20was%20a%20new%20virus%20to%20us%2C%20and%20we%20did%20not%20have%20any%20experience%20battling%20such%20an%20infection.%20Now%2C%20we%20have%20everything%20in%20place%20to%20contain%20it%20effectively%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Shailaja%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20by%20PTI.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EThe%20Nipah%20virus%20is%20a%20zoonotic%20virus%20and%20is%20named%20after%20the%20Malaysian%20village%20it%20was%20first%20detected%20in.%20It%20can%20be%20transmitted%20to%20humans%20from%20animals%20such%20as%20bats%20or%20pigs.%20It%20can%20also%20be%20transmitted%20through%20contaminated%20food%20or%20close%20contact%20with%20an%20infected%20person.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EAccording%20to%20the%20World%20Health%20Organisation%2C%20Nipah%20virus%20infection%20in%20humans%20causes%20a%20range%20of%20clinical%20presentations%2C%20from%20asymptomatic%20infection%20to%20acute%20respiratory%20infection%20and%20fatal%20encephalitis.%20The%20case%20fatality%20rate%20is%20estimated%20to%20be%2040-75%25.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EFruit%20bats%20of%20the%20Pteropodidae%20family%20are%20the%20natural%20host%20of%20the%20virus.%20The%20WHO%20says%20there%20is%20no%20treatment%20or%20vaccine%20available%20for%20either%20people%20or%20animals%2C%20and%20the%20primary%20treatment%20for%20humans%20is%20supportive%20care.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Fol%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694675640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2F4ckdn2vo_kerala-nipah_625x300_14_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fshailaja-teacher-nipah-spread-nipah-count-now-five-schools-shut-in-kerala-district-10-points-4388522%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Another%20Nipah%20virus%20infection%20has%20been%20confirmed%20in%20Kerala%2C%20taking%20the%20total%20cases%20to%20five.%20Two%20people%20have%20died%20and%20the%20other%20three%2C%20including%20a%20nine-year-old%20boy%2C%20are%20undergoing%20treatment.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fshailaja-teacher-nipah-spread-nipah-count-now-five-schools-shut-in-kerala-district-10-points-4388522%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fshailaja-teacher-nipah-spread-nipah-count-now-five-schools-shut-in-kerala-district-10-points-4388522%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fshailaja-teacher-nipah-spread-nipah-count-now-five-schools-shut-in-kerala-district-10-points-4388522%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20Indian%20Is%20India%2C%20and%20Other%20Considerations%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F20123532%2FIMG_2186.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EProminent%20scholar%20and%20economist%20Bibek%20Debroy%2C%20who%20serves%20as%20the%20economic%20adviser%20to%20the%20current%20government%2C%20authored%20an%20article%20titled%20%E2%80%98%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2Fopinion%2Fonline-views%2Ftheres-a-case-for-we-the-people-to-embrace-a-new-constitution-11692021963182.html%5C%22%3EAdvocating%20a%20New%20Constitution%3A%20A%20Case%20for%20%E2%80%98We%20the%20People%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%98.%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPublished%20in%20%3Cem%3EMint%3C%2Fem%3E%20on%20August%2014%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20this%20article%20calls%20for%20the%20adoption%20of%20a%20new%20constitution%2C%20setting%20a%20target%20date%20of%202047%20for%20its%20implementation.%20While%20there%20were%20previously%20speculations%20about%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20intentions%20to%20amend%20the%20constitution%2C%20Debroy%E2%80%99s%20public%20stance%20on%20this%20matter%20confirms%20the%20validity%20of%20these%20assumptions.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20fact%20that%20government%20officials%20and%20bureaucrats%20are%20openly%20endorsing%20the%20idea%20of%20a%20new%20constitution%20on%20public%20platforms%2C%20such%20as%20%3Cem%3EMint%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20underscores%20the%20seriousness%20of%20this%20proposal.%20This%20development%20dispels%20any%20doubts%20or%20rumours%2C%20as%20it%20reflects%20a%20deliberate%20line%20of%20thinking%20within%20influential%20circles.%20It%20is%20significant%20that%20individuals%20close%20to%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20are%20now%20advocating%20for%20constitutional%20change%2C%20indicating%20that%20this%20is%20not%20a%20random%20or%20isolated%20viewpoint.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20important%20to%20note%20that%20right-wing%20Hindu%20ideologues%20and%20leaders%20have%20long%20criticised%20the%20existing%20constitution%2C%20viewing%20it%20as%20a%20colonial%20legacy%20rooted%20in%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20Act%2C%201935.%20This%20perspective%20contrasts%20with%20the%20historical%20context%20in%20which%20the%20constitution%20was%20crafted%20after%20extensive%20deliberation%2C%20led%20by%20figures%20like%20Dr.%20B.R.%20Ambedkar%20and%20Speaker%20Rajendra%20Prasad%2C%20who%20were%20deeply%20engaged%20in%20the%20anti-colonial%20struggle%20that%20shaped%20India%20as%20a%20nation.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20opposition%20to%20the%20constitution%20manifests%20itself%20in%20various%20ways.%20When%20K.%20Sudarshan%20became%20an%20RSS%20%3Cem%3Esarsanghchalak%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20he%20openly%20declared%20that%20the%20Indian%20constitution%20was%20based%20on%20Western%20values%20and%20should%20be%20replaced%20by%20one%20based%20on%20Indian%20scriptures%20referencing%20Manusmriti.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20ashamed%20to%20change%20the%20constitution%20completely%20because%20we%20have%20already%20changed%20it%20a%20hundred%20times%2C%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20said%20France%20has%20revised%20its%20own%20four%20times.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fvideo-karan-thapar-fali-nariman-new-constitution%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98We%20Have%20Veiled%20Emergency%2C%20Judges%20Often%20Lack%20Spine%2C%20Writing%20New%20Constitution%20at%20This%20Time%20Impossible%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThere%E2%80%99s%20nothing%20sacred%20about%20that.%20In%20fact%2C%20it%20is%20the%20root%20cause%20of%20most%20of%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20problems%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20also%20related%20to%20their%20concept%20of%20decolonisation%20of%20minds%20as%20put%20forward%20by%20RSS%20general%20secretary%20Dattatreya%20Hosabale%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Euro-centric%20ideas%2C%20systems%20and%20practices%2C%20the%20western%20world%20view%20were%20still%20ruling%20us%20for%20decades.%20Independent%20nations%20didn%E2%80%99t%20shirk%20them%20totally.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20colonial%20era%20cannot%20be%20viewed%20as%20black%20or%20white.%20It%20has%20shades%20of%20grey.%20Colonial%20powers%20plundered%20our%20wealth%2C%20but%20they%20also%20had%20to%20open%20institutions%20that%20articulated%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eequality%20between%20men%20(and%20women).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20The%20RSS%20committee%20and%20the%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20advisor%20can%20make%20various%20arguments%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20abolition%20of%20this%20constitution%2C%20but%20essentially%20they%20reject%20the%20equality%20that%20the%20values%20of%20people%20like%20Bhagat%20Singh%2C%20the%20struggles%20launched%20by%20Ambedkar%20and%20the%20national%20movement%20have%20shaped%20the%20whole%20world.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMovement%20indeed%2C%20up%20until%20the%201990s%2C%20the%20country%20attempted%20to%20embark%20on%20the%20path%20of%20equality%2C%20relying%20on%20the%20Indian%20constitution%20for%20support%20and%20Nehru%E2%80%99s%20modernisation%20policies.%20Now%20it%20seems%20we%E2%80%99re%20taking%20a%20step%20backwards.%20With%20the%20temple%20and%20cow%20dominating%20the%20scene%2C%20invoking%20ancient%20values%20and%20the%20Brahmanic%20interpretation%20of%20the%20past%20(so-called%20%E2%80%9Ccivilisational%20values%E2%80%9D)%20paves%20the%20way%20to%20inequality%2C%20subverting%20what%20we%20have%20seen%20through%20the%20larger%20mass%20movement%20of%20history%20achieved%E2%80%A6the%20struggle%20for%20freedom%20in%20India.%20Any%20opposition%20to%20the%20constitution%20of%20India%20is%20merely%20a%20reuse%20to%20bring%20the%20country%20back%20to%20a%20time%20when%20inequalities%20(caste%2C%20class%20and%20gender)%20were%20sanctified%20by%20religion%20(Brahmanism).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDebroy%20clarifies%20that%20his%20article%20represents%20his%20personal%20views%20and%20does%20not%20necessarily%20reflect%20the%20stance%20of%20the%20Economic%20Advisory%20Council%20to%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20or%20the%20Indian%20government.%20However%2C%20the%20article%E2%80%99s%20thorough%20and%20confident%20articulation%20suggests%20that%20it%20should%20not%20be%20dismissed%20as%20merely%20one%20individual%E2%80%99s%20opinion.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDebroy%20outlines%20a%20range%20of%20reform%20agendas%2C%20covering%20aspects%20like%20factor%20markets%2C%20tax%20reform%2C%20government%20expenditure%20prioritisation%2C%20infrastructure%20development%2C%20labour%20market%20formalisation%2C%20urbanisation%2C%20and%20legislative%20efficiency%2C%20all%20with%20the%20aim%20of%20achieving%20change%20by%202047.%20He%20highlights%20that%20numerous%20amendments%20over%20the%20years%20have%20altered%20the%20original%20constitution%2C%20leading%20to%20the%20need%20for%20a%20new%20one%2C%20a%20position%20he%20believes%20is%20not%20bound%20by%20the%201973%20Supreme%20Court%20judgment%20on%20the%20basic%20structure.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20can%20remember%20the%20blog%20article%20by%20Arun%20Jaitley%20named%20%E2%80%98%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.arunjaitley.com%2Fes%2Fthe-njac-judgement-an-alternative-view%2F%5C%22%3EThe%20NJAC%20Judgement%20%E2%80%93%20An%20Alternative%20View%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%98%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20which%20he%20posted%20on%20October%2018%2C%202015%2C%20where%20he%20clearly%20mentioned%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Indian%20democracy%20cannot%20be%20tyranny%20of%20the%20unelected%20and%20if%20the%20elected%20are%20undermined%2C%20democracy%20itself%20will%20be%20in%20danger%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EElection%20is%20a%20very%20integral%20part%20of%20democracy%20which%20cannot%20be%20avoided%20but%20in%20every%20decision%20it%20is%20not%20the%20case%2C%20the%20people%20who%20made%20the%20constitution%20knew%20it%20very%20well%20so%20they%20proposed%20various%20institutions%20for%20different%20activities.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20cites%20a%20study%20by%20the%20University%20of%20Chicago%20Law%20School%2C%20indicating%20that%20written%20constitution%20in%20other%20countries%20have%20an%20average%20lifespan%20of%20only%2017%20years.%20Given%20that%20India%E2%80%99s%20current%20constitution%20is%20largely%20based%20on%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20Act%2C%201935%2C%20which%20is%20viewed%20as%20a%20colonial%20legacy%2C%20Debroy%20argues%20for%20a%20new%20preamble%20that%20reevaluates%20the%20meanings%20of%20terms%20like%20secularism%2C%20democracy%2C%20justice%2C%20freedom%2C%20and%20equality%20in%20the%20context%20of%20changing%20times.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECritics%20argue%20that%20Debroy%E2%80%99s%20perspective%20raises%20questions%20about%20the%20legacy%20of%20leaders%20like%20Ambedkar%2C%20Rajendra%20Prasad%2C%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%2C%20Sardar%20Vallabhbhai%20Patel%2C%20and%20others%20who%20played%20pivotal%20roles%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20independence%20and%20constitution-making.%20They%20contend%20that%20labelling%20the%20constitution%20as%20a%20colonial%20legacy%20is%20an%20audacious%20attempt%20to%20rewrite%20history%20and%20undermine%20the%20values%20enshrined%20in%20it.%20One%20BJP%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%2C%20Naresh%20Bansal%2C%20questioned%20the%20place%20of%20very%20word%20%E2%80%9CIndia%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20constitution%2C%20as%20it%20is%20a%20symbol%20of%20slavery.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Fbharat-india-hindustan-history%5C%22%3EBharat%2C%20India%20and%20Hindustan%20Don%E2%80%99t%20Cancel%20Each%20Other%20Out.%20They%20Reflect%20Continuities%20in%20Our%20History%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20government%E2%80%99s%20recent%20focus%20on%20revising%20various%20aspects%20of%20the%20country%2C%20from%20parliamentary%20buildings%20to%20legal%20codes%20and%20then%20to%20th%2C%20has%20raised%20concerns%20about%20its%20intentions%20and%20the%20potential%20implications%20for%20India%E2%80%99s%20democratic%20and%20secular%20character.%20This%20shift%20in%20emphasis%20from%20the%20values%20of%20the%20Indian%20constitution%20to%20alternative%20interpretations%20is%20sparking%20debates%20about%20the%20direction%20in%20which%20the%20country%20is%20headed.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20instance%20when%20the%20new%20parliament%20house%20was%20inaugurated%20it%20was%20said%20that%20the%20old%20parliament%20house%20is%20the%20sign%20of%20the%20colonial%20era.%20When%20the%20opposition%20formed%20an%20alliance%20and%20named%20it%20%E2%80%98INDIA%E2%80%99%2C%20Assam%E2%80%99s%20Chief%20Minister%20Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma%20called%20the%20word%20%E2%80%9CIndia%E2%80%9D%20a%20sign%20of%20slavery.%20When%20the%20government%20is%20proposing%20new%20bills%20for%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%2C%20then%20too%20it%20is%20calling%20the%20old%20system%20a%20symbol%20of%20the%20colonial%20era.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnd%20now%20they%20are%20calling%20the%20constitution%20a%20symbol%20of%20colonialism.%20What%20kind%20of%20audacity%20is%20this%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20I%20mentioned%20before%2C%20these%20type%20of%20thoughts%20cannot%20be%20called%20random.%20On%20August%208%20former%20Chief%20Justice%20Ranjan%20Gogoi%20made%20his%20first%20speech%20where%20he%20also%20mentioned%20that%20there%20is%20a%20point%20to%20debate%20on%20the%20basic%20structure%20of%20the%20constitution.%20He%20stated%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EBasic%20structure%20of%20the%20constitution%20has%20a%20very%20debatable%20jurisprudential%20basis%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9D.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGogoi%E2%80%99s%20statement%20creates%20a%20paradox%2C%20because%20when%20he%20was%20in%20the%20post%20of%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%2C%20in%20many%20verdicts%2C%20he%20clearly%20supported%20the%20verdict%20of%201973%20and%20said%20that%20the%20basic%20structure%20of%20the%20constitution%20cannot%20be%20changed.%20But%20it%20cannot%20be%20coincidence%20that%20just%20after%20one%20week%20of%20Gogoi%E2%80%99s%20speech%2C%20Debroy%20openly%20articulated%20it.%20Debroy%E2%80%99s%20call%20for%20a%20new%20constitution%20aligns%20with%20a%20broader%20trend%20among%20some%20right-wing%20circles%2C%20who%20argue%20against%20the%20Western%20influence%20and%20character%20of%20the%20current%20constitution%2C%20favouring%20a%20return%20to%20traditional%20Indian%20values%2C%20even%20citing%20%3Cem%3EManusmriti%3C%2Fem%3E%20as%20a%20potential%20basis.%20This%20position%20contrasts%20with%20the%20historical%20trajectory%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20independence%20struggle%2C%20which%20aimed%20to%20eradicate%20caste%20and%20gender%20hierarchies%20and%20promote%20equality.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20conclusion%2C%20the%20proposal%20for%20a%20new%20constitution%2C%20as%20advocated%20by%20Debroy%20and%20some%20right-wing%20circles%2C%20represents%20a%20significant%20departure%20from%20India%E2%80%99s%20post-independence%20ethos%20and%20raises%20complex%20questions%20about%20the%20nation%E2%80%99s%20values%2C%20identity%2C%20and%20future%20direction.%20The%20debate%20around%20this%20issue%20is%20emblematic%20of%20broader%20discussions%20about%20the%20evolving%20character%20of%20Indian%20democracy%20and%20its%20relationship%20with%20historical%20legacies.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3EHarshvardhan%20is%20a%20student%20of%20history%20and%20political%20science%20in%20Christ%20University%2C%20Bengaluru.%20His%20email%20is%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eharshs31vardhan%40gmail.com.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694675454000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F20123532%2FIMG_2186.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fhow-indian-is-india-and-other-considerations%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20government's%20recent%20focus%20on%20revising%20various%20aspects%20of%20the%20country%2C%20from%20parliamentary%20buildings%20to%20legal%20codes%20(and%20now%20the%20very%20name)%2C%20has%20raised%20concerns%20about%20its%20intentions%20and%20the%20potential%20implications%20for%20India's%20democratic%20and%20secular%20character.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fhow-indian-is-india-and-other-considerations%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Cipla%20foundi