sco%20had%20expressed%20concern%20over%20the%20handling%20of%20the%20case.%20The%20video%20shows%20officer%20Daniel%20Auderer%20laughing%20about%20the%20deadly%20crash%20and%20saying%20there%20was%20no%20need%20for%20a%20criminal%20investigation%20against%20his%20colleague%20Kevin%20Dave%2C%20who%20was%20driving%20the%20car.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20was%20Jaahnavi%20Kandula%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%2023-year-old%20was%20from%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20and%20pursuing%20a%20master's%20degree%20from%20the%20Northeastern%20University%20campus%20in%20South%20Lake%20Union.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20went%20to%20the%20US%20from%20Bengaluru%20on%20a%20student%20exchange%20programme%20in%202021%20and%20was%20due%20to%20graduate%20this%20December.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMs%20Kandula's%20family%20is%20deeply%20distressed%20by%20the%20revelations.%20Her%20grandfather%20told%20NDTV%20that%20the%20family%20had%20not%20recovered%20from%20loss%20and%20the%20policeman's%20behaviour%20makes%20it%20worse.%20%26quot%3BHow%20can%20anyone%20speak%20like%20that%20after%20a%20tragic%20accident%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20happened%20on%20January%2023%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EMs%20Kandula%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-cop-caught-on-tape-laughing-after-indian-student-killed-in-accident-probe-launched-4385167%5C%22%3Ehit%20and%20killed%20by%20a%20police%20car%3C%2Fa%3E%20while%20crossing%20the%20street.%20According%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%C2%A0Seattle%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Kevin%20Dave%2C%20the%20police%20officer%20driving%20the%20car%20was%20going%20119%20kmph%20and%20the%20graduate%20student's%20body%20was%20thrown%20more%20than%20100%20feet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMs%20Kandula%20was%20taken%20to%20Harbourview%20Medical%20Centre%2C%20but%20died%20due%20to%20her%20injuries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20the%20police%20officer%20on%20the%20scene%20reacted%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.seattletimes.com%2Fseattle-news%2Flaw-justice%2Finvestigation-launched-into-tape-of-seattle-police-guild-leaders-downplaying-death-of-woman-struck-by-officer%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3ESeattle%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20that%20officer%20Auderer%20was%20called%20to%20the%20scene%20and%20his%20body%20camera%20recorded%20audio%20from%20a%20call%20he%20made%20to%20a%20colleague.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20she%20is%20dead%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20officer%20is%20heard%20saying%20before%20laughing.%20%26quot%3BNo%2C%20it's%20a%20regular%20person.%20Yeah%2C%20just%20write%20a%20cheque%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says%2C%20before%20laughing%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEleven%20thousand%20dollars.%20She%20was%2026%2C%20anyway.%20She%20had%20limited%20value.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20Seattle%20Police%20Department%20released%20the%20footage%20on%20Monday%2C%20it%20led%20to%20outrage%20on%20social%20media.%20%26quot%3BSue%20the%20Police%20department...that's%20how%20they%20will%20learn%20to%20respect%20dead%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20user%20said%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20this%20was%20an%20American%20citizen%20killed%20on%20Indian%20soil%20then%20USA%20would%20have%20shaken%20up%20Indian%20government%20to%20the%20roots!%20Those%20policemen%20should%20be%20punished%20in%20prison%20or%20their%20licence%20should%20be%20permanently%20suspended%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20another.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20officer%20Audrer%20said%20after%20the%20outrage%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EOfficer%20Auderer%20said%20his%20comments%20were%20taken%20out%20of%20context.%20Jason%20Rantz%2C%20a%20radio%20host%2C%20said%20he%20has%20a%20written%20statement%20from%20the%20police%20officer%20saying%20his%20comments%20were%20meant%20to%20mimic%20how%20city%20attorneys%20might%20try%20to%20minimise%20liability%20for%20the%20woman's%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Mr%20Kandula's%20family%20is%20surprised%20why%20this%20information%20was%20not%20revealed%20earlier.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20lost%20our%20child%20but%20this%20is%20beyond%20shocking%2C%26quot%3B%20her%20grandfather%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694674980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fs8bsp748_jaahnavi-kandula-tribute-1200_625x300_14_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Fwho-was-jaahnavi-kandula-indian-student-killed-by-police-vehicle-in-us-4388521%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Jaahnavi%20Kandula%20was%20hit%20and%20killed%20by%20a%20police%20car%20while%20crossing%20the%20street%20in%20Seattle%20on%20January%2023%20this%20year.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Fwho-was-jaahnavi-kandula-indian-student-killed-by-police-vehicle-in-us-4388521%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Fwho-was-jaahnavi-kandula-indian-student-killed-by-police-vehicle-in-us-4388521%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Fwho-was-jaahnavi-kandula-indian-student-killed-by-police-vehicle-in-us-4388521%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Warning%20Issued%20After%20UK%20Woman's%20Death%20Following%20Butt%20Lift%20In%20Turkey%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20coroner%20in%20the%20UK%20will%20write%20to%20the%20Health%20Secretary%20over%20risks%20associated%20with%20having%20cosmetic%20surgeries%20abroad%20after%20a%20British%20woman%20died%20following%20a%20buttock%20enlargement%20surgery%20in%20Turkey.%20Notably%2C%C2%A0Melissa%20Kerr%20died%20at%20the%20Medicana%20Kadikoy%20Hospital%20in%20Istanbul%20last%20year%20on%20November%2019%2C%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fmelissa-kerr-british-womans-death-after-brazilian-butt-lift-in-turkey-prompts-coroners-warning-12959896%5C%22%3ESky%20News%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%C2%A0The%2031-year-old%20died%20on%20the%20day%20she%20had%20the%20Brazilian%20butt%20lift%20procedure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20investigation%20into%20her%20death%20also%20revealed%20that%20she%20was%20given%20''limited%20information%20regarding%20the%20risks%20and%20mortality%20rate''%20of%20the%20surgery%2C%20as%20per%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmetro.co.uk%2F2023%2F09%2F12%2Fwoman-31-who-died-after-brazilian-butt-lift-not-made-aware-of-the-risks-19488591%2F%5C%22%3EMetro%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20this%20surgery%2C%20fat%20is%20harvested%20from%20other%20parts%20of%20the%20body%20and%20injected%20into%20the%20buttocks.%20In%20the%20case%20of%20Ms%20Kerr%2C%20the%20injected%20fat%20entered%20a%20vein%20before%20moving%20and%20blocking%20her%20pulmonary%20artery.%C2%A0Norfolk's%20senior%20coroner%20Jackeline%20Lake%20said%20her%20cause%20of%20death%20was%20a%20pulmonary%20thromboembolism.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMs%20Lake%20said%20she%20would%20be%20writing%20a%20report%20for%20the%20health%20secretary%20to%20try%20and%20prevent%20further%20deaths%20from%20this%20''risky''%20procedure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20case%2C%20Ms.%20Lake%20said%2C%20''Ms.%20Kerr%20wasn't%20seen%20by%20a%20surgeon%20or%20clinician%20prior%20to%20the%20date%20of%20the%20procedure%20and%20underwent%20a%20limited%20assessment%20prior%20to%20the%20procedures.%20There%20has%20been%20the%20release%20of%20an%20international%20alert%20to%20surgeons%20regarding%20the%20high%20mortality%20rate%20associated%20with%20this%20procedure.%20There%20has%20also%20been%20the%20introduction%20of%20a%20voluntary%20moratorium%20on%20this%20type%20of%20procedure%20in%20the%20UK.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20added%2C%20''These%20are%20clearly%20not%20being%20followed%20in%20Turkey.%20I'm%20concerned%20patients%20are%20not%20being%20made%20aware%20of%20the%20risks%20or%20the%20mortality%20rate%20associated%20with%20such%20surgery.%20I%20do%20have%20concerns%20there%20will%20be%20future%20deaths%20and%20I'm%20of%20the%20view%20future%20deaths%20can%20be%20prevented%20by%20way%20of%20better%20information.''%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20plastic%20surgeon%20Simon%20Withey%2C%20who%20was%20asked%20to%20prepare%20a%20report%20for%20Ms%20Kerr's%20inquest%20said%20the%20death%20rate%20associated%20with%20Brazilian%20butt%20lifts%20is%20''likely%20to%20be%20in%20excess%20of%20one%20in%204%2C000''.%20He%20added%20it%20is%20''quite%20possible''%20that%2C%20if%20the%20risk%20of%20the%20procedure%20had%20been%20explained%20to%20Ms.%20Kerr%20''before%20she%20was%20financially%20committed%20to%20proceed%2C%20she%20would%20not%20have%20done''.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20few%20WhatsApp%20messages%20between%20Melissa%C2%A0and%20a%20hospital%20worker%20in%20Tukey%20have%20also%20been%20released.%20in%20one%20of%20her%20messages%2C%C2%A0she%20said%20that%20she%20felt%20''a%20bit%20nervous''%2C%20and%20also%20asked%20for%20pictures%20of%20previous%20patients%20which%20she%20was%20not%20provided.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%C2%A0Ms%20Kerr%20also%20had%20breast%20enlargement%20surgery%20a%20decade%20earlier%20without%20complications.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694674860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-11%2F8spd4m3g_the-mother-persuaded-her-daughter-to-get-a-double-eyelid-procedure_625x300_16_November_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwarning-issued-after-uk-womans-death-following-brazilian-butt-lift-surgery-in-turkey-4388482%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22An%20investigation%20into%20her%20death%20also%20revealed%20that%20she%20was%20given%20''limited%20information%20regarding%20the%20risks%20and%20mortality%20rate''%20of%20the%20surgery.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwarning-issued-after-uk-womans-death-following-brazilian-butt-lift-surgery-in-turkey-4388482%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3