C%20urban%20%E2%80%98elite%E2%80%99%20were%20fewer%20in%20number%20and%20the%20masses%20many%20%E2%80%93%20naturally%2C%20the%20distributors%20preferred%20movies%20made%20keeping%20the%20latter%20in%20mind%2C%20with%20all%20the%20masala%20ingredients%20thrown%20in.%20Gentry%20was%20a%20code%20word%20for%20obscure%2C%20slow%2C%20arty%20kind%20of%20films%2C%20i.e.%20the%20ones%20that%20would%20appeal%20to%20very%20few.%20It%20was%20also%20assumed%20that%20there%20would%20be%20no%20cross%20over%20audiences%20and%20that%20the%20raucous%20front%20bencher%20types%20would%20not%20bother%20to%20see%20an%20arty%20film%20and%20the%20intelligentsia%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20care%20to%20hoot%20or%20dance%20in%20the%20aisles%20in%20film%20with%20eight%20songs%20and%20dances.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EVery%20few%20stars%20crossed%20over%20either%2C%20especially%20from%20the%20mass%20to%20the%20art%2C%20though%20a%20few%20forayed%20the%20other%20way%20round%2C%20with%20varying%20degrees%20of%20success%2C%20Naseeruddin%20Shah%20and%20Shabana%20Azmi%20among%20them.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShahrukh%20Khan%20has%20done%20the%20impossible%20%E2%80%93%20he%20is%20loved%20by%20the%20mass%20audiences%20and%20within%20that%2C%20across%20age%20groups%20and%20genders.%20He%20is%20loved%20in%20the%20small%20towns%20and%20in%20the%20metros.%20He%20is%20loved%20by%20the%20well-off%20and%20the%20middle%20classes%2C%20by%20those%20in%20fancy%20apartments%20and%20in%20more%20modest%20dwellings.%20The%20gentry%20and%20the%20%3Cem%3Ejanata%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Most%20crucially%2C%20he%20has%20breached%20that%20one%20barrier%20that%20stars%20from%20another%20generation%20did%20not%20%E2%80%93%20the%20high-minded%20intelligentsia%2C%20which%20between%20writing%20serious%20papers%20and%20op-eds%20about%20the%20state%20of%20the%20nation%2C%20also%20queues%20up%20for%20his%20films.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHis%20latest%20film%20%3Cem%3EJawan%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20a%20bit%20earlier%2C%20his%20last%2C%20%3Cem%3EPathaan%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20both%20showed%20that%20Khan%2C%20even%20as%20he%20approaches%20his%2060s%2C%20is%20still%20the%20nation%E2%80%99s%20favourite%2C%20much%20more%20than%20his%20two%20contemporaries.%20Salman%20Khan%2C%20%E2%80%98Bhai%E2%80%99%20to%20his%20legions%20of%20fans%2C%20has%20virtually%20no%20fandom%20among%20the%20%E2%80%98gentry%E2%80%99%20and%20Aamir%20Khan%2C%20who%20was%20fun%20to%20watch%20in%20the%20beginning%2C%20has%20now%20turned%20so%20serious%20and%20meticulous%20in%20preparing%20for%20his%20roles%2C%20is%20in%20danger%20of%20becoming%20plain%20boring.%20Which%20leaves%20Shah%20Rukh%20Khan%20ahead%20of%20the%20field.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShah%20Rukh%20Khan%20knows%20this%20and%20in%20both%20the%20films%2C%20more%20so%20in%20%3Cem%3EJawan%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20has%20pressed%20all%20the%20right%20buttons.%20%3Cem%3EPathaan%3C%2Fem%3E%20was%20not%20just%20an%20action%20film%2C%20inspired%20heavily%20from%20Bourne%20and%20Bond%2C%20but%20had%20heavy%20dollops%20of%20nationalism%20thrown%20in.%20More%20important%2C%20it%20was%20the%20first%20film%20after%20that%20sordid%20episode%20of%20his%20son%E2%80%99s%20arrest%20for%20allegedly%20carrying%20drugs%2C%20which%20soon%20unravelled%20as%20a%20trumped%20up%20charge.%20His%20son%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Findia%2Fstory%2Faryan-khan-arrest-comes-back-to-bite-officers-who-probed-case-heres-what-you-need-to-know-2378423-2023-05-12%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eeventually%20came%20out%20unscathed%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20but%20it%20must%20have%20been%20a%20difficult%20time%20for%20his%20family.%20Khan%20had%20chosen%20not%20to%20say%20anything%20during%20that%20period%2C%20which%20endeared%20him%20to%20his%20fans%20and%20when%20%3Cem%3EPathaan%3C%2Fem%3E%20opened%2C%20they%20thronged%20to%20show%20their%20admiration.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffilm%2Fsrk-i-hear-you-and-so-does-everyone-else%5C%22%3ESRK%2C%20I%20Hear%20You.%20And%20So%20Does%20Everyone%20Else.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESocial%20media%20was%20full%20of%20Indians%20all%20over%20the%20world%20declaring%20that%20they%20had%20seen%20the%20film%20and%20posing%20outside%20theatres.%20It%20was%20all%20about%20Khan%20and%20showing%20solidarity%20with%20him%2C%20a%20kind%20of%20Revenge%20Watching%20phenomenon.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EJawan%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20the%20goodwill%20for%20him%20continues%2C%20though%20the%20impulses%20are%20different.%20Khan%20has%20much%20more%20control%2C%20since%20it%20has%20been%20made%20by%20his%20own%20company%20Red%20Chillies%20Entertainment.%20The%20director%20Atlee%2C%20is%20from%20the%20southern%20film%20industry%2C%20where%20the%20movies%20have%20a%20particular%20visual%20and%20creative%20language%2C%20which%20has%20developed%20national%20appeal.%20And%20the%20director%20has%20risen%20to%20the%20occasion%20%E2%80%93%20he%20has%20thrown%20in%20everything%20in%20the%20film%20to%20come%20up%20with%20one%20spicy%20mix%20after%20another%2C%20including%20a%20surprise%20guest%20star%20and%20unrelenting%20action.%20(And%20a%20not-so-sly%20dig%20about%20the%20Aryan%20Khan%20case%2C%20where%20he%20declares%20that%20to%20harm%20his%20son%2C%20his%20enemies%20will%20first%20have%20to%20take%20on%20the%20father).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAlong%20with%20that%20are%20the%20direct%20references%2C%20with%20virtuous%20intent%2C%20to%20contemporary%20events.%20Farmers%20strike%3F%20Check.%20Corruption%3F%20Another%20check.%20Responsible%20voting%3F%20A%20big%20check.%20It%20is%20enough%20the%20warm%20the%20cockles%20of%20a%20progressive%E2%80%99s%20heart%2C%20and%20it%20has.%20And%20this%20undoubtedly%20is%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20doing%2C%20because%20he%20knows%20that%20its%20all%20very%20well%20to%20win%20over%20the%20%3Cem%3Ejanata%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20but%20also%20crucial%20to%20keep%20the%20culturati%20PLUs%20on%20his%20side%20too.%20Is%20it%20sincere%20or%20dishonest%20or%20manipulative%3F%20Probably%20a%20bit%20of%20everything%2C%20but%20it%20seems%20to%20have%20done%20its%20job%2C%20because%20this%20time%20round%2C%20both%20in%20the%20newspapers%20and%20on%20social%20media%2C%20this%20cohort%20is%20full%20of%20oohs%20and%20aahs%20about%20him%20and%20the%20movie.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20all%20this%20is%20on%20the%20screen%2C%20where%20all%20kinds%20of%20liberties%20can%20be%20taken.%20In%20real%20life%20one%20has%20to%20be%20tuned%20to%20some%20hard%20realities.%20This%20is%20particularly%20true%20for%20celebrities%20and%20film%20stars%20in%20contemporary%20India%2C%20where%20powerful%20figures%20on%20the%20one%20hand%2C%20and%20trolls%20on%20the%20other%2C%20keep%20an%20eye%20for%20what%20they%20say.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERecently%2C%20even%20as%20his%20film%20with%20all%20that%20messaging%20started%20drawing%20huge%20audiences%2C%20Khan%20tweeted%2C%20%E2%80%9CCongratulations%20to%20Hon.%20PM%20%40narendramodi%20ji%20for%20the%20success%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20G20%20Presidency%20and%20for%20fostering%20unity%20between%20nations%20for%20a%20better%20future%20for%20the%20people%20of%20the%20world.%20It%20has%20brought%20in%20a%20sense%20of%20honour%20and%20pride%20into%20the%20hearts%20of%20every%20Indian.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3ECongratulations%20to%20Hon.%20PM%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnarendramodi%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40narendramodi%3C%2Fa%3E%20ji%20for%20the%20success%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20G20%20Presidency%20and%20for%20fostering%20unity%20between%20nations%20for%20a%20better%20future%20for%20the%20people%20of%20the%20world.%3Cbr%3EIt%20has%20brought%20in%20a%20sense%2