12img14_Dec_2022_PTI12_14_2022_000063B.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20Opposition%20has%20submitted%20a%20list%20of%2016%20domain%20experts%20to%20the%20parliamentary%20standing%20committee%20on%20home%20affairs%20which%20is%20examining%20the%20three%20new%20criminal%20law%20Bills%20meant%20to%20replace%20existing%20colonial-era%20criminal%20law%20codes%20in%20India%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fopposition-submits-list-of-16-domain-experts-to-be-called-by-panel-examining-new-criminal-laws%2Farticle67303505.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%20%3C%2Fem%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESenior%20advocate%20Fali%20S.%20Nariman%2C%20former%20Chief%20Justice%20U.U.%20Lalit%2C%20and%20Justice%20Madan%20Lokur%2C%20a%20former%20Supreme%20Court%20judge%2C%20are%20among%20the%20list%20of%20names%20proposed%20by%20the%20opposition.%20The%20opposition%20suggested%20that%20the%20new%20Bills%20should%20be%20examined%20thoroughly%20by%20a%20set%20of%20experts%2C%20including%20Supreme%20Court%20and%20high%20court%20judges%2C%20members%20of%20Bar%20Councils%2C%20legal%20scholars%2C%20prison%20officials%20and%20reform%20activists%2C%20ethnic%20and%20religious%20leaders%2C%20as%20well%20as%20cybercrime%20experts%2C%20among%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnion%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fsedition-law-repealed-three-new-bills-tabled-in-parliament-to-replace-criminal-laws%5C%22%3Ehad%20introduced%3C%2Fa%3E%20three%20new%20Bills%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%3A%20the%20Bharatiya%20Nyaya%20Sanhita%20(BNS)%20Bill%2C%202023%20to%20replace%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%2C%201860%3B%20the%20Bharatiya%20Nagarik%20Suraksha%20Sanhita%20Bill%20(BNSS)%2C%202023%20to%20replace%20the%20Code%20of%20Criminal%20Procedure%2C%201898%3B%20and%20the%20Bharatiya%20Sakhshya%20Bill%20(BSB)%2C%202023%20to%20replace%20Indian%20Evidence%20Act%2C%201872.%20The%20Bills%20were%20introduced%20on%20the%20last%20day%20of%20the%20monsoon%20session%20of%20the%20parliament%2C%20on%20August%2011.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20has%20set%20out%20a%20three-month%20period%20for%20the%20parliamentary%20standing%20committee%20to%20examine%20the%20new%20Bills%20before%20the%20government%20can%20get%20them%20passed%20in%20the%20winter%20session%20of%20the%20parliament.%20The%20parliament%20committee%2C%20headed%20by%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20MP%20Brijlal%2C%20consists%20of%2027%20MPs%20from%20various%20political%20parties%20from%20both%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20Rajya%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20Bills%20were%20tabled%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20by%20the%20government%2C%20the%20opposition%20has%20raised%20alarm%2C%20stating%20that%20the%20government%20is%20trying%20to%20rush%20the%20Bills%20through%20parliament%20without%20adequate%20consultation%20and%20transparency.%20Although%20Shah%20claimed%20to%20have%20undertaken%20a%20%E2%80%9Ccomprehensive%20consultation%E2%80%9D%20process%20before%20tabling%20the%20Bills%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20the%20opposition%20is%20not%20convinced.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20opposition%20MP%20on%20the%20panel%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20going%20by%20the%20current%20pace%20of%20scrutiny%2C%20it%20would%20take%20at%20least%20one%20and%20a%20half%20years%20to%20go%20through%20the%20new%20Bills.%20%E2%80%9CThese%20legislations%20will%20impact%20the%20poorest%20of%20poor%20and%20still%20we%20are%20rushing%20through%20them%20without%20paying%20the%20due%20attention%2C%20which%20is%20very%20unfortunate%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20the%20newspaper.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20opposition%20MPs%20on%20the%20panel%20also%20alleged%20that%20they%20are%20not%20being%20given%20an%20opportunity%20to%20voice%20their%20views%20on%20the%20Bills%2C%20and%20also%20raised%20concern%20over%20the%20way%20minutes%20of%20the%20meetings%20are%20being%20recorded.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fhow-consultative-was-the-framing-of-the-three-criminal-law-bills-really%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20earlier%2C%20another%20committee%20whose%20recommendations%20ultimately%20culminated%20in%20the%20present%20form%20of%20the%20Bills%20has%20operated%20in%20complete%20secrecy%20ever%20since%20its%20constitution%20in%20May%202020.%20The%20committee%20also%20agreed%20to%20the%20involvement%20of%20non-members%20in%20shaping%20the%20recommendations%20for%20the%20Bills%20and%20the%20home%20ministry%20violated%20a%20statutory%20law%20to%20keep%20away%20any%20information%20related%20to%20the%20task.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESources%20had%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Ccrucial%20behind-the-scenes%20role%E2%80%9D%20was%20played%20by%20the%20solicitor%20general%20of%20India%2C%20Tushar%20Mehta%2C%20and%20the%20additional%20solicitor%20general%20of%20India%20(ASG)%2C%20Suryaprakash%20V.%20Raju%2C%20in%20making%20recommendations%20and%20framing%20the%20three%20Bills%20despite%20them%20not%20being%20part%20of%20the%20committee.%20Raju%2C%20who%20practiced%20at%20the%20Gujarat%20high%20court%20until%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fsv-raju-appointed-additional-solicitor-general-of-sc-6482332%2F%5C%22%3Eappointment%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0as%20ASG%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20in%20July%202020%2C%20had%20represented%20Shah%20in%20the%20Sohrabuddin%20encounter%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Committee%20for%20Reforms%20in%20Criminal%20Laws%20(CRCL)%20was%20constituted%20on%20May%204%2C%202020%2C%20and%20none%20of%20its%20recommendations%20have%20been%20put%20in%20the%20public%20domain%20so%20far.%20Despite%20the%20all-important%20nature%20of%20its%20work%2C%20the%20committee%E2%80%99s%20workings%20have%20been%20kept%20secret%2C%20highlighting%20the%20lack%20of%20transparency%20in%20its%20functioning%20and%20the%20process%20it%20followed.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694670374000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F12%2F14153018%2F2022_12img14_Dec_2022_PTI12_14_2022_000063B.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fnew-criminal-bills-opposition-submits-list-of-16-domain-experts-to-parl-panel-for-eliciting-views%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Senior%20advocate%20Fali%20S.%20Nariman%20and%20former%20Chief%20Justice%20U.U.%20Lalit%20are%20among%20the%20list%20of%20names%20proposed%20by%20the%20opposition.%20The%20opposition%20has%20accused%20the%20government%20of%20trying%20to%20rush%20the%20Bills%20through%20parliament%20without%20adequate%20consultation.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fnew-criminal-bills-opposition-submits-list-of-16-domain-experts-to-parl-panel-for-eliciting-views%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kolkata%20Police%20uses%20SRK's%20%E2%80%98Jawan%E2%80%99%20look%20to%20promote%20road%20safety%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694668853000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-103652473%2Cimgsize-57708.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fbengali%2Fmovies%2Fnews%2Fkolkata-police-uses-shah-rukh-khans-bandaged-look-in-jawan-to-promote-road-safety%2Farticleshow%2F103652393.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Shah%20Rukh%20Khan's%20'Jawan'%2C%20featuring%20his%20popular%20bandaged%20look%2C%20has%20sparked%20a%20viral%20trend%20inspiring%20road%20safety%20messages.%20Kolkata%20Police%20shared%20a%20poster%20with%20SRK%20riding%20without%20a%20helmet%20next%20to%20his%20'Jawan'%20character%2C%20emphasizing%20helmet%20use.%20Eastern%20Railway%20used%20SRK's%20image%20to%20caution%20against%20leaning%20on%20train%20doors.%20New%20Delhi%20Police%20and%20UP%20Police%20also%20adopted%20this%20trend%20to%20promote%20road%20safety.%20'Jawan'%20has%20shattered%20box%20office%20records%2C%20earning%20over%20Rs%20600%20crore%20globally%2C%20marking%20a%20historic%20first-week%20total%20for%20a%20Hindi%20film.%20It%20continues%20to%20soar%2C%20poised%20to%20cross%20Rs%20700%20crore.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22etimes.in%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A12%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fbengali%2Fmovies%2Fnews%2Fkolkata-police-uses-shah-rukh-khans-bandaged-look-in-jawan-to-promote-road-safety%2Farticleshow%2F103652393.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20Beloved%20Publishing%20House%20and%20a%20Business%20Model%20of%20Impulsive%20Ethics%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F14103916%2F266377862_6529640610410462_3805678544101550645_n.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMoney%20takes%20on%20a%20different%20kind%20of%20tyranny%20over%20most%20people%2C%E2%80%9D%20translator%20and%20editor%20Anjum%20Katyal%20says%20in%20Pushan%20Kripalani%E2%80%99s%20documentary%2C%20%3Cem%3EOf%20the%20Book%20and%20Other%20Stories.%20%3C%2Fem%3EThe%20film%20is%20on%20Seagull%2C%20the%20independent%20publisher%20known%20for%20its%20exquisite%20books%20and%20cerebral%20catalogue%20that%20completed%2040%20years%20in%20the%20business%20in%202022.%20The%20idea%20for%20Kripalani%E2%80%99s%20film%20was%20seeded%20at%20the%2040th%20anniversary%20celebrations%20of%20Seagull%2C%20and%20took%20a%20few%20more%20months%20to%20complete%20%E2%80%93%20by%20which%20time%20Seagull%20completed%20its%2041st%20year%20in%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKatyal%20is%20speaking%20of%20Naveen%20Kishore%2C%20the%20theatre%20lighting%20practitioner%2C%20photographer%2C%20poet%20and%20publisher%20of%20Seagull%20who%20founded%20the%20publishing%20house%20in%201982.%20%E2%80%9CHe%E2%80%99s%20got%20a%20different%20way%20of%20thinking%20about%20money.%20We%E2%80%99re%20scared%2C%20we%E2%80%99re%20conservative%2C%20we%20need%20the%20back-up%2C%20we%20need%20the%20security%E2%80%A6It%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20bother%20him.%20It%20would%20bother%20me%20a%20lot%2C%20I%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20sleep%20at%20night%2C%20thinking%20that%20I%20have%20to%20do%20this%2C%20do%20that%2C%20pay%20him%20back%2C%E2%80%9D%20Katyal%20says.%20She%20would%20know.%20She%20was%20Seagull%E2%80%99s%20chief%20editor%20for%20close%20to%20two%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20subject%20of%20money%20comes%20up%20some%20nine%20times%20in%20the%20111-minute%20film.%20Kishore%20brings%20it%20up%20four%20or%20five%20times%20himself.%20His%20colleague%20and%20senior%20editor%20Sunandini%20Banerjee%2C%20also%20known%20for%20her%20startling%20book%20cover%20design%2C%20mentions%20it%20twice.%20The%20quizzing%20tycoon%20Siddharth%20Basu%2C%20who%20brought%20the%20international%20MasterMind%20and%20Who%20Wants%20to%20Be%20a%20Millionaire%20to%20India%20with%20terrific%20success%2C%20mentions%20it%20once.%20Katyal%20mentions%20it%20in%20her%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20this%20is%20apposite.%20For%20the%20last%20several%20years%20when%20I%20have%20identified%20myself%20as%20a%20Seagull%20fan%2C%20I%20have%20been%20told%20of%20the%20publishing%20house%E2%80%99s%20secret%20trust%20fund%20that%20actually%20enables%20them%20to%20stay%20in%20business.%20Or%20Kishore%E2%80%99s%20enormous%20side%20business%20in%20art%20and%20artist%20representation%2C%20always%20mentioned%20with%20a%20dismissive%20air%20or%20a%20wave%20of%20the%20hand%2C%20implying%20something%20amiss%20or%20underhand.%20Another%20story%20is%20that%20Seagull%20is%20a%20front%20for%20the%20American%20government%E2%80%99s%20philanthropic%20organisations.%20Yet%20another%20goes%20that%20Kishore%E2%80%99s%20father%20was%20wealthy%2C%20%E2%80%98a%20hotelier%E2%80%99.%20And%20sometimes%2C%20the%20story%20is%20that%20Seagull%20is%20about%20to%20fold%20up.%20%E2%80%98It%E2%80%99s%20incredible%20that%20they%20managed%20for%20as%20long%20as%20they%20have!%E2%80%99%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20film%2C%20Kishore%20reveals%20his%20secret.%20When%20he%20entered%20college%2C%20his%20father%20had%20an%20unfortunate%20spate%20of%20being%20in%20and%20out%20of%20jobs.%20Kishore%20started%20working%20for%20a%20motor%20parts%20company%20where%20his%20work%20was%20composing%20letters%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20firm%20and%20his%20salary%20was%20Rs%2065.%20His%20college%20fee%20was%20Rs%2019.%20With%20the%20remaining%2C%20he%20played%20cards%20for%20money%2C%20making%20an%20average%20of%20Rs%20700-800%20a%20month%20that%20he%20handed%20over%20to%20his%20mother%20for%20the%20household.%20This%20continued%20for%20a%20period%20of%2013%20months%20until%20his%20father%20got%20a%20stable%20job%20for%20another%20year.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20a%20strange%20time%2C%20but%20what%20that%20probably%20did%20was%20make%20me%20comfortable%20with%20risk.%E2%80%9D%20Incidentally%2C%20Kishore%E2%80%99s%20father%20was%20indeed%20in%20the%20hotel%20business%20%E2%80%93%20he%20worked%20as%20a%20manager%20with%20the%20Oberoi%E2%80%99s.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FxZ56DEyO50M%3Fsi%3DQeze_8UVO1Wfxp8u%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C%22%3E%EF%BB%BF%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EMoney%20runs%20through%20the%20film%20as%20a%20thread%2C%20and%20this%20is%20refreshing.%20Publishing%20as%20a%20business%20is%20opaque%20about%20financials%20%E2%80%93%20in%20the%20public%20domain%2C%20we%20tend%20to%20hear%20that%20things%20are%20tough%20and%20there%20is%20no%20money%20in%20books.%20Yet%2C%20the%20image%20of%20publishing%20in%20the%20media%20is%20glamorous%20%E2%80%93%20photographs%20of%20events%20in%20literary%20festivals%20and%20well-appointed%20hotels%20with%20wine%20and%20nice%20things.%20It%20solidifies%20the%20impression%20that%20publishing%20is%20a%20mysterious%20business%20meant%20for%20a%20chosen%20few.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKripalani%E2%80%99s%20film%20does%20not%20give%20a%20price%20breakdown%20of%20how%20a%20Seagull%20book%20adds%20up%20%E2%80%93%20how%20much%20a%20writer%20is%20paid%2C%20how%20much%20the%20printing%20costs%2C%20what%20the%20marketing%20budget%20is%2C%20none%20of%20that.%20But%20it%20does%20take%20you%20into%20the%20calculation%20of%20how%20Seagull%20approaches%20a%20book%20project.%20When%20Nemai%20Ghosh%2C%20who%20made%20a%20name%20for%20himself%20as%20the%20still%20photographer%20for%20Satyajit%20Ray%E2%80%99s%20films%2C%20wanted%20to%20publish%20his%20lifelong%20work%20in%20theatre%20photography%2C%20he%20had%20approached%20a%20few%20publishers.%20Photographs%20are%20expensive%20to%20publish%20well%2C%20so%20it%20was%20not%20an%20easy%20call.%20Kishore%E2%80%99s%20thought%20was%3A%20this%20person%20has%20paid%20their%20dues%2C%20as%20it%20were%2C%20through%20their%20work.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20you%20take%20on%20a%20book%20like%20this%2C%20you%20say%20no%20to%20the%20possibility%20of%20eight%20other%20books%20which%20are%20textual%20and%20perhaps%20just%20as%20vital.%20But%20you%20can%20make%20it%20possible%20that%20this%20particular%20person%20does%20not%20have%20to%20go%20to%20six%20other%20publishers%20hawking%20a%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%20in%20the%20film.%20Ghosh%E2%80%99s%20book%20%3Cem%3EDramatic%20Moments%3A%20Photographs%20and%20Memories%20of%20Calcutta%20Theatre%20from%20the%201960s%20to%20the%201990s%3C%2Fem%3E%20was%20published%20in%202000%20as%20a%20191-page%20hardbound%20book%20priced%20at%20Rs%20900.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20this%20is%2C%20is%20a%20different%20way%20of%20doing%20business.%20Kishore%20does%20the%20financial%20math%20%E2%80%93%20one%20book%20of%20photographs%20costs%20the%20equivalent%20of%20eight%20other%20books.%20But%20he%20also%20does%20another%20math%20%E2%80%93%20how%20can%20we%20give%20a%20man%20with%20a%20lifetime%E2%80%99s%20worth%20of%20work%20their%20due%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20note%20about%20the%20film%2C%20Kripalani%20himself%20says%20he%20was%20%E2%80%9Coverwhelmed%20by%20talk%20of%20distribution%2C%20strategies%2C%20market%20forces%2C%20bottom%20lines%E2%80%9D%20after%20finishing%20a%20feature%20film.%20This%20film%20%3Cem%3EGoldfish%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20a%20superbly%20written%20and%20realised%20drama%20about%20the%20repairing%20of%20a%20relationship%20between%20an%20ageing%20mother%20and%20an%20angry%20daughter%2C%20released%20in%20theatres%20in%20September%20this%20year.%20Kripalani%20is%2C%20in%20a%20way%2C%20a%20child%20of%20Seagull.%20His%20parents%2C%20the%20actors%20Jayant%20and%20Gulan%20Kripalani%2C%20are%20friends%20of%20Kishore.%20He%20was%20drawn%20to%20making%20a%20film%20on%20Seagull%20because%20they%20seemed%20to%20have%20a%20different%20metric%20of%20success.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20did%20not%20seem%20to%20look%20at%20a%20feasibility%20study%20before%20they%20made%20a%20decision.%20They%20jumped.%20And%20then%20looked%20around%20for%20a%20parachute.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F14104101%2FFzoFKQmXoAA9Tvo.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F14104101%2FFzoFKQmXoAA9Tvo.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F14104101%2FFzoFKQmXoAA9Tvo-300x169.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F14104101%2FFzoFKQmXoAA9Tvo-1024x576.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-672959%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22675%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EStills%20from%20%E2%80%98Of%20the%20Book%20and%20Other%20Stories%E2%80%99.%20Photo%3A%20X%2F%40seagullbooks%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20film%2C%20Kishore%E2%80%99s%20story%20about%20a%20Nobel-winning%20author%20offers%20an%20almost%20fairytale-like%20example%20of%20the%20Seagull%20way%20of%20doing%20business.%20The%20prize%20announcement%20for%20Mo%20Yan%20came%20around%20the%20Frankfurt%20Book%20Fair%2C%20known%20to%20be%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20largest%20book%20trade%20fair.%20Seagull%20owned%20the%20rights%20for%20all%20languages%2C%20and%20they%20sold%20rights%20for%2032%20territories%20after%20the%20Nobel%20announcement%2C%20sales%20worth%20132%2C000%20euros.%20Seagull%20decided%20to%20pay%20the%20author%2050%25%20of%20what%20they%20earned%2C%20instead%20of%20the%20percentage%20drawn%20up%20in%20the%20contract%20years%20ago.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20an%20intuitive%20act%20of%20%E2%80%98Hey%2C%20things%20would%20have%20been%20different%20if%20I%20had%20contracted%20you%20today.%E2%80%99%20It%20may%20seem%20very%20romantic%20and%20goody-goody%E2%80%A6But%20it%E2%80%99s%20nice%20to%20be%20able%20to%20do%20this%20percentage%20sharing%20differently%20because%20eventually%2C%20money%20is%20a%20conduit.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20likely%20the%20kind%20of%20thinking%20that%20has%20allowed%20Seagull%2C%20a%20publishing%20house%20with%20six%20editorial%20employees%20(as%20of%20the%20moment)%2C%20to%20develop%20a%20catalogue%20of%20more%20than%20600%20titles%2C%20including%20five%20Nobel%20Prize%20winners%20(Mo%20Yan%2C%20Imre%20Ketesz%2C%20Peter%20Handke%2C%20Elfriede%20Jelinek%2C%20Herta%20Muller)%2C%20one%20alternative%20Nobel%20winner%20(Mary%20Condse)%2C%20the%20rockstar%20academics%20Gayatri%20Chakravorty%20Spivak%2C%20Romila%20Thapar%20and%20Judith%20Butler%2C%20and%20the%20legendary%20writer-activist%20Mahasweta%20Devi.%20It%20began%20as%20a%20publishing%20house%20for%20theatre%2C%20cinema%20and%20the%20visual%20arts.%20But%20sometime%20in%20the%20early%202000s%2C%20Seagull%20pivoted%20to%20translations%20of%20world%20literature%20%E2%80%93%20not%20merely%20the%20French%20and%20German%20%E2%80%93%20a%20good%20decade%20and%20a%20half%20before%20the%20current%20buzz%20around%20translations%20that%20we%20see%20in%20India%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeagull%E2%80%99s%20enviable%20list%20of%20writers%20and%20astounding%20book%20covers%20have%20been%20written%20about%20over%20the%20past%20few%20years%2C%20and%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcaravanmagazine.in%2Freviews-essays%2Fflight-seagull-indian-publisher-europe%5C%22%3Earticle%20by%20the%20writer%20Anjum%20Hasan%20in%20%3Cem%3ECaravan%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20especially%20good.%20But%20what%20Kripalani%E2%80%99s%20film%20does%20is%20a%20behind-the-scenes%20look%20at%20how%20it%20is%20to%20work%20as%20a%20small%20publishing%20house%20with%20big%20cerebral%20ambitions.%20Publishing%20is%20a%20subjective%20business%2C%20like%20any%20creative%20industry.%20You%20never%20know%20if%20a%20book%20will%20work.%20And%20so%2C%20the%20call%20to%20go%20by%20instinct%20rather%20than%20second-guessing%20oneself%2C%20by%20taking%20decisions%20with%20the%20heart%3Cstrong%3E%2C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20and%20treating%20your%20writers%20as%20friends%20rather%20than%20clients%20may%20in%20fact%20be%20solid%20business%20strategy.%20An%20impulsive%20decision%20like%20offering%20your%20newly-minted%20Nobel%20prize%20winner%2050%25%20of%20sales%20proceeds%20may%20in%20fact%20help%20draw%20in%20other%20celebrated%20writers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20story%20of%20Urvashi%20Butalia%20and%20Ritu%20Menon%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20only%20one%20other%20film%20about%20publishing%20in%20India%20that%20I%20know.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FKw8woVAxIO0%3Fsi%3DoMFYFohJY87oDysp%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Books%20We%20Made%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20Anupama%20Chandra%20and%20Uma%20Tanuku%20is%20a%20delightful%20documentary%2C%20funded%20by%20the%20Public%20Service%20Broadcasting%20Trust%2C%20about%20the%20work%20of%20Urvashi%20Butalia%20and%20Ritu%20Menon%20who%20set%20up%20feminist%20publishing%20in%20India.%20First%2C%20they%20worked%20together%20on%20a%20publishing%20house%20called%20Kali%20for%20Women%20from%201984%20to%202003%2C%20and%20there%20on%20separately%20%E2%80%93%20Butalia%20set%20up%20another%20feminist%20house%20called%20Zubaan%20and%20Menon%2C%20Women%20Unlimited.%20This%20film%20too%20speaks%20of%20money%3A%20how%20there%20was%20none%20for%20a%20long%20time%2C%20how%20Butalia%20and%20Menon%20budgeted%20no%20salary%20for%20themselves%20for%20years%2C%20how%20Menon%E2%80%99s%20family%20garage%20served%20as%20a%20rent-free%20office%20and%20even%20water%20and%20electricity%20bills%20did%20not%20come%20out%20of%20the%20publishing%20budget.%20Of%20having%20too%20little%20money%20to%20print%20photographs%20well%20and%20the%20unexpected%20generosity%20of%20outsiders%20like%20the%20photographer%20Pablo%20Bartholomew%20who%20did%20a%20series%20of%20portraits%20of%20women%20poets%20for%20a%20Kali%20for%20Women%20diary%20for%20free%20or%20nearly%20free.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20too%20is%20a%20story%20of%20doing%20business%20in%20a%20different%20way%2C%20%E2%80%9Con%20the%20margins%E2%80%9D%20as%20Menon%20says%2C%20without%20the%20resources%20or%20the%20pressure%20of%20the%20mainstream.%20But%20here%20too%2C%20we%20hear%20of%20the%20need%20to%20survive%20as%20a%20business%2C%20to%20sell%20well.%20Mainstream%20publishing%20tends%20to%20speak%20of%20independent%20publishing%20as%20vanity%20projects%20or%20cottage%20industries%2C%20financed%20by%20largesse%20and%20freed%20of%20the%20demands%20of%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FswmFuJiYlDw%3Fsi%3DKJct0DtpermKMtfB%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C%22%3E%EF%BB%BF%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Books%20We%20Made%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20however%2C%20invokes%20a%20terrific%20tactile%20love%20for%20books%20as%20objects.%20It%20spends%20many%20minutes%20of%20its%2067-minute%20run%20time%20putting%20the%20books%20produced%20by%20Butalia%20and%20Menon%20on%20screen.%20Savouring%20them.%20Butalia%20describes%20a%20book%20called%20%3Cem%3EShareer%20ki%20Jaankari%3C%2Fem%3E%20authored%20by%2075%20women%20in%20rural%20Rajasthan%2C%20illustrating%20the%20female%20body.%20The%20book%20ingeniously%20uses%20folded%20paper%20to%20depict%20the%20sexual%20organs%20and%20reproductive%20system%20of%20women.%20We%20see%20the%20processes%20of%20printing%20and%20laying%20out%20of%20pages%20as%20they%20were%20once%20done.%20We%20hear%20Butalia%20say%20she%20loved%20the%20printing%20process%20and%20the%20filmmakers%20take%20that%20as%20a%20cue%20to%20underline%20that%20publishing%20is%20not%20only%20about%20ideas%20and%20creative%20labour%20but%20also%20technical%20processes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKripalani%20eschews%20this%20approach%20completely%2C%20using%20interviews%20with%20Seagull%20editors%20and%20authors%20and%20collaborators%20to%20tell%20the%20story.%20To%20me%2C%20this%20feels%20like%20a%20missed%20opportunity%20because%20Seagull%20is%20known%20for%20its%20cover%20design%20and%20superb%20production%20quality.%20Kishore%20himself%20is%20full%20of%20stories%20of%20fixing%20little%20things%2C%20such%20as%20how%20he%20figured%20out%20a%20way%20to%20avoid%20the%20bubbled%20spines%20we%20would%20sometimes%20see%20in%20books%20before%20automate%20perfect%20binding%20machines%20became%20used%20routinely.%20He%20stuck%20a%20strip%20of%20chart%20paper%20on%20the%20inside%20of%20the%20spine%20so%20that%20it%20stayed%20firm.%20Seagull%20would%20often%20give%20the%20work%20of%20typesetting%20to%20P.K.%20Ghosh%20(in%20the%20era%20before%20desktop%20publishing)%2C%20whom%20the%20historian%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscroll.in%2Farticle%2F1049508%2Ffrom-one-historian-to-another-remembering-ranajit-guha-who-redefined-indian-historiography%5C%22%3ERamachandra%20Guha%20called%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%9Cone%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20great%20typesetters%E2%80%9D.%20What%20does%20a%20book%20printed%20by%20Ghosh%20look%20like%3F%20What%20can%20we%20see%20on%20the%20page%20to%20appreciate%20the%20mastery%20Guha%20refers%20to%3F%20Have%20we%20lost%20some%20beauty%20in%20the%20move%20to%20desktop%20publishing%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKripalani%E2%80%99s%20choice%2C%20however%2C%20is%20a%20deliberate%20one.%20%E2%80%9CI%20wanted%20to%20focus%20on%20the%20ideas%20behind%20publishing%20what%20they%20do.%20For%20processes%2C%20people%20can%20google%20it%20themselves%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20when%20I%20put%20the%20question%20to%20him%20after%20a%20screening%20in%20Kolkata.%20%E2%80%9CI%20wanted%20a%20film%20of%20ideas.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20those%20who%20know%20Seagull%20even%20a%20little%2C%20a%20story%20of%20conversations%20also%20makes%20sense%20intuitively.%20If%20you%20have%20ever%20visited%20the%20bookstore%20and%20asked%20a%20question%20or%20two%2C%20or%20even%20if%20you%20have%20interacted%20with%20their%20accounts%20on%20social%20media%2C%20you%20would%20be%20offered%20a%20coffee%20or%20lemonade%20and%20invited%20to%20a%20conversation.%20Anyone%20who%20knows%20Seagull%20even%20a%20bit%20knows%20how%20much%20they%20value%20the%20give%20and%20take%20of%20conversation.%20That%20anyone%20who%20enjoys%20the%20world%20of%20ideas%20and%20stories%20and%20art%20becomes%20a%20part%20of%20the%20Seagull%20family%2C%20so%20to%20speak.%20And%20from%20there%2C%20a%20book%20or%20a%20project%20can%20just%20be%20a%20conversation%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20the%20Book%20and%20Other%20Stories%3Cem%3E%C2%A0by%20Pushan%20Kripalani%20is%20currently%20being%20screened%20at%20events%20open%20to%20the%20public%20in%20cities%20across%20India.%20In%20addition%20to%20the%20main%20film%20of%20111.14-minute%20film%2C%20there%20are%20six%20long%20interviews%20with%20patrons%2C%20long-time%20collaborations%20and%20admirers%20of%20Seagull.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESohini%20Chattopadhyay%20is%20a%20National%20Award-winning%20film%20critic%20and%20award-winning%20journalist.%20Her%20book%20The%20Day%20I%20Became%20a%20Runner%3A%20A%20Women%E2%80%99s%20History%20of%20India%20Through%20the%20Lens%20of%20Sport%20will%20be%20published%20by%20HarperCollins%20India%20in%20October%202023%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694668379000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F14103916%2F266377862_6529640610410462_3805678544101550645_n.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffilm%2Fseagull-books-naveen-kishore-business-model%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Many%20of%20us%20know%20the%20story%20of%20Seagull%2C%20the%20independent%20publishing%20house%20that%20boasts%20of%20the%20giants%20of%20world%20literature%20and%20academia%20on%20their%20list.%20A%20documentary%20takes%20us%20inside%20their%20intuitive%20and%20unusual%20business%20calculations.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffilm%2Fseagull-books-naveen-kishore-business-model%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Blue%20Ant%20Media%20Sets%20Asia-Pacific%20Expansion%2C%20Hires%20Jon%20Penn%20for%20new%20Sydney%20Office%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694668212000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FJon-Penn-Blue-Ant-lcr-res.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1235723194%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Blue%20Ant%20Media%2C%20the%20Canadian-owned%20group%20with%20operations%20spanning%20TV%20production%2C%20distribution%20and%20channels%20management%2C%20is%20creating%20a%20new%20Asia-Pacific%20base%20in%20Sydney%2C%20Australia.%20It%20has%20hired%20Jon%20Penn%20as%20its%20Asia-Pacific%20MD%20and%20Jason%20Soh%20as%20VP%20