%2Fnsync-reunite-new-song-better-place-trolls-band-together-trailer-1235723178%2Famp%2F%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Ffilm%2Fnews%2Fnsync-reunite-new-song-better-place-trolls-band-together-trailer-1235723178%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22G20's%20New%20Delhi%20Declaration%3A%20Serving%20the%20Interest%20of%20the%20Global%20Landlords%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F10222855%2FF5o4uL_WkAAv_10.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20G20%20summit%20in%20India%20ended%20on%20a%20high%20note%20with%20a%20New%20Delhi%20Declaration.%20This%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20immense%20satisfaction%20for%20the%20prime%20minister%20personally%20and%20for%20his%20entire%20team%20which%20had%20to%20struggle%20to%20arrive%20at%20a%20consensus%20among%20the%20warring%20elements%20of%20the%20grouping.%20It%20highlights%20India%E2%80%99s%20present%20pole%20position%20in%20the%20global%20order.%20Other%20nations%20are%20trying%20to%20draw%20it%20into%20their%20sphere%20of%20influence%2C%20or%20at%20least%20trying%20to%20prevent%20it%20from%20getting%20closer%20to%20the%20other%20side.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20advantage%20is%20a%20result%20of%20the%20continuing%20Ukraine%20war%20and%20the%20aggravating%20Cold%20War%20between%20the%20G7%20and%20China-Russia%20combine.%20It%20has%20required%20deft%20manoeuvring%2C%20more%20so%20because%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20political%20problems%20with%20China%20which%20resulted%20in%20its%20president%20giving%20the%20meeting%20a%20miss.%20This%20caused%20considerable%20consternation%2C%20given%20China%E2%80%99s%20economic%20and%20political%20clout.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAmbiguity%20not%20action%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20G20%20declaration%E2%80%99s%20political%20message%20is%20ambiguous%20at%20best%2C%20enabling%20both%20sides%20in%20the%20Cold%20War%20to%20read%20what%20they%20want%20and%20pronounce%20victory%20%E2%80%93%20and%20good%20diplomacy%20is%20all%20about%20this.%20So%20what%20does%20the%20declaration%20mean%3F%20Real%20progress%20would%20have%20been%20if%20the%20G20%20leaders%20could%20have%20announced%20an%20end%20to%20the%20disastrous%20war%20in%20Ukraine.%20Lakhs%20have%20died%20and%20been%20injured%20in%20the%20last%20year%20and%20a%20half.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EArms%20and%20ammunition%20are%20being%20spent%20at%20a%20phenomenal%20rate%20which%20only%20benefits%20the%20armament%20industry%20and%20the%20military%20industrial%20complex%20of%20the%20world.%20The%20marginalised%20of%20the%20world%20continue%20to%20suffer%20the%20consequences%20of%20supply%20bottlenecks%20and%20may%20face%20more%20adversity%20if%20high%20inflation%20persists%20and%2For%20a%20global%20recession%20begins.%20A%20worker%20asked%20me%2C%20what%20is%20G20%20and%20what%20does%20it%20give%20me%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Civil%20Society%20Calls%20Out%20G20%20Declaration%E2%80%99s%20Omission%20of%20Civic%20Space%20Erosion%2C%20Democracy%20Decline%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fcivil-society-calls-out-g20-declarations-omission-of-civic-space-erosion-democracy-decline%5C%22%3ECivil%20Society%20Calls%20Out%20G20%20Declaration%E2%80%99s%20Omission%20of%20Civic%20Space%20Erosion%2C%20Democracy%20Decline%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EG20%20nations%20are%20the%20landlords%20of%20the%20world.%20They%20represent%20the%20economic%20and%20political%20interests%20of%20their%20elites.%20They%20have%20decided%20to%20fight%20to%20the%20finish.%20The%20marginalised%20people%20are%20incidental%20to%20their%20considerations.%20India%2C%20as%20the%20poorest%20of%20the%20G20%20countries%2C%20has%20the%20largest%20number%20of%20the%20marginalised%20in%20the%20world.%20These%20are%20the%20workers%2C%20the%20farmers%2C%20the%20women%20and%20the%20youth.%20Is%20their%20precarious%20condition%20exposed%20by%20the%20pandemic%20going%20to%20be%20addressed%20by%20the%20declaration%20in%20the%20coming%20years%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELofty%20slogans%20no%20substitute%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGlobal%20declarations%20and%20agreements%20are%20cloaked%20in%20progressive%20language%20to%20hide%20the%20real%20intent%20of%20the%20landlords.%20Climate%20negotiations%20or%20the%20Sustainable%20Development%20Goals%20agreements%20are%20high%20sounding%2C%20but%20extreme%20weather%20events%20are%20only%20increasing%20in%20numbers%20annually%20and%20that%20is%20aggravating%20the%20poverty%20and%20distress%20of%20the%20marginalised.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20quoted%20the%20Prakrit%20inscription%20on%20an%20Ashokan%20pillar%20close%20to%20the%20venue%20of%20the%20summit%2C%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EHevam%20loksa%20hitmukhe%20ti%2C%20atha%20iyam%20natisu%20hevam%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99.%20He%20translated%20it%20as%20%E2%80%98the%20welfare%20and%20happiness%20of%20humanity%20should%20always%20be%20ensured%E2%80%99.%20Without%20agreeing%20to%20address%20the%20consumerism%20of%20the%20well-off%20in%20the%20world%2C%20this%20happiness%20cannot%20be%20ensured%2C%20forget%20%E2%80%98always%E2%80%99.%20If%20the%20situation%20is%20as%20grim%20as%20in%202022-23%2C%20when%20the%20temperature%20has%20only%20risen%201.2%20degrees%20above%20the%20pre-industrial%20average%20temperature%2C%20what%20would%20it%20be%20at%201.5%20degrees%20above%3F%20Not%20a%20day%20can%20be%20wasted%2C%20yet%20the%20declaration%20talks%20of%20goals%20over%20the%20coming%20years.%20There%20is%20no%20clarion%20call%20to%20the%20elite%20to%20curb%20consumption.%20The%20landlords%20do%20not%20want%20to%20sacrifice%20their%20lifestyle%20or%20their%20profits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Summit%20slogan%2C%20%E2%80%98Vasudhaiva%20Kutumbakam%E2%80%99%20enlarged%20to%20%E2%80%98One%20Family%2C%20One%20Earth%20and%20One%20Future%E2%80%99%2C%20is%20evocative.%20But%20are%20these%20meant%20for%20the%20global%20compact%20and%20not%20to%20be%20applied%20within%20each%20nation%3F%20Can%20there%20be%20%E2%80%98welfare%20and%20happiness%E2%80%99%20where%20not%20only%20is%20there%20extreme%20deprivation%20and%20poverty%2C%20but%20it%20persists%3F%20Can%20there%20be%20one%20global%20or%20national%20family%20with%20extreme%20and%20rising%20inequality%3F%20There%20is%20only%20One%20Earth%20which%20is%20becoming%20increasingly%20unliveable.%20So%2C%20the%20One%20Future%20that%20we%20are%20moving%20towards%20looks%20bleak%20for%20the%20marginalised.%20The%20Bezzos%20and%20Musks%2C%20considering%20colonising%20space%2C%20will%20find%20life%20on%20the%20Moon%20and%20Mars%20even%20tougher%20than%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20the%20noble%20words%20in%20the%20declaration%20come%20nowhere%20close%20to%20the%20deeds%20of%20the%20global%20landlords.%20This%20applies%20with%20even%20greater%20force%20in%20India%20from%20where%20the%20slogans%20emanate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIssue%20of%20resources%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIs%20raising%20these%20concerns%20churlish%20or%20nitpicking%20when%20the%20world%20leaders%20are%20full%20of%20praise%20for%20India%E2%80%99s%20presidency%3F%20The%20proponents%20point%20to%20the%20major%20paragraphs%2Fchapters%20in%20the%20New%20Delhi%20Declaration%20which%20are%20not%20just%20regarding%20the%20Ukraine%20war%20but%20also%20express%20concern%20about%20the%20marginalised.%20Everything%20is%20there%20%E2%80%93%20inclusive%20growth%2C%20gender%20equality%2C%20climate%20change%2C%20financial%20markets%2C%20energy%20and%20food%20security%2C%20global%20debt%20vulnerabilities%2C%20health%20and%20education%2C%20digital%20public%20infrastructure%2C%20international%20taxation%2C%20etc..%20These%20are%20crucial%20global%20concerns%2C%20especially%20for%20the%20developing%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20landlords%20who%20decide%20are%20adept%20at%20making%20tall%20promises%20to%20create%20a%20fa%C3%A7ade%20behind%20which%20they%20carry%20forward%20their%20real%20agenda.%20In%20India%20we%20see%20this%20in%20the%20budgets%20which%20are%20cloaked%20in%20tall%20promises%20to%20end%20poverty%2C%20illiteracy%2C%20etc.%20but%20these%20persist%2075%20years%20after%20independence.%20The%20ruling%20elite%20feel%20the%20poor%20escaping%20extreme%20poverty%20ought%20to%20be%20grateful%20even%20if%20they%20lead%20an%20uncivilised%20existence.%20They%20should%20not%20look%20at%20their%20marginalisation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22The%20G20%20Has%20Summarily%20Failed%20to%20Address%20Agrarian%20Distress%20in%20its%20Member%20Countries%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Fg20-farmers-agriculture-bio-fuel-india-us%5C%22%3EThe%20G20%20Has%20Summarily%20Failed%20to%20Address%20Agrarian%20Distress%20in%20its%20Member%20Countries%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAre%20adequate%20funds%20raised%20to%20implement%20the%20tall%20promises%20in%20the%20Indian%20budget%20or%20in%20the%20Delhi%20declaration%3F%20Who%20is%20to%20raise%20the%20funds%20and%20how%20will%20they%20be%20shared%20among%20nations%3F%20The%20chapter%20on%20global%20taxation%20is%20the%20briefest%20of%20all%20%E2%80%93%20one%20para.%20No%20goal%20is%20set%20as%20to%20how%20resources%20will%20be%20raised%20and%20how%20will%20they%20be%20distributed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMultilateral%20funding%20for%20development%20has%20been%20available%20from%20global%20financial%20institutions%20like%20the%20World%20Bank.%20Rather%20than%20helping%20development%2C%20in%20many%20cases%20it%20pushed%20nations%20into%20a%20debt%20trap.%20China%20has%20also%20been%20advancing%20loans%20under%20the%20One%20Belt%2C%20One%20Road%20initiative%20with%20similar%20results.%20So%2C%20more%20multilateral%20development%20banks%20can%20hardly%20be%20the%20solution.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20international%20financial%20architecture%20enables%20flight%20of%20capital%20from%20the%20developing%20world.%20They%20have%20lost%20more%20than%20they%20have%20received.%20London%20and%20New%20York%20are%20tax%20havens%20just%20as%20much%20as%20Delaware%20or%20Switzerland%20or%20Jersey%20Island%20and%20Cayman%20Island.%20The%20landlords%20of%20the%20developed%20nations%20can%20prevent%20this%20bleeding%20of%20the%20developing%20world%20resources%20but%20for%20obvious%20reasons%2C%20they%20do%20not%20do%20so.%20The%20elites%20of%20the%20developing%20countries%20who%20resort%20to%20flight%20of%20capital%20too%20benefit%20from%20it.%20So%2C%20implicitly%20there%20is%20consensus%20among%20the%20global%20landlords%20to%20persist%20with%20this%20system%20by%20not%20resorting%20to%20any%20tough%20action%20on%20this%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20situation%20is%20aggravated%20by%20the%20%E2%80%98race%20to%20the%20bottom%E2%80%99%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.oecd.org%2Ftax%2Fbeps%2Fabout%2F%5C%22%3Ebase%20erosion%20and%20profit%20shifting%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20result%20is%20inadequate%20resources%20for%20public%20goods%20and%20forced%20privatisation.%20The%20declaration%20states%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20recognize%20the%20critical%20role%20of%20private%20enterprise%20in%20accelerating%20growth%20and%20driving%20sustainable%20economic%20transformations.%E2%80%9D%20So%2C%20the%20global%20landlords%20are%20washing%20their%20hands%20off%20their%20responsibility%20to%20the%20marginalised.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECryptocurrencies%20and%2C%20since%20November%202022%2C%20AI%20based%20on%20Large%20Language%20Models%20pose%20a%20major%20global%20challenge.%20They%20threaten%20to%20marginalise%20the%20marginals%20like%20never%20before.%20The%20urgent%20global%20action%20called%20for%20is%20missing.%20Perhaps%20the%20global%20landlords%20want%20it%20that%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EConclusion%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20also%20side%20shows%20like%20the%20announcement%20of%20the%20road%20and%20rail%20connectivity%20from%20India%20to%20Europe%20via%20West%20Asia.%20It%20seems%20to%20be%20the%20result%20of%20long%20term%20thinking.%20That%20is%20why%20Adani%20had%20acquired%20the%20Haifa%20port%20in%20Israel%20through%20which%20the%20connectivity%20would%20be%20established.%20Indeed%2C%20it%20is%20not%20to%20help%20the%20marginalised.%20Till%20now%2C%20India%20has%20lost%20out%20in%20the%20Free%20Trade%20Agreements%20it%20has%20entered%20into%20due%20to%20its%20technological%20lag.%20So%2C%20for%20whose%20benefit%20is%20it%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20visit%20to%20Gandhi%20Samadhi%20demonstrates%20the%20gap%20between%20the%20show%20and%20the%20intent.%20It%20did%20not%20strengthen%20the%20resolve%20to%20enforce%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98last%20person%20first%E2%80%99.%20In%20India%2C%20currently%20the%20Gandhian%20institutions%20and%20ideas%20are%20under%20attack.%20Recently%20one%20of%20the%20institutions%20in%20the%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20constituency%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fin-varanasi-occupants-of-iconic-gandhian-institution-thrown-out-their-land-taken-over%5C%22%3Edemolished%20on%20the%20pretext%20of%20development%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20is%20empty%20rhetoric%20when%20the%20Preamble%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20meet%20at%20a%20defining%20moment%20in%20history%20where%20the%20decisions%20we%20make%20now%20will%20determine%20the%20future%20of%20our%20people%20and%20our%20planet.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20declaration%E2%80%99s%20achievement%20is%20preservation%20of%20the%20interest%20of%20the%20global%20elite%20(including%20the%20Indian%20elite).%20The%20global%20landlords%20enabled%20it%20while%20paying%20lip%20service%20to%20global%20good.%20The%20Indian%20government%20through%20its%20deft%20handling%20has%20been%20able%20to%20serve%20the%20interest%20of%20big%20business%20at%20the%20expense%20of%20the%20marginalised%20and%20this%20coincides%20with%20the%20global%20objective%20of%20the%20other%20landlords.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EArun%20Kumar%20retired%20as%20Professor%20of%20Economics%2C%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20University.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694667205000%2C%22visual%22