ales-breakup-markets-2023-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Libya%3A%20Flood%20Death%20Toll%20Rises%20to%20More%20Than%205%2C000%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F14094514%2FF551TXxXMAAzvhe.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EFlooding%20in%20eastern%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Flibya%2Ft-19016309%5C%22%3ELibya%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0has%20left%20more%20than%205%2C100%20people%20dead%2C%20officials%20said%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThousands%20more%20people%20were%20missing%20in%20the%20eastern%20city%20of%20Derna%2C%20and%20tens%20of%20thousands%C2%A0displaced.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMediterranean%20Storm%20Daniel%20arrived%20in%20Libya%20on%20Sunday%2C%20and%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Flibya-more-than-2000-dead-after-catastrophic-floods%2Fa-66786792%5C%22%3Ecaused%20two%20dams%20outside%20Derna%20to%20burst%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20the%20current%20situation%20in%20Libya%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20than%207%2C000%20people%20were%20injured%20in%20Derna%2C%20aid%20worker%20Ossama%20Ali%20told%20the%20Associated%20Press%20(AP).%20Most%20of%20them%20were%20being%20treated%20in%20field%20hospitals%20set%20up%20by%20authorities%20and%20aid%20agencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20city%E2%80%99s%20mayor%2C%C2%A0Abdulmenam%20Al-Ghaithi%2C%20believes%20as%20many%20as%2020%2C000%20residents%20could%20be%20dead.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20UN%20migration%20agency%2C%20the%20International%20Organization%20for%20Migration%2C%20said%20that%20at%20least%2030%2C000%20people%20in%20Derna%20had%20lost%20their%20homes%20to%20flooding.%20The%20agency%20said%20that%20the%20damage%20was%20so%20extensive%20that%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fmedicane-left-libya-trapped-between-floods-and-the-sea%2Fa-66793714%5C%22%3Ethe%20city%20was%20almost%20inaccessible%20to%20aid%20workers%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDerna%20lies%20on%20a%20narrow%20coastal%20plain%20on%20the%20Mediterranean%20under%20steep%20mountains.%20Only%20two%20roads%20from%20the%20south%20remain%20usable%2C%20hampering%20the%20movement%20of%20aid%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAid%20workers%20and%20officials%20have%20said%20that%20the%20death%20toll%20is%20likely%20to%20keep%20rising%2C%20as%20bodies%20continue%20to%20wash%20up%20ashore.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBodies%20are%20everywhere%2C%20inside%20houses%2C%20in%20the%20streets%2C%20at%20sea.%20Wherever%20you%20go%2C%20you%20find%20dead%20men%2C%20women%2C%20and%20children%2C%E2%80%9D%20Emad%20al-Falah%2C%20an%20aid%20worker%20from%20Benghazi%2C%20told%20AP.%20%E2%80%9CEntire%20families%20were%20lost.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWar%20and%20corruption%20exacerbate%20disaster%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Libyan%20political%20analyst%20has%20called%20for%20the%20first%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Flibyans-increasingly-frustrated-with-politics-rising-prices-foreign-interference%2Fa-62402038%5C%22%3Egeneral%20elections%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20be%20held%20in%20almost%2010%20years%20after%20the%20internationally-recognised%20Government%20of%20National%20Unity%20(GNU)%20postponed%20accepting%20international%20aid.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTwo%20rival%20governments%20that%20are%20perfectly%20happy%20to%20rule%20over%20the%20rubble%20whilst%20their%20citizens%20lay%20underneath%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%C2%A0Anas%20El%20Gomati%2C%20founder%20of%20Tripoli-based%C2%A0Sadeq%20Institute%2C%20told%20DW.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20Red%20Crescent%20and%20Libyan%20civilians%20themselves%20have%20been%20responsible%20for%20the%20bulk%20of%20the%20disaster%20recovery.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAnd%20frankly%2C%20the%20local%20authorities%20there%2C%20the%20LNA%20or%20the%20rival%20administration%20in%20the%20west%2C%20they%20can%20step%20aside%2C%E2%80%9D%20Gomati%20added.%20%E2%80%9CThey%E2%80%99ve%20done%20enough.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGomati%20also%20called%20for%20an%20inquiry%20into%20how%20the%20disaster%20occurred%2C%20from%20the%20dam%20above%20Derna%20not%20being%20maintained%20under%20the%20Gadhafi%20regime%2C%20all%20the%20way%20to%20corruption%20and%20%E2%80%9Ccriminal%20negligence%E2%80%9D%C2%A0in%20the%20present%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20certainly%20think%20there%20needs%20to%20be%20a%20postmortem%20%E2%80%94%20figuratively%20and%20literally%20%E2%80%94%20after%20the%20events%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAsma%20Khalifa%20from%20the%20German%20Institute%20for%20Global%20and%20Area%20Studies%20said%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Ffloods-in-libya-civil-war-compounds-devastation%2Fa-66804458%5C%22%3ELibya%E2%80%99s%20years-long%20civil%20war%C2%A0weakened%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20institutions%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%E2%80%9Cand%20aided%20mass%20corruption%20and%20abuse%20of%20public%20funds.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20the%20main%20reason%20for%20the%20chaotic%20response%20to%20the%20crisis%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20told%20DW.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEU%20pledges%20aid%20to%20Libya%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlso%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Feuropean-commission%2Ft-17455066%5C%22%3EEU%20Commission%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0said%20that%20the%20bloc%20would%20provide%20disaster%20response%20equipment%20and%20humanitarian%20funding%20worth%20%E2%82%AC500%2C000%20(%24537%2C000).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20equipment%20offered%20are%20tents%2C%20field%20beds%2C%20blankets%2C%2080%20generators%2C%20food%20items%2C%20hospital%20tents%20and%20water%20tanks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20humanitarian%20funding%20is%20to%20go%20to%20organisations%20%E2%80%9Coperating%20on%20the%20ground%20to%20deliver%20lifesaving%20health%20and%20water%20and%20sanitation%20supplies.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELibya%E2%80%99s%20representative%20to%20the%20United%20Nations%20in%20Geneva%20had%20requested