-aspirant-from-jharkhand-hangs-self-in-kota%2Farticleshow%2F103624662.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Times%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20No%20suicide%20note%20was%20found%2C%20the%20police%20have%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKota%E2%80%99s%20test%20preparation%20business%20is%20reportedly%20worth%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2F16yearold-neet-student-dies-by-suicide-in-rajasthan-s-kota-24th-case-this-year-101694588469330.html%5C%22%3ERs%2010%2C000%20crore%20annually%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20with%20students%20from%20across%20the%20country%20coming%20to%20stay%20in%20the%20town%E2%80%99s%20hostels%20and%20study%20at%20test%20prep%20centres%20after%20completing%20their%20Class%2010%20exams.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGiven%20the%20extremely%20high%20number%20of%20suicides%20this%20year%2C%20the%20district%20administration%20has%20recognised%20the%20need%20for%20change%20%E2%80%93%20but%20has%20focused%20on%20questionable%20areas%20rather%20than%20investing%20in%20mental%20health%20care.%20In%20August%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fafter-22nd-student-suicide-this-year-kota-administration-installs-spring-loaded-fans%5C%22%3Eadministration%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%20it%20would%20be%20installing%20spring-loaded%20fans%20in%20all%20rooms%20%E2%80%9Cto%20provide%20students%20mental%20support%20and%20security%E2%80%9D.%20While%20the%20authorities%20have%20also%20passed%20rules%20on%20giving%20students%20time%20off%20and%20conducting%20psychological%20evaluations%2C%20these%20are%20reportedly%20not%20followed%20in%20many%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERajasthan%20cabinet%20minister%20Shanti%20Dhariwal%20has%20claimed%20that%20the%20suicides%20happen%20because%20of%20%E2%80%9Caffairs%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cparental%20pressure%E2%80%9D%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Findia%2Fstory%2Frajasthan-minister-shanti-dhariwal-claims-affair-parental-pressure-as-reasons-for-students-death-by-suici