%2F2023%2F08%2F25092830%2FWhatsapp_mmmm.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Meta%20on%20Wednesday%20(September%2013)%20launched%20Channels%20for%20its%20popular%20messaging%20platform%20WhatsApp%2C%20a%20%E2%80%9Cone-way%20broadcast%20tool%E2%80%9D%20that%20will%20allow%20people%20to%20receive%20updates%20from%20people%20and%20organisations%20in%20a%20%E2%80%9Cprivate%20way.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20present%2C%20Channels%20is%20available%20only%20to%20the%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20and%20celebrities%20Katrina%20Kaif%2C%20Diljit%20Dosanjh%20and%20Vijay%20Deverakonda%2C%20but%20Whatsapp%20said%20that%20it%20was%20%E2%80%9Cwelcoming%20thousands%20of%20organisations%2C%20sports%20teams%2C%20artists%2C%20and%20thought%20leaders%20that%20people%20can%20follow%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20a%20press%20release%2C%20Meta%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CWhatsApp%20Channels%20are%20a%20one-way%20broadcast%20tool%20and%20deliver%20a%20private%20way%20to%20receive%20updates%20from%20people%20and%20organisations%20that%20matter%20to%20you%2C%20right%20within%20WhatsApp.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20feature%2C%20earlier%20rolled%20out%20in%20Singapore%20and%20Colombia%20in%20June%2C%20will%20now%20be%20available%20in%20India%20and%20150%20other%20countries.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20has%20learnt%20that%20while%20users%20in%20India%20will%20be%20able%20to%20receive%20updates%20from%20these%20Channels%2C%20they%20will%20not%20be%20able%20to%20create%20their%20own%20Channels%20just%20yet.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWhatsApp%20Channels%20are%20rolling%20out%20globally%20over%20the%20next%20few%20weeks.%20Over%20the%20coming%20months%2C%20we%E2%80%99ll%20also%20make%20it%20possible%20for%20anyone%20to%20create%20a%20channel%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20WhatsApp%20spokesperson%20said%20to%C2%A0%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20Meta%2C%20Channels%20aims%20to%20be%20a%20%E2%80%9Cprivate%20broadcast%20service.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EChannels%20are%20separate%20from%20chats%20and%20who%20users%20choose%20to%20follow%20will%20not%20be%20visible%20to%20other%20followers.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EMeta%20said%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Cpersonal%20information%20of%20both%20admins%20and%20followers%E2%80%9D%20will%20be%20protected.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECommenting%20on%20the%20collaboration%2C%20BCCI%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Indian%20Cricket%20team%20is%20thrilled%20to%20partner%20with%20WhatsApp%20on%20the%20launch%20of%20Channels.%20We%20kick-off%20our%20partnership%20with%20WhatsApp%20with%20the%20ICC%20Men%E2%80%99s%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%202023%20which%20is%20set%20to%20begin%20in%20October.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fquestions-over-financing-of-union-ministers-interviews-with-youtube-influencers%5C%22%3EQuestions%20Over%20Financing%20of%20Union%20Ministers%E2%80%99%20Interviews%20With%20YouTube%20Influencers%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20will%20leverage%20Channels%20to%20generate%20excitement%20and%20support%20as%20India%20gets%20ready%20to%20host%20the%20marquee%20event%20after%20a%20decade-long%20wait.%20With%20WhatsApp%20Channels%2C%20fans%20will%20be%20aware%20of%20important%20and%20accurate%20information%20and%20news%20around%20match%20schedules%2C%20timings%2C%20scorecards%20etc.%20Get%20on%20WhatsApp%20channels%20and%20never%20miss%20out%20on%20updates%20from%20on%20and%20off%20the%20field.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EActor%20and%20entrepreneur%20Kaif%20said%20that%20Channels%20will%20serve%20as%20a%20personalised%20newsletter.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWhatsApp%20Channels%20serves%20as%20a%20personalised%20newsletter%20through%20which%20I%20can%20share%20insights%20and%20updates%20with%20my%20dedicated%20audience%2C%20fans%2C%20and%20all%20those%20who%20have%20consistently%20shown%20their%20support%20throughout%20my%20journey.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EWhatsApp%E2%80%99s%20market%20in%20India%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20probably%20its%20largest%20markets%20in%20the%20world%2C%20India%20is%20crucial%20for%20its%20commercial%20success.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20February%202021%2C%20then%20Union%20minister%20for%20information%20and%20technology%20Ravi%20Shankar%20Prasad%20said%20at%20a%20press%20conference%20that%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FTimesNow%2Fstatus%2F1364857924254801921%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EWhatsApp%20has%2053%20crore%20(530%20million)%20users%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3Ein%20India.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELast%20week%20Meta%E2%80%99s%20India%20head%20Sandhya%20Devanathan%20had%20highlighted%20that%20India%20is%20%E2%80%9Chuge%20priority%20market%E2%80%9D%20for%20the%20company.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIndia%20is%20a%20huge%20priority%20market%20for%20the%20company.%20So%2C%20India%20has%20one%20of%20our%20largest%20user%20bases%2C%20be%20it%20on%20Facebook%2C%20Instagram%2C%20or%20WhatsApp.%20But%20equally%2C%20India%20is%20also%20the%20place%20where%20we%20test%20a%20lot%20of%20what%20we%20roll%20out%20globally%20as%20well.%20It%20has%20also%20been%20where%20we%20develop%20a%20lot%20of%20our%20innovative%20products%20and%20that%20investment%20will%20continue%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said%20to%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Fbusiness%2Findia-a-priority-market-with-limitless-possibilities-says-meta-india-head-2673436%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EPress%20Trust%20of%20India.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E%E2%80%98India%3A%20the%20WhatsApp%20election%E2%80%99%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20not%20clear%20who%20the%20%E2%80%9Cthought%20leaders%E2%80%9D%20allowed%20to%20create%20Channels%20are%2C%20at%20present%2C%20if%20that%20includes%20political%20leaders.%20Its%20likely%20impact%20in%20an%20election%20year%20is%20not%20lost%20on%20anybody%2C%20making%20it%20something%20of%20interest%20to%20political%20watchers%20and%20something%20beyond%20pure%20entertainment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20May%205%2C%202019%2C%20even%20before%20the%20results%20of%20the%20general%20elections%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Financial%20Times%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20had%20run%20a%20%E2%80%98Big%20Read%E2%80%99%20story%20with%20a%20headline%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ft.com%2Fcontent%2F9fe88fba-6c0d-11e9-a9a5-351eeaef6d84%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIndia%3A%20the%20WhatsApp%20election%2C%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20saying%20that%20it%20is%20the%20most%20influential%20social%20media%20platform%20in%20many%20parts%20of%20the%20world%20%E2%80%93%20it%20could%20also%20shape%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20political%20future.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELast%20time%20when%20WhatsApp%20restricted%20the%20number%20of%20%E2%80%98forwards%E2%80%99%2C%20it%20was%20elections%20in%20Brazil%20that%20caused%20it%20to%20enforce%20the%20restriction.%20Last%20year%20too%2C%20Brazilian%20authorities%20urged%20messaging%20platform%20WhatsApp%20to%20hold%20back%20the%20launch%20of%20a%20new%20%E2%80%9CCommunities%E2%80%9D%20tool%20until%20elections%20were%20completed%20in%20October.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20new%20feature%2C%20Communities%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aa.com.tr%2Fen%2Famericas%2Fbrazil-urges-whatsapp-to-delay-new-tool-ahead-of-national-elections%2F2649014%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eas%20per%20news%20reports%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20would%20have%20permitted%20communications%20to%20be%20sent%20to%202%2C560%20people%20simultaneously.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESao%20Paulo%20prosecutors%20wrote%20a%20letter%20to%20the%20Meta-owned%20platform%20saying%20that%20the%20expansion%20of%20two%20non-application%20message%20groups%20could%20drive%20the%20spread%20of%20fake%20news%20during%20the%20elections%2C%20counteracting%20measures%20taken%20by%20the%20company%2C%20according%20to%20Globo%20news%20outlet.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20recent%20years%2C%20there%20has%20been%20a%20growth%20or%20flow%20of%20misinformation%20about%20the%20Brazilian%20democratic%20institutions%2C%20especially%20about%20the%20voting%20system%20used%20in%20the%20country%2C%E2%80%9D%20they%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAhead%20of%20elections%2C%20the%20Modi%20government%20has%2C%20as%20before%2C%20been%20the%20most%20innovative%20in%20devising%20new%20ways%20to%20use%20social%20media%20to%20capture%20digital%20audiences.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fquestions-over-financing-of-union-ministers-interviews-with-youtube-influencers%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eseries%20of%20interviews%20with%20Union%20ministers%20conducted%20by%20social%20media%20influencers%20in%20collaboration%20with%20MyGov%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20have%20also%20raised%20questions%20about%20the%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20use%20of%20public%20funds%20to%20finance%20interactions%20between%20influencers%20and%20senior%20government%20functionaries%20as%20well%20as%20the%20terms%20of%20these%20interactions.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694624934000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F25092830%2FWhatsapp_mmmm.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftech%2Fwhatsapp-rolls-out-powerful-one-way-broadcast-tool-channels-in-india%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22WhatsApp%20is%20undeniably%20the%20most%20popular%20messaging%20tool%20in%20India%20and%20its%20ability%20to%20further%20extend%20broadcast%20abilities%20in%20an%20election%20year%20will%20be%20watched%20with%20interest.%20The%202019%20general%20election%20had%20been%20termed%20as%20the%20first%20%E2%80%98WhatsApp%20Election%E2%80%99.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftech%2Fwhatsapp-rolls-out-powerful-one-way-broadcast-tool-channels-in-india%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Three%20Officers%20Killed%20in%20South%20Kashmir%20Militant%20Attack%2C%20Security%20Brass%20Reach%20Amidst%20Search%20Ops%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F13215256%2FUntitled-design-6.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESrinagar%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20A%20colonel%20is%20among%20three%20officers%20of%20the%20Indian%20Army%20and%20J%26amp%3BK%20Police%20who%20were%20killed%20in%20a%20militant%20attack%20in%20south%20Kashmir%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20September%2013%2C%20prompting%20the%20top%20security%20brass%20to%20rush%20to%20the%20area%20where%20a%20major%20search%20operation%20is%20underway.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20commanding%20officer%20of%20the%20Army%E2%80%99s%2019%20Rashtriya%20Rifles%20based%20in%20south%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20Kokernag%20was%20killed%20along%20with%20a%20young%20major-ranked%20officer%20and%20a%20deputy%20superintendent%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%20Police%20during%20the%20attack%20on%20Wednesday%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20terrorists%20had%20taken%20a%20strategically-advantageous%20position%20and%20opened%20fire%20relentlessly%20on%20a%20joint%20team%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%20Police%20and%20the%20Army%20near%20Ahlan%20Gadol%20water%20stream%2C%20giving%20the%20team%20little%20time%20to%20react%2C%E2%80%9D%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGunfire%20during%20anti-insurgency%20operation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20Army%20spokesperson%20said%20that%20an%20anti-insurgency%20operation%20was%20launched%20jointly%20by%20J%26amp%3BK%20Police%20and%20the%20Army%20in%20the%20intervening%20night%20of%20September%2012%20and%2013%20following%20%E2%80%9Cspecific%20intelligence%20on%20the%20presence%20of%20terrorists%E2%80%9D%20in%20Gadol%20area%20of%20Kokernag%2C%20some%2090%20km%20from%20the%20capital%20Srinagar.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReports%20said%20that%20the%20operation%2C%20which%20was%20put%20on%20hold%20during%20the%20night%2C%20resumed%20on%20Wednesday%20morning%20after%20security%20forces%20reportedly%20got%20a%20tip%20that%20the%20attackers%20were%20taking%20shelter%20in%20a%20hideout%20in%20a%20hilly%20area%20of%20Gadol%20village%2C%20which%20is%20situated%20amidst%20dense%20forests%20and%20thick%20vegetation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20security%20forces%20moved%20towards%20the%20hideout%2C%20they%20came%20under%20heavy%20gunfire.%20Reports%20said%20that%20an%20Army%20colonel%20took%20the%20first%20shots%20followed%20by%20his%20deputy%2C%20a%20major-ranked%20officer%2C%20and%20a%20deputy%20superintendent%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%20Police.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAll%20the%20three%20were%20critically%20injured%20in%20the%20initial%20firing%20and%20terrorists%20continued%20to%20fire%20in%20order%20to%20prevent%20the%20evacuation%20of%20the%20victims%20from%20the%20spot.%20However%2C%20an%20Army%20chopper%20was%20pressed%20into%20service%20and%20one%20of%20the%20victims%20was%20evacuated%20to%20a%20military%20hospital%20in%20Srinagar%20where%20he%20succumbed%20to%20injuries%2C%E2%80%9D%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20deceased%20have%20been%20identified%20as%20Colonel%20Manpreet%20Singh%2C%20a%20recipient%20of%20Sena%20Medal%20in%202021%2C%20Deputy%20Superintendent%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Police%20(DSP)%2C%20Humayun%20Muzamil%20Bhat%20and%20Major%20Aashish%20Dhonchak%20of%20the%20Army%E2%80%99s%2019%20Rashtriya%20Rifles.%20The%20bodies%20of%20Singh%20and%20Dhonchak%20have%20not%20been%20retrieved%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDSP%20Bhat%E2%80%99s%20father%2C%20Ghulam%20Hassan%20Bhat%2C%20retired%20from%20J%26amp%3BK%20Police%20as%20Deputy%20Inspector%20General.%20The%20younger%20Bhat%2C%20a%202018%20Jammu%20Kashmir%20Police%20Service%20officer%2C%20had%20gotten%20married%20last%20year%20and%20has%20a%20two-month%20old%20daughter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Army%20didn%E2%80%99t%20share%20more%20details%20about%20the%20deceased%20officers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDilbag%20Singh%2C%20Director%20General%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%20Police%2C%20Lt%20Gen%20Rajiv%20Ghai%2C%20who%20heads%20the%20strategic%20Chinar%20Corps%20based%20in%20Srinagar%20which%20supervises%20the%20Army%E2%80%99s%20operations%20in%20Kashmir%2C%20and%20Vijay%20Kumar%2C%20Additional%20Director%20General%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%20Police%2C%20arrived%20in%20Gadol%20along%20with%20other%20senior%20officers%20of%20security%20establishment%20on%20Wednesday%20afternoon%20to%20assess%20the%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EOn%20behalf%20of%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20Police%20Pariwar%20DGP%20J%26amp%3BK%20Sh%20Dilbag%20Singh%20has%20condoled%20the%20martyrdom%20of%20the%20braveheart%20officers%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%20Police%20and%20Army%20in%20an%20encounter%20at%20Gadool%2CKokernag%2CAnantnag.%3Cbr%3EThe%20DGP%20has%20said%20in%20his%20message%20that%20he%20is%20deeply%20saddened%20by%20the%20terrible%20loss%20of%20three%20young%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FpMJSwYE8wX%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FpMJSwYE8wX%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20J%26amp%3BK%20Police%20(%40JmuKmrPolice)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FJmuKmrPolice%2Fstatus%2F1701995472859316533%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ESeptember%2013%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDGP%20Singh%20later%20led%20a%20wreath-laying%20ceremony%20for%20the%20slain%20police%20officer%20which%20was%20also%20attended%20by%20J%26amp%3BK%E2%80%99s%20Chief%20Secretary%20Arun%20Mehta%20and%20other%20officers%20of%20the%20civil%20and%20security%20administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20reports%2C%20a%20major%20search%20operation%20has%20been%20launched%20to%20track%20down%20the%20perpetrators%20with%20drones%20and%20choppers%20conducting%20aerial%20reconnaissance%20surveys%20around%20the%20forested%20areas%20of%20Gadol%20to%20keep%20an%20eye%20on%20any%20suspicious%20movement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Resistance%20Front%2C%20which%20officials%20believe%20is%20an%20offshoot%20of%20Pakistan-based%20terror%20outfit%20Lashkar-e-Toiba%2C%20has%20claimed%20responsibility%20for%20the%20%E2%80%9Crevenge%20attack%E2%80%9D%2C%20according%20to%20several%20posts%20on%20social%20media.%20The%20Wire%2C%20however%2C%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20verify%20the%20authenticity%20of%20these%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESoldier%20killed%20in%20Narla%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20encounter%20took%20place%20more%20than%20a%20month%20after%20three%20army%20soldiers%20were%20gunned%20down%20in%20a%20forested%20area%20in%20the%20adjoining%20Kulgam%20district%20of%20south%20Kashmir.%20A%20Jaish-e-Mohammad-linked%20terror%20outfit%20had%20claimed%20responsibility%20for%20the%20attack%20in%20which%20two%20more%20Army%20soldiers%20were%20injured.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20setback%20for%20security%20forces%20in%20Kokernag%20came%20on%20a%20day%20when%20the%20Army%20gunned%20down%20two%20terrorists%20in%20Rajouri%20district%20of%20Jammu.%20An%20Army%20soldier%20was%20also%20killed%20in%20the%20operation%20in%20Narla%20village%20while%20three%20more%20soldiers%20were%20injured.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20initial%20exchange%20of%20gunfire%20in%20Rajouri%2C%20Kent%2C%20a%20six-year-old%20female%20Labrador%20of%20the%20Army%E2%80%99s%20dog%20unit%2C%20was%20shot%20and%20died%20while%20trying%20to%20save%20her%20handler.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20year%2C%20at%20least%2010%20Army%20soldiers%2C%20including%20five%20commandos%20of%20the%20elite%20para%20unit%20were%20killed%20in%20two%20separate%20attacks%20and%20encounters%20in%20Poonch%20and%20Rajouri%20districts%20of%20Pir%20Panjal%2C%20a%20region%20which%20remained%20free%20of%20terrorism%20for%20nearly%20two%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENorthern%20Army%20Commander%20Lieutenant%20General%20Upendra%20Dwivedi%20told%20reporters%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20a%20function%20at%20IIT%20Jammu%20that%20Pakistan%20was%20pushing%20foreign%20terrorists%20into%20J%26amp%3BK%20to%20disrupt%20peace.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPakistan%20is%20trying%20to%20make%20efforts%20from%20its%20side%20to%20send%20foreign%20terrorists%20here%2C%20despite%20the%20better%20internal%20conditions%20(security%20situation)%2C%20so%20that%20they%20can%20create%20some%20kind%20of%20obstacle.%20This%20is%20because%20of%20the%20progress%20that%20we%20are%20making%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%E2%80%9D%20Lt%20Gen%20Dwivedi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694623001000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F13215256%2FUntitled-design-6.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fsouth-kashmir-officers-killed-attack%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22An%20Army%20spokesperson%20said%20the%20killings%20took%20place%20during%20a%20joint%20anti-insurgency%20operation%20involving%20J%26amp%3BK%20Police%20and%20the%20Army%20in%20the%20intervening%20night%20of%20September%2012%20and%2013.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fsouth-kashmir-officers-killed-attack%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Special%20discussion%20on%20Parliament's%20journey%20on%20first%20day%20of%20upcoming%20session%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694622797000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-05%2F26%2Ffull%2F1685119195-4932.jpg%22%