ted%20me%20for%20their%20daughters.%20Only%20after%20a%20lot%20of%20assurances%20from%20others%20was%20I%20able%20to%20get%20married%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Ravindra%20bought%20an%20acre%20of%20land%20in%20Amravati.%20With%20a%20bank%20loan%20of%20Rs%205%20lakh%2C%20he%20expanded%20the%20farm%20with%204%2C000%20hens.%20%E2%80%9CBy%20then%2C%20I%20started%20earning%20well%20from%20the%20business%20and%20got%20my%20%3Cem%3Ekachaa%20%3C%2Fem%3Ehouse%20renovated.%20Soon%20after%2C%20I%20expanded%20the%20farm%20to%2012%2C000%20hens%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20his%20happiness%20was%20short-lived.%20In%202006%2C%20India%20witnessed%20an%20outbreak%20of%20bird%20flu%20that%20took%20a%20toll%20on%20the%20poultry%20business.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20the%20first%20bird%20flu%20in%20the%20country.%20People%20were%20scared%20to%20consume%20broilers%20and%20eggs.%20They%20even%20forced%20poultry%20farmers%20to%20kill%20their%20birds.%20I%20sold%2016%2C000%20broilers%20for%20Rs%202%E2%80%933%20per%20kg%2C%20which%20were%20earlier%20sold%20at%20Rs%2050%E2%80%9360%20per%20kg%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Famravati-3-1694610856.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Over%20the%20years%2C%20Ravindra%20advanced%20his%20farm%20with%20improved%20technologies.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Famravati-3-1694610856.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Famravati-3-1694610856-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Famravati-3-1694610856-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Famravati-3-1694610856-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20h