%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F327807%2Fgautam-yadav-person-living-with-hiv-shares-myths-and-things-to-know%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eproper%20scientific%20analysis%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20reports.%20The%20goal%20for%20both%20patient%20and%20doctor%20is%20to%20put%20the%20former%20on%20the%20right%20path.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%2C%20she%20says%2C%20will%20encourage%20people%20to%20get%20professional%20expert%20advice%20instead%20of%20reaching%20out%20for%20unsolicited%20advice%20from%20friends%20and%20family%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20health.%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20works%20for%20one%20person%20may%20not%20work%20for%20another%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20cautions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20even%20while%20Laxmi%E2%80%99s%20endeavour%20was%20proving%20successful%2C%20she%20points%20to%20certain%20gaps%20that%20she%20struggled%20with%20as%20someone%20who%20was%20a%20novice%20to%20the%20business%20world.%20%E2%80%9CTo%20add%20to%20this%20I%20was%20a%20woman%20entrepreneur%20entering%20a%20new%20field.%20There%20were%20many%20areas%20that%20I%20needed%20assistance%20with%20%E2%80%94%20pitching%20presentations%2C%20interacting%20with%20other%20professionals%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F329202%2Fgwalior-professor-nidhi-katare-becomes-successful-mushroom-farmer-earns-lakhs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emarketing%20the%20brand%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20product%2C%20etc.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FI-WIN_TBI_02-1-1-1694182758.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22I-Venture%20%40%20ISB%20Women%20of%20Innovation%20(I-WIN)%20Program%20helps%20women%20entrepreneurs%20scale%20their%20startups%5C%22%2