%20world%20by%20making%20them%20investment-ready%2C%20designing%20business%20models%2C%20setting%20up%20engagements%20with%20experts%2C%20offering%20them%20pilot%20opportunities%20etc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDetailing%20the%20process%20of%20how%20it%20works%2C%20Harshit%20says%20%E2%80%9CWe%20prepare%20a%20structure%20for%20the%20program%20along%20with%20the%20offerings%2C%20then%20open%20applications%20to%20startups%20across%20India.%20This%20is%20followed%20by%20a%20bridge%20round.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20selection%20round%20involves%20the%20team%20analysing%20each%20startup%20against%20a%20list%20of%20criteria.%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F316961%2Fbengaluru-entrepreneur-platform-find-jobs-for-women-after-career-maternity-break-herkey%2F%5C%22%3EThe%20startup%3C%2Fa%3E%20should%20be%20one%20year%20old%20at%20least%2C%20should%20be%20product%20based%20and%20the%20team%20must%20be%20able%20to%20spot%20areas%20of%20refinement%2C%E2%80%9D%20elaborates%20Harshit.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20the%20next%20four%20months%2C%20the%20ventures%20are%20given%20personalised%20attention%2C%20where%20gaps%20are%20identified%2C%20and%20the%20venture%20strategy%20is%20deconstructed%20by%20experts.%20In%20addition%20to%20this%20one-on-one%20mentoring%20support%20is%20provided%20to%20each%20woman%2C%20enabling%20her%20to%20identify%20the%20challenges%20she%20is%20facing.%20The%20I-Venture%20%40%20ISB%20team%20is%20constantly%20in%20touch%20with%20the%20selected%20participants%20to%20know%20their%20progress%20and%20discuss%20the%20leads%20they%20have.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20four%20months%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F313382%2Ftelangana-millet-man-led-millet-revolution-helped-dalit-women-earn-pv-satheesh%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erigorous%20training%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20women%20are%20ready%20to%20fly.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%