ctors%20in%20Hollywood.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E2.%20Heroines%20of%20war%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20Bangladesh%20Liberation%20War%20(1947%E2%80%931971)%2C%20a%20group%20of%20freedom%20fighters%20organised%20themselves%20into%20a%20group%20called%20the%20%E2%80%98Mukti%20Bahini%E2%80%99.%20They%20set%20the%20stage%20for%20young%20women%20to%20be%20trained%20in%20combat%20and%20various%20operations.%20Two%20of%20its%20members%20Captain%20Sitara%20Begum%20and%20Taramon%20Bibi%20were%20conferred%20with%20the%20%E2%80%98Bir%20Protik%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20the%20fourth%20highest%20gallantry%20award%20in%20Bangladesh%20%E2%80%94%20for%20their%20outstanding%20bravery.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaramon%20Bibi%20worked%20as%20a%20cook%20for%20the%20Mukti%20Bahini%20and%20never%20missed%20a%20chance%20to%20use%20this%20position%20of%20hers%20to%20roam%20through%20the%20area%20and%20keep%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F324744%2Fmany-nayak-historic-film-on-caste-kahi-debe-sandesh-created-chhatisgarhi-cinema%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etrack%20of%20happenings.%3C%2Fa%3E%20She%20did%20this%20in%20the%20guise%20of%20a%20woman%20with%20a%20mental%20disability.%20She%20would%20observe%20the%20Pakistani%20Army%E2%80%99s%20movements%20and%20then%20report%20these%20to%20the%20Mukti%20Bahini%2C%20who%20would%20then%20act%20on%20these%20reports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECaptain%20Sitara%20Begum%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20served%20as%20a%20doctor%20with%20the%20force.%20The%20Kolkata%20native%20oversaw%20operations%20at%20a%20Bangladesh%20Hospital%20where%20casualties%20of%20war%20and%20emergent%20cases%20needed%20attention.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYears%20before%20these%20two%20fearless%20women%20could%20play%20their%20role%2C%20a%20young%20girl%20Rajkumari%20Gupta%20displayed%20the%20same%20zeal%20during%20%3Ca